user_reviews: [{"Name":"Satyam Chaudhary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAV-NdO6RXpeLAnl6QS1XtMPs2F7xb4cUgjI-9zAFYFsqPCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had really great experience at this place… The taste was so good and truly indian. The quantity and quality was outstanding. The music was amazing as well, hindi music which i really liked. They have different options of food such as north indian south indian. They also gave us gulab jaaum for free … great gesture great customer service. ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️🇮🇳🇮🇳","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPCKZPCoPa37eroL9PMZecknMKubWVcfFB_AKf\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Aung Thiha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwYf1ki_6-c2s5n7bDPLDnFlNyr0J4svOmCKIggCE4dk19s0qL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Although it was my first time coming here, the food was amazing. I had goat Thali and my girlfriend had Chloe and puri and the spices was perfect especially the goat curry I couldn’t get enough of it. Definitely recommend this and you should try the place out if you are looking for authentic Indian food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMo0_yLp2dD0CJcKf2Sw61tvPr6jZEIb0RWJh9K\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Eduardo Gutiérrez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCf5SMWULQ_Xi4NkYNoBJ3lzxdcPw0LEANBIv7mAAZmLyCnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I had a very good experience here. Food was delicious, excellent Indian food, very welcoming and friendly service. Both the young man who told us what some plates were about and the waitress were very helpful and patient. The plates didn't look too large but oh my, they were. We left the place very satisfied. The curry was rich and flavourful. Nice background Indian music and everything very clean and organized.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1hXOaiO9DLTy70hI4x0Sk_iz0OvvP8JPUIKKK\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Pierre Chauvot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfwae3DmSiFlf6yRJvj5IPH0RTcYu2LslJMaql94_yykD5gFJM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first experience at 4 Seasons Chaat House was delightful. The service was excellent; our waiter took the time to explain the various dishes and checked on us several times throughout the meal. The appetizers were particularly impressive, and the main course was equally delightful. I look forward to returning and highly recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOENjqr9RjAlxbkNm3PGNy-qOWhyJciPqbEpS6Y\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Dhwani Kedia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqGYhZ3WmMa_IDwM3tRR2i6RpXT2xw2VzKb13HI7q8NYUhgyS6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered veg chowmein, veg chilli momos and amristsari kulcha. I would say all 3 dishes were very nice. Chowmein was proper indo street style. And the amristsari kulcha came with chole which tasted really good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxiLD2WxSLhdjRVEcILSyBYiq4tOu1u2-YKzJ3\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"V D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXTyl-R6NJcyrgjR7_vBed8eYvsa2XbmRpBt6p_Rp4nZHddA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"4 Seasons Chaat House offers a delightful experience. Their Dahi Puri is incredibly refreshing, with a perfect balance of crisp puris, tangy yogurt, and flavorful chutneys. The lamb curry is satisfying, with tender meat and rich, aromatic spices. The service is attentive, ensuring a pleasant dining experience. Overall, a must-visit for anyone craving authentic and delicious Indian street food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMox04mD47MM0xKd-fseppYPRmnCZNHf7kk8Llo\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Jasleen Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJq_mX4JcS2qCxDJUdxLM5cEoBdw7wYfyUdfHLGfdunsmqsnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve ordered from this restaurant through Uber Eats multiple times, and it never ceases to impress. Each dish showcases a distinct and masterful flavor profile, perfectly balanced with just the right blend of spices. The Tandoori Soya Chaap is nothing short of extraordinary—truly a culinary masterpiece.Overall, this place deserves a flawless 10/10 for its consistent excellence.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP40IJUB4fY-V0qfNghXjMny0KCyltV3nOW6d3B\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Yulim Yoon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtNF4mImeFZ7QtRmwhw9wcZ7r6MKKexCz9qurZDFK4b390eRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly staff and great food! The staff was very helpful and quick. The butter curry, coconut shrimp, and Dahi Puri were amazing! However, the garlic naan lacked garlic flavor, and the rice portion was not big.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYhiOFyL2GfhvUOxH5_alU__z-c7G5FQQPZdXM\u0026fid=0x0:0x8648c0d45ae07d73"],"When":"2024-7-22"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We stopped by El Santo for happy hour and had a great experience! We sat at the bar and enjoyed a couple of drinks in the romantic atmosphere inside. A must-try is the El Trio de Salsas - it’s absolutely delicious! We highly recommend El Santo for a fun and romantic evening out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkT8EmXcTzgAFww4IqHdYHds65_KcYK6Ej0Von\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Amanda Ballantyne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_5vlj7yXUGy_6pMA2oPSW0Ema7d32lk4ZVKgwLnF8pOgeHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a wonderful experience here yesterday. We were headed to a show so needed an early dinner and decided to try out the happy hour at a favourite of ours, El Santo. We moved out of New West a year ago but try to get back to this gem when we can. We parked at the Columbia skytrain station and it’s just a 2 minute walk from there. From the minute we stepped through the doors we were greeted warmly and provided with friendly, knowledgeable service from the wonderful staff. We decided to do tapas style so we could sample more items and had the trio of salsas with their homemade tortilla chips, a trio of tacos, the best brussel sprouts ever and the cornbread with jalapeño jelly. Every bite was just perfection and we left stuffed! My only regret was that I was too full to get some of their churros for dessert…I dream about those things…sigh. Also, their margaritas are the best in the business. Seriously, you must try one. It was another great visit and there will be many more to come!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ8vf5MxY9NvVXqT2JWy_P0GGaR3iAGfHVgrk5\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Thomas Wilczynski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJD24Or0RUBGSuMLrdcePCdBXv8sl7ZLUknVBIS-JYZ_nACiVt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This restaurant is excellent! Sophisticated vibes and an impressive menu. The chicken empanadas were perfect. Now, it is an upscale dining experience, so prices are higher and quantity is lower. If this is your style, then I totally recommend El Santo. But, my family and friends wouldn't enjoy this so much. I just went here solo to celebrate the day after my birthday, and I had no regrets.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPI24atQLYD_a0X0w6Jh1s1MjvoEZnGt7xWFbdu\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Jessie Kenk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHO7_squ4YXAxgK5UNOjY9caZDzSTUhThfzCKeZMd7_ZDrAuM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"El Santo is a cute little restaurant a super close walk from the New West Skytrain station. Went on a Sunday evening and they were able to accommodate my party of 6. The restaurant lighting had a moody ambiance but a super lively atmosphere. The host and the waitstaff provided excellent service. Everyone loved their drinks both the alcoholic cocktails and zero-proof. I ordered the burrata and it was delicious I loved the tart marmalade. The pescaco taco was a hearty helping size the fish and the toppings were super fresh. Other dishes of note were the guacamole trio, empanadas, and definitely get the churros for dessert they are fried perfectly!! Overall the quality of the food is worth the price pull definitely recommended as a date night, as an outing for a special occasion or just if you're craving delicious Mexican food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEOCerU6c6cS0Knw3TyKAtBfiYOhgb_ml3nrXY\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Oluwayomi Adebule","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXqcIg8ujO4XiC50cD8_FM6q8RuvnCHkeqVI4f08BodMBvibbJTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ambience was ok. Lighting was a bit dark, but maybe they went for the cozy dim. The service was great and Sophia was attentive and ever ready to help. The food portions were quite small and you need to order more than one dish for fulfillment. As it was brunch, the menu was very limited. The drinks were cool and they offered to fix the overly limey taste of the mangonada. It’s an ok choice for brunch if you’re in the New Westminster area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXm3-kUfykxZ6OvDYhrG5fYaAP8XFpXjW71zzF\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Harrison K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyo531Mh7oStmPsGBaM8AJF3i5eACQbjfzoajBXrYo2AJFczKXPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to El Santo a few times. The food is great. The drinks are great. The service is great. The owner was present and friendly.\n\nThe menu is clear, interesting, and makes me want to come back again. I had a special experience there last night. Kudos to the team for the great service! 5 stars.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPq7cX3DdaoFJQCOwD8YZvPvLjPhv3mQuzaE71v\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"FORK IT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWQ1Zlffqb4yf-X0sZJA8Q4AQh2En8DJPTiPmPPRNczFataG21=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We've been to El Santo twice, the food is fantastic - our personal favorites are the tacos. Service is good but had an issue with slow service during our first trip when we were seated on the patio. Second visit was much better. Be sure to order a side of cornbread, it's has great texture and fluffy (not super dense).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3kkp-3lJn_Bgnh4vkSMHWyaHKoBsAUwiN_mJ0\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2023-12-13"},{"Name":"Sandra Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS3d7aZA4lMhkB4lrjOTrDjB_p6PvngmeWQeM0VFHPfzqli2Uc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My first time here and it was a delight. Excellent service and interesting menu of drinks, tacos and more. We were given the back room and stayed to chat until closing (4 hours!); that’s how comfortable we ladies felt.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzzDl5wwn740Xcx2FcbMxTj1GE374Ew69hxOru\u0026fid=0x0:0x78b241c739ac4f3e"],"When":"2024-6-17"}]

Everything was delicious, but I loved the house special and cold cuts subs the best. The bread is made in house, and the veggies are crisp and fresh. They were sold out of the fish cake option; would love to try it next time as it was highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNq3YXNry5LW4nrUz3JgqALWtnEPPtbNBdy1yUC&fid=0x0:0x6fbdb648c890ebb1"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Robyn Stalkie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0D0viPJQ2DPspzMME4w7-dQOnaiZXIAsobcm4vyhV_EP5MGWLIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the lemongrass beef banh mi (pictured) and the house special banh mi, both are phenomenal! On top of all that, the owner is super nice and welcoming. We love a friendly, high-quality local business to support!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOc9IJl8U8NObNmH0-ghcmKlhIDVPLqhKG8Bw3C&fid=0x0:0x6fbdb648c890ebb1"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"DJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUy5WLlQVhPVYxUgEaVuA2cUdIWSqrSf3U8cWSRiXWA_X__YG82=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's my first trying their Banh Mi and I enjoyed their Ultimate Meat sub! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"S A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJOMOiZKMkVhzEB7ZORr37dwap2afh8DAG6IHDyoctwDav8XVN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited this place around 9:15 PM, and while it wasn’t crowded, it had a pleasant vibe. The ambiance is fantastic—warm, welcoming, and with a cozy, homely vibe. The staff are incredibly friendly and hospitable, making the experience even better.

Food:
•	Onion Rings (Onion Pakora): The portion size is massive—500 grams, easily enough for four people. It’s absolutely delicious and brings a wave of nostalgia. 5/5
•	Chai: Easily one of the best chai I’ve ever had. 5/5
•	Vada Pav: Authentic Mumbai-style, served with mirchi on the side. 4.5/5

The food is extraordinary, and each dish feels unique. The menu itself is very good, they wrote their story which is inspiring,  and descriptions of each dish, giving diners a deeper connection to the food.

The decor is inspiring and distinctly Indian. The large Shivaji wallpaper is an eye-catching centerpiece, and the walls are decorated with vibrant paintings.

✨One unique feature stole my attention —a display that automatically changes numbers every 30 seconds when a person follows on their Instagram. It’s innovative and something I’ve never seen before, not even in renowned places like Chef Ramsay’s restaurants. Whoever came up with this idea is a genius!

This place offers a truly authentic vibe and stays true to its word of filling not just the stomach but also the soul. I’m already planning my next visit to try more dishes. 5/5

Highly recommend it to anyone looking for a slice of India, especially Maharashtra!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJN7Ux-8c-ptDmyx0qJOW4VNPYjzF49xgMlI2z&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Jessica Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOeC5VCbc6g3HH3dxXpDS9bE993HEKMDVI3SjHX2aNdHbQOJHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very fun and memorable experience with a variety of sauces and spices to be put together in soft buns and the sweetest part was that the person working there made it for me in front of me after finding out it was my first time trying this. Her version turned out better than mine so that was good to discover. The lemonade was the best too so grateful she mentioned it. If someone likes spice they have to go here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzLbkXhPLQ16hQN75HxkNkrf74ZmCoKZW5uxG4&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Sneha Asati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9R-sCgdzbUB7L6z4ugERo-TvCCYYI9pRLSX05DM_Kqe1P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is an authentic maharastrian restaurant. I ordered puranpoli with Katachi Amti, vada pav, kothimbir vadi and Misal pav and thecha.
I must mention Katachi amti was one of the best I had so far, and I am comparing food with what I used to have in locals of maharastra.
The ha is just same as you will find in area of khandesh and marathwada.
Having this thecha took me to my memories to those places.
Vada was so oil free and very authentic.

One must try this places to know what is Maharastrian food is with authenticity not just in taste but the way they serve and meet customers.
Owner takes Athiti Devo bhav concept very seriously.

I am definitely visiting place again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPY7cXMrDDT3ok0Zoot6FOQaYkT19SHlhWr4As&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Kal H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWg0T9Dm25DyoGPq0klBDFGunO6KyhuEtE0HxE6FHqy7DOxmZEJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I went with friends to try VadaPav Mirchi by Geeta.
Firstly, The food was very tasty and I’ve never had Marathi food before. Similar to Gujarati food I’m most familiar with.

I’ve had a few days to think this over and I really want to support VadaPav, however there are a few concerns I wasn’t pleased about:
- the service was quite slow and bringing out the starters at the same time as a main was surprising but not all our meals came together too so it was a wait for the rest to appear especially when you want to start a meal together.
- Unfortunately they didn’t have the items I wanted on the menu: “We’ve run out” which didn’t seem possible as we went for an early lunch. They did however suddenly have one starter at the end of our meal once the owner came to talk to us. Not complimentary of course.
- the prices, imo, are very expensive for the little quantity I personally ordered. The stainless steel plates looked empty compared to the photos on the picture menus (see photos for my order).
- there were 3 of us adults, we ordered 2 mains and 3 starters. No drinks. Our total paid was $110. Again exorbitant for the little quantity of food received.
- the signature VadaPav is tasty (and so glad no onions) but think it would be better if the two tiny bread rolls were warmed instead of super cold?

I hope they take my comments to note and I really do wish them well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_QVK_SOoH9TBcCvx8-a9fF9eVlkjXlM1osIDF&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Jasleen Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJq_mX4JcS2qCxDJUdxLM5cEoBdw7wYfyUdfHLGfdunsmqsnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first time visiting this restaurant, and I must say, it was a delightful surprise! The food was served with such care and attention to detail, and the employee's recommendations were spot-on and truly impressive. The flavors were unlike anything I’ve ever experienced—each bite was a treat for the taste buds. We are already looking forward to coming back and exploring more dishes from their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtfpH6NKMncm3o5wdN0fArmfRfLxMio98SkYYz&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Bansi Khant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEknKHs5BCZh8ldDUUSHJm-RxN31Gd-WO6faHT71rcnHWdMjhM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is the most authentic place for Maharashtra’s dishes. It is nice place with marathi songs playing in the background, you would feel you are in Mumbai. I ordered misal pav and vadapav. They were ao delicious. Paperless menu. Clean washroom. Friendly staff. Prices are little higher","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPk9Y_N_KwY0j1vmh3kX3v_3SY9nTT8e2djMD9T&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Yashwanti Borade","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnmtXVHq7EJ1ebNx-KH_O33FJq--nTH2MHsiWxHWPWGMlv1EOV5g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food WILL remind you of Maharashtra! To add cherry on the top, the owners and staff are all so pleasant to talk to! Makes the experience one of it's kind in the lower mainland!
We tried the bhel, vadapav, sabudana vada and Pav bhaji, it was heavenly!
The decor reminded me of restaurants in Maharashtra, showcasing the map of the state, wallpapers of Shivaji Maharaj and many saints, too! They play good Marathi music that'll make you bob your head as you savour each bite!
100% recommend!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiwbhxfQTVs4MbPsCFqGY8BIV-pDQWCQrvy0dg&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"Sandeep Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWtr0rGTEaK0fL2PXFOyX7ydxQsGjCKp-ECupdgiocDntlnYIxHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here is amazing!!🤩 This place is very different from your typical Indian restaurant/cafe. The atmosphere is that of a casual cafe with feature art wall.The food seemed a little pricey when going through the menu, however, the portions are were so big, especially the Kanda Bhaje (Onion fritters), we are a family of four, and we still had leftovers to take home. Highly recommend their masala chai (it’s on the sweeter side,  generous milk, strong tea flavour, and distinct ginger taste). My two kids shared a Shrikhand Puri & Bhaaji plate (sweet yogurt, fried flatbread, lentil soup, potato curry), and they loved it soo much, our waiter tipped us that we could order more of individual items from the plate, the kids loved so we did that. Also towards the end the owner came up to us to say hi, and ask how we liked the food and of our experience there, we felt everyone was super friendly and helpful. We are definitely going to be coming back here to try more items, as this was just our first visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMB22KTgrVXdqPiIuQMKRldUdLpwsaV9bNpldQE&fid=0x0:0x4f70b6c0bdafc7a9"],"When":"2024-9-8"}]

[{"Name":"K W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVerGSMVZq5pPiETKXh_wr8CdqRuI6f0r01YGBB82mTJNdyt-A_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place is busy for good reason! We ordered the margarita pitcher to share, chips & guac and I ordered 2 tacos for myself. The food is delicious, well flavoured, & has good sized portions. staff are very friendly & attentive, despite being so busy! Go early to avoid the wait.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMomLGYpnz5Vgei1dy12cJk5zdDJia0TmtBjhJt&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Scott Tsai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRsXeUuhru0GbyjYAfI5Sqcvukd0aZ9hv6cFG9Uki8lsJ8EDJGxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everythinggggg is just perfect, food are great and fantastic overall. The lineup can be up to 20min+ if after 6-7pm but it varies. There's weekday special too but 11-4pm . I highly recommend monster burrito or $3 taco especially the shrimp with cheese or beef tongue💕💕","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbdDNHyy1MYii6hBQnRngmqYmNyUEUhjRiDIFK&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Camilia Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWigkoqaNhHJinW1sDEWmiP5-QkCbLl16QFp5xZiy1DDMYI0dmUuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here for lunch today and I was surprised to see such a small place so full for lunchtime! I believe the other comments when they say there’s a wait on the weekends! I ordered the pollo asado and my friend ordered a burrito. It was so delicious! The service was amazing and the atmosphere was welcoming. I will have to come back ☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAlkDGSUXd0xgKchhT9F5DbaiMl7DB7aw41QoD&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Carla Cabrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyAMgtnaFupCyPAv17OwvwftYUJ_kVL13H0OIF7_nMrISRiNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wonderful tacos! I went for lunch on a Wednesday, and it was busy, but since the place is big and has plenty of tables, I could find a seat. The waitress took quite a bit to take my order, but I guess it was because crowded and just 2 people attending the clients in the dining room. I asked a ceviche to share, which was good, and a plate of 3 tacos (shrimp, carne asada and mushrooms), all of them were super tasty and yummy, it came with lots of toppings, price is super affordable and worth it. The chili sauces are delicious. It feels like a real mexican restaurant (flavor, size and price). Definitely, I would  like to go back and try other dishes. I forgot to take photos of the tacos cause they were so good that I remembered just when it was over. 😅","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEWXULL66QwT1duKf8Z6NYiGFXQGR5-vD4iBQW&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-10-30"},{"Name":"EM BRUNCH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHAIEhTHPNKaVrAENeCluwUU3ICAVU7jFdASNd2XhEQlICPnbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a gem, delicious food, expect to wait (well worth the wait). (Beef tongue, tongue, and chorizo tacos) Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOC4avIl614FCCCCBw_1Z6x4UOHqi9uAR5BbkKX&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Esther W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ44_CjQ6-wehLPc33Ng17kPOWOSFrXqo3jg5WgP7CtwNUYUeR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is amazing.
Would come again but….
Knocked down a star for the abnormal amount of flies in the restaurant.

Recommend new menus as the old ones are sticky feeling.
Restaurant was so busy the waitress didn’t even come by once till the end, would have preferred to get some hot sauce.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhN3TScBKDckearCaHhFL2P_5a33OjcJslXcIR&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Ellise T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPm6V1RCVQF-kZbmGdjH4TRiLMpf7DB5U0r-1fjBEf84Ngffdy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"6 tacos, rice and beans, and tres leches cake for only $30: the prices cannot be beat. Food is delicious and authentic, service is friendly and attentive. Easily the best Mexican restaurant in the Vancouver area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIsYOlqw1OEW9q0-AZ4ZR-RH6zlcxKhJD5MvKf&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-7-11"},{"Name":"Colin Ayin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNThQBOssLQG15FrOGVWLdw-1FGy71jx_7x0mXbil8RYsYWWrX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good daily deals. Reasonably priced food compared to a lot of other places and authentic cuisine. Have recommended this place to many friends and all agree this is a great spot for food with friends and family that won't bust your wallet","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTB0gzuwnOTmuSQ5KAc5H4heR16MOY3YPV7yDp&fid=0x0:0x59734df77df7b2a7"],"When":"2024-9-4"}]

[{"Name":"Celina Arenillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPvcNqjpmtihcb5J8miFlC4lw0H-EdaSQUtLM4u3kh0_GMHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had dinner here. The food was great and cheaper as compared to other Indian Restaurants in New Westminster. Service was pleasant.

I think they have to work on their back area where the washroom was, it was unkept and dark, making the washroom look not as clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdsNgkpEQ6TbpZvsQvIghhP9MNUvHErvt28k-9&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Richard Catania","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItC6YbJoIIB4dwzioVUZ1DnCoFgM8-BVohNT5avuOwKh7Rhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Poor communication, and lack luster food. Ordered a butter chicken, chicken vindaloo, chicken biryani, and naan. When I got there they had a tandoori chicken instead of the vindaloo. She didn’t know what vindaloo was. I said I asked if you had vindaloo when I called to order and you said yes. I showed her a picture, she asked the owner I assume and they made a vindaloo.  Food was very oily, and very bland. The butter chicken was not bad and naan was good. The vindaloo was tasteless. No punch of spice nor vinegar. Same with the biryani. Butter chicken and vindaloo did not come with the basmati rice as it was supposed to. I called back when I got home and was told it only comes with curries. What is butter chicken and vindaloo?  Will not order from here again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO85KB_cKwsNNSmmVnlxxzgqbI9jaQxnFo3Ycph&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"discovery sonu ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_b2reRKsjtiT_HffF8-yN5QM1sqqpXd5OaoIUa8-ff3hRWT7Gdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this restaurant and had a wonderful experience. The interior decoration is beautiful and creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The staff is incredibly cooperative. And a special mention goes to Mandeep Kaur, who provided exceptional service. She was friendly, professional, she made our dining experience enjoyable 😊😊😊Overall, it's a fantastic place to eat, and I highly recommend it to anyone looking for a great meal and excellent service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpFtpUL7UTlXjlxA1DkEvaMjpbHbSXvZFRL4vD&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Johnny G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBbi4rvv-nHDl7H6RXbToA_kk3n9Hj_ierIgyWzQHyZr_63w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The flavours here are amazing. Every dish is fully loaded with deliciousness. I want to try everything here. Very curious what everything tastes like. Fish pakora deal is reasonable and portion is pretty big. The samosas are excellent. Nice and crispy with spice. Non veg combo was pretty solid, pretty filling. Lamb curry and butter chicken was so flavorful. These flavors turned my chicanery filled day into a super positive flavor explosion in my mouth.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMByDw_KPHdSo-oNPXdSWgscX1D-xSQthM4RR2-&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Srikantha Kalaghatta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7kV3vSmU11E2VJr6yMSYBtHLByJ47CPuwfOKoc_5xVBiEfsZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My wife and I went to this restaurant last evening and we both were really hungry. The place is quite modest and there is street parking right in front of the restaurant. The experience at this restaurant didn't start off great! The initial welcome lacked attention from the front desk staff, leaving us to find our own table and later, place our order at the front desk ourselves as no one came to our table to take the order.

We ordered Veg Fried Rice and Channa Batura and both were exceptionally flavorful. However, it took 28 minutes for our order to arrive despite us being the only customers at that time. The tardiness aside, we would certainly be going back here for the tasty food.

The potential of this restaurant lies in its delectable cuisine. With improved service, Indian Courtyard has the potential to offer an excellent dining option in the New Westminster neighborhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFC9cWeuGKfDCbkfs7-dtRsYiOJF_rNZTC0yiM&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2023-12-14"},{"Name":"604 Eats","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKydooBZGXt2w5Pplqp4pqyT8VrJYMUXmY8f1v2W9oYs1nCEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food smelled delicious and tasted pretty good.  The price for the portion size is pretty decent.  My coconut curry lamb was amazing, but my friend's chicken Tikka masala was too spicy for her liking.  The veggie pakora was good, but a little dry/overcooked.  The restaurant has a nice ambiance, but I think most of their business is take out as they didn't have wine as a drink selection.  I would come here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxMRE-vTlo4RqDWAIzteLaXsoMW1cAzo5L66QC&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2022-11-15"},{"Name":"Ramin Tahouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3PGFwXhFR5wrjRgqZ8C6g76cQqHMugwCusafBYZgKtQdvNkVR0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came in here with an old buddy to get some late night grub. Food was over all tasty and excellent. Their lamb methi malai was really good. The portion sizes don’t seem to make much sense. I was a bit disappointed in the portion size being $18 for the main but was served as half the size of a normal full order at any other restaurant you can think of. Their Raita was on the other hand, over portioned. But all in all really good food and service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsMIuqXRQkmmVae-4LjhOtqlGCoX1SKWxOPeaW&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2023-9-29"},{"Name":"Coleen C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUauoBULHRivIFwYCvu4BqvyF8VvNRVLHo1AYN5p3b5oAIqNmsS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first dining experience here was amazing! I've been hearing good things about this restaurant in FB New West group and this place doesn't disappoint. The flavour definitely hits the spot! I'll definitely go back again to try other things in the menu. I hope they'll add in their menu an option of butter chicken sauce in the samosa someday. I think its a good combination. I highly recommend this place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOw6KunyGFNf_P-QFA5WL1aQ8AKDC-tRi8Z9Ap6&fid=0x0:0x7dd7f0b272a60b60"],"When":"2021-5-28"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Nick Conville","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKpi4QYB5c_SP88c5k4iX-5Go-rx0QbVgwqitr4Tn-Yz8YBvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The brothers that own Donaire make absolutely phenomenal food!!!

Every day when I work construction in the area, probably 12 years ago, I would go there at least three or four times a week during lunch and it was always quick fresh and delicious… They make food for the working man it’s hot and it fills your belly for a day of work…

Move on and I’m not a business owner myself and understand the importance of these reviews and telling people how amazing certain businesses are so thank you guys…. I was absolutely pumped to see that coming through Vancouver racing for a ferry. They were still open, and I got two of their best owners, and they even gave me a special discount.!!

No tax for the holiday!!!
Not all heroes wear capes and when you Try their food you’ll see what I mean. I highly recommend the super chicken lamb combo and just tell him make it the way they’d make it for themselves.!!!

You guys rock
Nick Conville
Island, silver, and gold brokers Canada
You made my night and I’ll be back for sure. Next time I’m in Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMYJGzjSmRsxGnQvdpbVHvjliFg50auZHCbdnf&fid=0x0:0xe3981d8a9ad71da5"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Jason Bonett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJevN1qrI-JE0p9isQdXAMsJWOKwVPQ2fXZP9U8C6xpdZTkddDE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I went to this place based on the reviews, take your money somewhere else just up the street there a few other donairs a thousand times better than this, girl took some white rice added some dry meat on it and some cabbage on the side and said $14.99, but i can't just sit here and lie so i took some pics you tell me what about this looks appetizing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKIQ86JMGvDCrubE83mjqbFuDYhXjjqpKHt9QW&fid=0x0:0xe3981d8a9ad71da5"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Emmanuel Morúa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVgDDr7Bq5maIJYTC_on0x6OlVE8ViM6rt1o7JGzQMU2HdiVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly way beyond better than any other places like Donair Dude or even some other local donair spots, for $16.50 I got a large lamb donair with extra lamb, peace tea and a baklava and I’m super full (big eater). I couldn’t believe is so cheap and the donair so tasty, very compact and flavourful. Definitely my new donair place, so far the best I tried in New Westminster.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR103qSjJmBj_y2LJhZkReShHacgsr5NhBVXAr&fid=0x0:0xe3981d8a9ad71da5"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Sammy Kovach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3t3Gi2do0oUWWA_SsdulsyOmoZPemK5rrGHM1VAOxXI7VIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This store still remains 5 stars, and my absolute favourite donairs. ALTHOUGH - ordering online has turned into a 2 star rating because, they almost never add your extra toppings to your order.... This would be my 4th attempt to getting a correct order. And to me, these toppings make their donairs a little extra delicious. I hope soon they will pay attention better, as the prices are even more online than coming in person... Makes you really not want to order online.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C Pérez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWILDNLHQbwQ4WYh0f_XaV2u7QTtA8bZ0QNemPRYV6F4iiNEtYnbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The chicken and beef donairs are really good.  The regular size is huge so, you can have 2 meals unless you are very hungry.  Once I ordered the chicken platter and I found the portions small although you get a ton of rice.  I recommend the donairs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_yLeDk525G_WfxqMy2wiOxtDyLDgAXqsWUilD&fid=0x0:0xe3981d8a9ad71da5"],"When":"2023-10-16"},{"Name":"Samuel Kwok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPB-mPjJbPqbBG9ozUjg8V-CCdJe21jhjrrg34dyj8Qy7Pyh9O=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The portion is big. My fat friend can finish it. I am fit so I can only eat half at a time. The Coke is in a can. The salad is fresh. When it’s cold outside, the donair warms you up. Generous amount of napkins given.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charlie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtCM69Z0a-wqgtNUeScJW00UVLPLB30hrfWfbWhtFpo0oE-amo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Now that’s what I call a donair!! 😋😋 I haven’t been here for 2 years, I live on the big island now & the lady behind the counter remembered me when I used to live close by & was a regular! 😊 Amazing service, always greeted with a great smile & your restaurant smells heavenly!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZ0_emRBJE5Jp1wJtuPL2tRf1pSnFtm28vVFcW&fid=0x0:0xe3981d8a9ad71da5"],"When":"2024-5-25"},{"Name":"M A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWtjemgVYBeaoLh3kqNTRMNip762xWWF_Yu_Wo8VBxi5HQjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Donair star is the best and they are moving just second store to west side of the current location.  Moving From 622  12 street to ( 628 12 street newest ) in couple of months most likely end of January 2025. With bigger place and sitting area inside during cold weather.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Only thing is parking which is very limited. [{"Name":"Wisa Nil.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkXG9YZ07iPb4Rgw-GoVzk323MIrdl33pwjT_E33MAGRMtWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"If you don't like sweet food, go away from this shop. Everything is so sweet. Firstly, I brought half and half of cheese and buldak flavor. Even the cheese flavor, It is still a little bit sweet, and buldak flavor is supper sweet but not spicy at all.

Then, I tried a second chance with soygarlic and Heak Buldak. Both make me disappointed. It's all still sweet, even soy garlic flavor, which is supposed to be salty more than sweet. Heak buldak also super sweet more than spicy.

All flavors like fried chicken coated with caramel. I'm not sure if I will be back to try something else.

Ps. Last time, I ordered sauce on the side, but they already mixed the sauce for me. [{"Name":"NôMāR Åltïçłöś","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKVyqW_kOlfqb-yGJ_Ks--LFkl55GXHpZ6S3YNX2dqaycCck_x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried this nice place in New Westminster that was recommended highly. Please change this. Take a name or give a number when placing the order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8adICqkRyDdIj8xP95wWBkb-F1Gl-vmfE6v6L&fid=0x0:0x8863030edcc337d5"],"When":"2024-12-25"},{"Name":"Aditya Ganjoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWpJnyIhPHCEbrHp3lldBFlE9nA6hEUFS5rwdA6WtnD68k9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my second visit to Chaiiwala, and I was very happy with my order. Everything was really good and I’m so excited there’s finally a good Indian restaurant serving more variety in the area. It’s also not too heavy on the pocket. The customer service was top notch as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoM2M5xBtCBd01RcGsYOPxLo3GMZfyS-wv24sQ&fid=0x0:0x8863030edcc337d5"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Jason York","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2KL5JJiTZL1QVt_3AcqILQXXBIuqDWdYOdj3lYENvavlAma6S8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"What a great franchise addition to New Westminster! The chai is quite sweet, but I'm told by my Indian friends that it is very normal in India.

Unfortunately not accessible entrance because of a couple steps.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhFLnfGG-TnL2b28-6mkB-OWuSePINzif-tOd-&fid=0x0:0x8863030edcc337d5"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Carmen Aboytes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCCLFKJlS62-34BUpujZzDsaZV9yysTxPBmk8fhCY7OoETeMyS6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The bowls and sandwiches here are super tasty – every bite is delicious! What truly stood out, however, was the outstanding customer service. The team's friendly demeanor, prompt service, and genuine care for their customers' experience made my visit truly unforgettable.

Kudos to the entire Chaiwala team for creating a wonderful experience! I highly recommend this gem to anyone looking for great food and exceptional hospitality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcIeWkj5aZsc3wx4mhFA1VNidLSzIlbmdWvwVj&fid=0x0:0x8863030edcc337d5"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Monica Aung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQuisHejduUWtxH28CK0sZCn-2Z2RMkUn2i3FrglGF1LMsgtjs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Their Karak Chai Tea is the best in Canada . user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alli L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7M-K_wMLVOHyWDXpjXXk3pyMIn-Cv8yGLpMXYPKQoyxLDNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tried this place for the first time today and was beyond disappointed. The food was not at ALL as advertised. I ordered the Nashville hot chicken sandwich, which was advertised to come with crispy buttermilk fried chicken, pickles, onions, truffle aioli, and iceberg lettuce.

What I received was a wet, soggy chicken breast on a wet, soggy bun. There was coleslaw/carrots instead of lettuce, there were no pickles on my sandwich, which is one of the best parts of a chicken sandwich. There were a few tiny chunks of diced onion in the mix with the coleslaw. And there was no truffle mayo either. The fries were also somehow completely wet and soggy.

I paid over $25.00 for slop and unfortunately did not get refunded. I do not recommend this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFa-AiBhNRJPZ_aWRdJc_bTImbiCeEALqEdEkB&fid=0x0:0x45bc8c7fe1685e53"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Theresa Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLecCztY_pXmy93BikSwe6M0XhZAjBKcATWBvCksY1zqc7aJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently went here with friends while we were in town for the Grey Cup.  The happy hour prices were pretty great,  the food was delicious, but the service was the best part! Our server Tracy was exceptional! She was friendly,  helpful, and treated us very well! We will definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLs6IW7OkXDNG_1x32NBJKHG0qD7nn4sWezhaZnNXJFbWqGcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Last night, we reserved a table for 16 people (family and friends for the family wedding this weekend). We were outside on the patio that was set up for us when we arrived.  Everything about the service and food and atmosphere was excellent.  Tracy and her colleagues were attentive and treated our bride and groom so well!
The wood fired pizzas were cooked to perfection, the beer was flowing and the cocktails were so yum.  This place was a great hit with our UK and Australian folks.
Tracy, your service, attention to detail and cheery smile was the highlight of our evening! You must have been so tired after the young ones left! Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Hatch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUe7DIzvoENQZ4GjCw_X6rw3ru2I8LVPZqfs82HioYw6dYMZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great! We were just in New Westminster for a night and needed a place for dinner. So glad we stumbled upon Howe Sound Taphouse. The smash burgers with bacon are the perfect size, and you can sub out the fries for an array of other options, like a caesar salad, soup, or poutine. Tracy was our server and she was top notch. Her recommendations were spot on and even gave us ideas of things to do on our road trip through western Canada. Give this place a try if you’re in the area. They will not disappoint! Oh and try the stickey toffee pudding with ice cream. So good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUha4uw8a4ALc1AAbzAulLyf7pPcko2YbFZc2Q&fid=0x0:0x45bc8c7fe1685e53"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Katherine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqeXJrpSHxfX8GE1npRfPdH-neJmrhomz_5TbH53kcZeP_LQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an awesome visit. The wings were fresh and delicious, it was a nice welcoming atmosphere but Tracy as our server was tremendous. So attentive, and so engaging.  I cross my fingers I get her as a bartender/server next time I come in!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lori Golden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6-VcfVSb5XiaNXuNybTZd8dFS8O8_6G4ifg6tWxwz1edWTIVr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a great experience at this location. Our server was absolutely amazing and I wish I could find my receipt that showed her name. She was very informative on all of our food and drink selections.
We had the pizza selection, the table was full of pizza and it was the best choice. Wildfire and great crust with a good amount of toppings. You could easily share the pizza with a friend or eat it yourself. We did decide to have dessert as it was house made and not brought in by bulk.  Cheese cake, wow! Simply devine. I'm allergic to the topping it came with and the chef was kind enough to make me a topping I could eat, that's above and beyond service. I highly recommend the pizza and cheese cake.
Great selection of beer, there is something for all tastes. Pop and cocktails available along with mocktails.
It has a really comfortable atmosphere but very Bar like. there is a patio but we arrived in a rain filled night so had to sit inside. It's clean and inviting.
Great location in new Westminster, if you're taking the SkyTrain it's right next to a station, Columbia I believe. If you're driving there is some parking out front. If not there is public pay parking a few blocks away.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had to see the New Howe Sound Brewing location in New Westminster. I enjoyed happy hour beer. It is still a comfortable community sports pub at its heart. The happy hour selection and food choices are good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5NXiS0BComNbFvti0ln9vMik4SamoRgUCGgpy&fid=0x0:0x45bc8c7fe1685e53"],"When":"2024-1-27"},{"Name":"Laura Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvFXX3bki0RGZbBISaWYaQdevOgHG4YwN6p2rh1Dtj-SGMLXEz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A week ago I was part of a group of 30 and we had a great time partying in the back patio area.  The weather cooperated and the staff reserved the upper patio area for us.  We had a smaller menu to choose from but there was still a lot of choice.  I enjoyed the Smash Burger and everyone seemed to enjoy their food as well.  Good beer and reasonable prices.  No complaints from anyone.  We had excellent service as well.  The pub has a compfortable atmosphere.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Afa Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhTgagBDdHz09XPRGJJA4c38TAv-F1f6HV90y0-8_ALLfJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a lovely little hidden gem in Victoria Hill! We went on a Friday and sat on the patio, which had nice big umbrellas for shade. Started with the White Blossom and Fennel Salad. Both very good and very well portioned!! The pizzas to follow were also very good. The ambience and attention to detail on both the food and decor makes this place exceptional. Can’t wait to go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5dPHNdYNHumoL0hIbzcJfr0IYyxZkaV8mvW8&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Beste Beksac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRHrZjQZ2Y7U8imEaoQIIwf8XpiwCv-hJrFmMIImXOYQ0KsPM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We loved everything we tried!
The Rocketman pizza had amazing ingredients and a perfect crust. The Lambada pide was super tasty, and the Tiramisu was perfectly balanced. We enjoyed every bite! We’ll be back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN34zPfPzgqIxZM4aEbND6Fy2SNohDflUN9mkM&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Thomas Cybucki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7aEXuW8hZrTVGQNEHTg42jfPaI_0ku-Xj046mhe9grmyBSnST=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying L'Onore, and it's one I've been wanting to try for a while. Didn't have a reservation so we were seated at the bar, which was just as good for the two of us.

My wife really enjoyed her Old Fashioned drink, I just had a beer on tap. We ordered the warm olives to start then shared two pizzas. The dough was fresh and had a nice, light crispiness just on the outside. Sometimes I find when we get this style of pizza from places, the toppings will be sparse. But we didn't feel that here, there was a good amount and definitely didn't feel like we were eating dough and tomato sauce. Loved the two we got (one was the Diavola),  and we definitely want to come back and try some other ones on the menu. Really enjoyed our dinner!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjBOfU_qNJ0Ks20bzlNO8bsBz7BxK8qQ8LJlvz&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Stephanie Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPpmqBG5uFjOO9zH3oPC1YLF3gyloafpU1sWsK191vkcK-dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There's pizza, and then there's PIZZA. This pizza is definitely quality over quantity. We got the Funguy and the Diavolo. The Diavolo was a masterpiece, a new combination of flavours that I had never tried before and we loved it. It was savoury, sweet and spicy.  The prices were very reasonable, and the two of us left feeling full and satisfied, but not bloated and regretful. The dining ambiance was really nice. I don't remember seeing a tv in there, and there was no super loud music either, which I liked a lot. It was relaxing and not overstimulating. Everyone working was friendly and took the time to acknowledge our presence. We will definitely be back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLhQJIWm1Mv9Qh1EaFViiHHpnj59FEEs3xb3N1&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"C B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU5ZahqHZDQJLqv2VLadq649JlqVkofuVk4HKRBFcswCnTXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This used to be my go to...but when my pizza arrives super soggy, not even cut...I will never order take out again. Eating in service is great, and when I called to let the manager know about items in my pizza that did not belong...he was great. Hopefully you can get back to what you were like when you first opened","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMxkggX2rk7x4xtwlrT7aa14dJEMC75XFFzwU96&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Grace Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJv2Qb5BK8BlHD8B-fNqpMIiwBP96of3n6s7qsHpu4xPXVSJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A friend suggested this place for a ladies night! Soooo good! Made fresh, very unique pizza names such as “unicorn” pizza with corn!! They have gluten free options too! The staff were very nice and the drinks were great too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQe0kI1Cj515tDGAurKUfc2R4kmW8Z0NWowYPf&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Larissa De Melo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXS7LlTvOBr91XzsML1fqci8yQw0llVT4I5YtVz_NTJfdC_iYlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good pizza, one of the best I've ever had in metro Vancouver. Tasty, fresh, good ingredients. The staff was friendly. Quite small space, but worth waiting a bit. Street parking is hard to find, but they have underground parking, entrance in the back (signage could be better for that).
Just wish the pizza was a bit cheaper so I could go back more often!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfdL-j3-NSSXhTGTO_2dObL2zA-DIFmBDo3mXt&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"TS OS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrxJ8Fjd3bGSI8mWbF186RbFWyg_DW73VTS3OIkFaxPfXFBEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Epitome of quality over portion size. This is one of my partner’s favorite pizza places. Atmosphere is cozy and our server was excellent. I personally liked NYCHEESE over ROCKETMAN. It is a very good pizza indeed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzyIRZJTLUQhDH2JmuP3CfoJ7_fJsT9RDJcFec&fid=0x0:0x4b89c8a772496c07"],"When":"2024-3-9"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered drinks, waffle nachos and wings. Although I enjoyed salt and pepper, I found the buffalo wings to be a bit soggy. I found the staff to be very friendly and attentive. I really recommend the place especially for late night drinks and snacks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2fY8JhX6tC_lC7BmtGZ0As0ZEByfCi163Fxhb&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Kate Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjE4MSAa0c4Uqc8iOt1LfqIkJDL1ULa2Z17gRh4YDWMExQ1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I heard they had a discount for people celebrating their birthdays so I decided to try this place out.

The place is big with lots of outdoor seating. Almost nowhere to park there except a few paid spots here and there.

When we came in we were greeted quickly and our server came to take orders fairly quickly as well. Then it all went downhill from there.

We ordered the prime rib medium rare. Although the color was great, the top of the steak was all dried from sitting there too long after cutting. The meat was also tough. The soup was broccoli and bacon and it was quite salty and the croutons were stale. We got the lattice fries which everyone raved about. The fries were ok but seasoning was only on a few.

We also ordered the seafood pesto fettuccine which claims it has lobster. It came with a lot of tiny shrimps and imitation crab. No lobster meat to be found. I thought for almost $30 for the pasta, there'd be some lobster bits. The garlic bread was good and the pesto sauce was delicious though.

When we were done, we wanted to get the bill and pay. Since this bar only allows one server per table, no other servers were willing to serve us. We waited over 20 min for our server to notice us looking at her. She was too busy at the drink bar making drinks. We got the bill, the -$30 was taken off for the birthday discount, we paid, and the server quickly just went away. No happy birthday or any goodbye greeting. She was just too busy.

Don't think we'll be returning here as regular customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMA5_-zgUj6YIJrCcdVvatTtnqiciOW39MU9G70&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Sandeep Patil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkfias45QhgRJ8x-jbidsLsdJf1V8WF5xtbY2Qhjx8BL_-hxwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located at convenient spot next to river Fraser and river parks, Kelly's allow you to relax down after a long walk by riverside of New Westminster. After soaking in the setting sun, watching trains pass over the river walk down in this Irish pub where attendants are dressed up to give the Irish vibe. You get plenty of cocktail options to choose from and while you are waiting for it you can solve the riddles on the menu card. The building gives a cabin feeling and always busy. The patio is another added advantage of this establishment where you can sip in your cocktail with potato skins while enjoying the cool breeze from river. Cost is okish compared to the location and vibe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQ-d34AOAzKeCK7Tu4DLiARxNpgZjeWWeOPG6j&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Madhukar Pathak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfDv7dCarikgkYCyK9sr2IdxEdH9H5SUBEbUg3puQPsZH5UJ3ADw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Loved this place !!
Been there couple of times already with a positive feedback each time.
Unfortunately, yesterday was not that time. The Lamb burger that was ordered had a hair in it. Thankfully it was noticed after one bite and the our Server was happy to change the order. But, that ruined the streak of great times in this pub.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAoGtTbSAczK4k3Cn_So460TdkXgXPL6_A8H6x&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Moira Casey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqH8ArDou9s_zoBtlaH2uA9ZPMDv3j1_WOTzaJd-UkxMhhAnEjxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food, drinks and service were all very good. Huge restaurant/pub with upstairs seating as well. Good place to meet family or friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9XlfaPyFUvinN_JsznCUYDLWF4l2fCXyxPPJq&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"kavya rawal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVF1Y6oHOVELURyrsxj6F02ztQQoo7vLbcyOfavbREk6dJ0XxFu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first time coming in for a birthday special. And everything was beyond expectations. literally the best vegetarian burger I’ve ever had. Onion rings were so fresh, and the strawberry mojito was just perfect. Our server Abbee was so friendly, walked us through vegetarian options and told us a little bit about the restaurant. Such a pleasant experience!
Fun fact: Building is 100 years old!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpbqYBfPmB15Lrka_gLShxv7bMQYfm-lmxMyD3&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"Champagne Kingdom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT9L6nbhgKeVF6uvC80gh6he8ZgVExYxBb0bRQFJovbeiruBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We visited Kelly O’Bryan’s in New Westminster and had a fantastic experience! The Irish restaurant/bar has a cozy atmosphere inside and is located in a beautiful building. We loved that they played great 90s tunes, even while showing sports on the screens. The prices for cocktails were also super reasonable. Overall, we highly recommend Kelly O’Bryan’s for a fun and relaxed night out!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leo Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhrqhlkToJU2ktCM__Ybm4QiDKDhUsqHcN5nJSXQE6aFyTEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First of all, I'm not a pub guy and I was there only for their b-day deal. It's really noisy but that's expected as it's a pub. Ordered their prime rib and the Cali club. Both were just mediocre at best. However, their fries were the highlight of the meal, I found that to be the most tasty out of everything we ordered.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKLhyhZ_sTbA2lhyf5q8aoM2jAxWwQSzxTk1YS&fid=0x0:0xb99a55913f8089e4"],"When":"2023-11-15"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Keith Eastcott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk5BCUEJh42hOpsF-_OoCCbmyygcrHIJcijMiuq6slKML49qmN0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow. This is such a great restaurant. They were decorated for Christmas. Lots of decorations. They had a live band playing and a dancefloor if the mood strikes. The server was very friendly and accommodating. Food was incredible, I had chicken Cordon blue. I definitely recommend you try this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-KmHrZDFI0-VhBZOXUQSN_UP4HLecc9GU1jNN&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stephanos is a family favourite. We've celebrated many birthdays, and even hosted a 60th birthday party for 100 guests.

The Greek food at Stephanos is consistently delicious. I'd highly recommend the calamari. It's light, crisp and satisfying.

When ordering for a crowd, order a couple of platters and add extra dishes on. The Dinner Platters for 2 and Starter Platters are served with large portions. The dinner platters are served with rice, potatoes and 2 kinds of salad. We typically order Greek and Caesar salad.

Guests are served fresh, hot pita bread, covered in melted butter. We love it!

It's the perfect spot for a crowd. There's plenty of seating, it's easy to make a reservation, and the dining room is always decorated for the season.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY7XnxOWvyltveugWn5_48exh9Cg7MlFafTjkE&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Julie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pd43YT5KSqkORSPaVbra7_KcodZ1kkwID5yaolZD_WuCOEiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We tried them and the service was excellent but the food was just OK. Most of us found it lacking flavour. We had beef souvlaki, chicken souvlaki which had no flavour, the roast lamb was good but nothing special, they had a lemon chicken rice soup that was decent and the Calamari was good. There was also an order of Teriyaki chick wings that were good. Nice wine selection and it was expensive for the quality of food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKnRCX1s5zmqNVWx8ryzLuJieShk5jGydzePDC&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Cari del Caribe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVm6firUBbVHSRlP2s4xiArkbddVcCCGxcWOmf78mRISiJv6uKo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Great service..everyone was friendly and our server was lovely. Their group set menu was of so-so value. We didnt receive a fair amount of appies per person. The calamari, my favorite food, was bland. I enjoyed their lamb and potatoes, but found the rice and salad a bit bland. Atmosphere was great with a good live band with a small dance floor.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"leesa tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsWaHyhzcw7kKPh9V3HkvTK5TTa81TdmCDp9IylYllx4puXIy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place to come to order some Greek food! Decent size portions for the price. I ordered the chicken souvlaki and calamari and it was good. If u come on Mondays, the souvlakis are on special. The one downside would be that I thought the service was a bit slow.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIbnswLcLLmNOwGpT0gOK4nmGmxRwjna12Wsgo&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2024-3-21"},{"Name":"Diamond","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJaYa4uYmCWK7gUfNjWoBc2J8Xa1ebQw8xU0_guCPQkbKY1RA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Shared the saganaki and the scallops & bacon. The saganaki was tasty! I had a delicious steak and one of our party had the combination plate with ribs, lamb chops and pan fried prawns. She said it was all good but she really liked the ribs! Nice atmosphere and clearly good for large parties as a group of 30+ came in and yet it wasn't too noisy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marnie Eudela-Umlas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg_gVRD_Hd9V3XIUh6_P71KHCryea9xsHYGqrZHTuXW_jdxEU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Our first time here as it was referred by a friend. We had a good time and we enjoyed eating and watching a band for a change. We wrote our requests and they sang some of it. Really had fun dancing to some songs too. Food was okay, I ordered my usual Greek favourite, Roast Lamb and it was smaller than normal. It’s okay but I am used too a bigger portion just like other Greek restos. We loved their desserts too and I particularly loved their Baklava. Place was huge, price is okay, service was good, washroom was clean and place was accessible. We will be back but maybe I will order the Calamari next time as it seems yummy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkimgrjQs_8ZK3yj5hQxENsOs0lOo5Jn-1J-D1&fid=0x0:0x6e194f0e51955461"],"When":"2023-2-19"},{"Name":"Dora Kardi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-Knh2tDf9afLFD1_6aKedelEDU8K1zCUli_fNkAg6_nYrrA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A wonderful experience at Stefanos! Great Service, Great Food, Amazing Ambience.  We loved the Christmas Decorations! The staff was attentive and made our evening very enjoyable.  Will definitely be back! Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Dru","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcIUWhXu36DJooUJ1lpbYjpqIkYmzEr706B1kzk2ckCpk9YfWe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is fresh, affordable and warm. I have been coming here for many years and I have always been happy with the meals they provide. My favourite menu item is the chicken platter. They give you a generous amount of protein. You can choose whatever vegetables and sauce you want with it. I definitely recommend trying their food :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNxAWJtLcNzcW398WP0klB_xU7aErAIDLxyM0_&fid=0x0:0xa60d8b2660cb370a"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"NAIMA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuoCNUx_8_-ZPwBeCP7vGRL0m5u3sU6Z2Qzwf3pY6Ced0lXV3K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried their food for the first time. The platter and the wrap was yummy. The wrap stuffing was really good but the outer bread was rubbery. Other than that everything tasted good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgVCDRJ4Ryr8FAE-GXknmGCXf7zrDncBjD4MS6&fid=0x0:0xa60d8b2660cb370a"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Alisha B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVgMlTN4oJ_Htiruh4fsD5lUN-XljwBfjL6ad3z1FmY77llA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Second time ordering, the food is pretty yummy except for the roughly 40 pounds of cilantro they put in the donair salad. Unfortunately there wasn’t an option to say no cilantro- which i find disgusting at the best of times - but either way, this is an insane amount of cilantro, which I didn’t get all of by any means, and I don’t recall there being any the first time we ordered. It was disappointing but I did come back because the food was tasty. Here’s to hoping the chef just tripped and dumped the entire stock of cilantro in by accident and not the norm!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1M31Zz-G8aDGbhE91yAdrqy3nRNzfglHVNHdT&fid=0x0:0xa60d8b2660cb370a"],"When":"2024-10-31"},{"Name":"Christopher Soltesz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwCdr1q4o4hRUHzAiDFyVvj2HQOVX7Dh5cS8YICujgTIHacg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beef platter is always good. I've been having takeout from paradise for almost 10 years and I still come back every so often to get that deal of platter and donair. (Pic I have eaten some of it already so that not the portion size)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCkux7fqLMp6kOgMa2RnF_-NZG6adAQz675EBR&fid=0x0:0xa60d8b2660cb370a"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Shahbaz Bedi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGZ4jaUmOO3IXLd0k-JF5n40w2tFxtazPEstIO3ihbc6ogXM2yVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited, and it was an excellent experience! The food was fresh, flavorful, and generously portioned. The donair meat was perfectly seasoned, and the sauces added just the right touch of sweetness and spice. The pita was soft and fresh, and all the toppings tasted incredibly fresh.

The staff was friendly and attentive, making sure my order was just how I wanted it. The service was quick, even during a busy time. The restaurant itself was clean and had a comfortable atmosphere, perfect for a casual meal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rhaymart Martirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoew8w-vlKn93HWxCSOgqLBUzhkhLkBx5zN4-lHNfYiHoFKgk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"“A Hidden Gem for Donair Lovers!”
I recently visited Paradise Donair and was absolutely blown away! The donairs were fresh, flavorful, and perfectly seasoned. The meat was tender and juicy, complemented by their signature creamy garlic sauce that tied everything together beautifully. The pita was soft and warm, and the fresh toppings added a nice crunch.

The service was fast and friendly, and the portion sizes were generous—definitely great value for the price. The restaurant itself had a clean and welcoming vibe, making it a perfect spot for a casual lunch or late-night craving.

If you’re a fan of authentic donairs, this place is a must-visit! I’ll definitely be coming back for more.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Dohm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJvWw0x7JFY_wD0o-wjjXD0OvULsEuKr8Em6tfR8uHYQ_llQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a regular for a long time and I would like to mention how great Melis is. She is always warm and does the best service possible. She knows I’m careful about cleanliness so she always goes above and beyond to make sure I’m eating my food without any doubts in my head.
