[{"Name":"Shawn Gale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt7ZcqBuTGbnxvR30S4a6N938p_TbyxARKKVRuZFB29uQM13f_Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This tap and bistro blew me away, The Notorious Grey Fox, site of the old BC Penitentiary. My wife and I visited here for the first time last Friday. We were unsure of what to expect, since we'd only seen the location from East Columbia. From that vantage point, it's hard to judge. We caught happy hour before 5pm and enjoyed amazing food. In particular, the chips and salsa, which was next level salsa made in house. Also, always a good indicator of service, the coffee was fresh and in a large cup, which they were quick to refill. I highly recommend visiting here. I know we'll be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9XJQ2PaH7iqt-PPcxNGkue7PjK7ED3wThDY-R&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Nathan Woods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYlKwIGO9PHjqLgc7mRGN7qYIzJ_Yb1JOij4343pL12ye4fG4D-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I've seen many iterations of a pub here, I was hoping this would be better...

Sat on the beautiful balcony, a fair beer selection. I had an IPA and Ma had a white wine...

Looking over the menu we both realized that there really wasn't a wide variety of food here.

I ordered the beef dip in the pepperoni flatbread.

Initially looked good, the bread was crusty but soft still. A little too much of their house horseradish on top. I would have preferred a nice little dish of this on the side so that I could load it at my discretion. The fries were tasty...

Ma, she wasn't impressed at all with the pepperoni flat bread. She said that it was bland and doughy...

I'll keep an eye on the menu, see if anything ever changes there. I wouldn't return for a meal, but I would have a beer there...

It is great they allow 🐕🐶 on their patio!

***Edit***

It's truly unfortunate that this place also replies, without ever really addressing the concerns.

Clearly, the respondent got their feeling hurt in life and they feel the need to be cutting in their replies. My review was an opinion, their response only tells me to not bother looking again at the menu, and to scratch this off as a place for a beer.

I'll wait for the next iteration of a pub here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1yMOMB9dKgCe1JdsqPRs61B68LUjVME3NSmy2&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A great pub located in New Westminster. Fun place to watch sports on one of their many screens. Great happy hour selection on food and drinks. Spacious inside seating and patio seating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJKlxjM-cdlDjkSNjNjgqjYGqo7sQIEfH6hhg8&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Todd Hodgins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW72ymeCGuxhZLuxllkGl5JZOyyu8tehQoStTIzhCVPdDgNDg8L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Hidden gem for sure, but unlike some places that you secretly want to keep to yourself, this is one you want to tell friends about. Rarely do I give full ⭐️ across the board, but I honestly couldn’t find anything wrong that I would prefer differently.
May if there was more beer selection, but the offering are sufficient and satisfying. The food is good “pub grub” with excellent flavors and choices.
Beef dip was superb, and the other sandwitch was a similar to a chicken parmesan with roasted veggies.
All good and definately worth the 15min wait. See you all soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODcFKcVQ8YeMfN_X0_rJWrmepmD45yBv-T5aWa&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Deanna Faist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsw4e9O1Zs9NjjHCt7DbI8rfBTkpUfZAGRh-70AWaPxUbEOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just stumbled upon this place by chance and what a delight! A cozy pub situated in a beautiful location, with excellent service and fantastic food. I got the chicken waffle sandwich with Caesar salad and the portions were perfect. Nice laid back pub atmosphere with good music and decor. There's hints of that "newly opened" vibe going on, but in an endearing way. Would definitely come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1OhKEmYWZAHNxOQWOys2YpHsyZTx0AbOypyxg&fid=0x0:0xd4bcafa0fd8a8964"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"Hana Tahaei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPsL8cPlTSK6C764cOFzHTu3aphjcYexQvAlc-d378XW7qNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing atmosphere, wonderful staff, and delicious food! Thank you very much for the fun memories! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWO71O-6vtxy0oWqlkgMTL_1fXX0zuePLUhWltL9zkToFe7FadaGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"OPEN!!!

[{"Name":"Regine Aragon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKJwfF8kCTrctxyjmRXYzpqQhsFMeyiHCRIOVgnwQwo-P8I_I7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's so good! Generous serving size, great customer service. 🙌

I've been living in the area for almost 2 years. I can't believe it took me this long to try this place. Definitely adding it to my regular New West eats.

Just wish they had more space for seats.

*Note: photo is of a regular chicken shawarma platter","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqlCqJB8cl_GFob-7vSwj8Os20pDjPF3uFaAtM&fid=0x0:0x86639338529f658a"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Clara Chau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoMWRC0cDGP4nCpQ1_Zdm86daXS0A0KJbVAa9QczqqbfD7fWIZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were told by friends that this place had really delicious platters and it was an amazing experience! It was our first time here and decided that we couldn't go wrong with the "special platter" which had chicken, lamb, and falafels. We noticed right away that the falafels were made fresh to order and was still crispy by the time we got home (we did take out as there are only 3-4 seats at the front). Beside the fryer was a large pot of fresh rice sitting on the stove as well. For salad you can choose to have a little bit of everything (lettuce, pickled beets, cucumbers, tomatoes, tabouli, pickled red onions, and pickles). They had hummus and tzatziki sauce as options and after the meat was piled on you are also given more sauce options (hot sauce and tahini). They also offer pita to compliment your meal (great with the sauces). This platter was enough to feed two and we'll definitely be back again to try the desserts.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK6DRK4bxWIOiSF65jJ0IFzYy5FOI9ASwAnUWY&fid=0x0:0x86639338529f658a"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Reimun Shleimun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJu0ZwA_4D35g6GEfkag5GeVQ67VwDP2OSszt_p0L2T_fRSmw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time in! Was delicious… Me and wife had chicken wrap, and also tried falafels and rice with chicken. Was amazing every bite. Chicken was Very tender and juicy! Falafels were delicious as well. You can tell freshness by what was offered. Will definitely be back when in the area. Atmosphere and service was great as well! Ty guys, keep it up :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKW5w42WrvL7_LF1bl9N7ZUyRWQELQB94sf_qh&fid=0x0:0x86639338529f658a"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Mohammed Yahya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLT1QQjsQL0cVBO4YH4tgQfBRBthb4gM79UjFdzAIKyKZVPkA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I tried theirs regular size chicken wrap. The size and chicken portion was good 4/5. Cleaning 5/5. One thing i didn’t like is the service. Poor service 2/5. Everything was ok. I recommend it 👌🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPACmszEZm-wCmsfkJQHhHn6Ll5UkR3q8wPWICx&fid=0x0:0x86639338529f658a"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Denis Santos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF32K7mKkPkKCpGUSEjmRXhqYloH84bwlSW6sQJ_X-vjOnAtXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best shawarmas places I tried. This is a very small joint located at upper part of new Westminster. The portions are very large considering their prices.  They have a range of veggies and sauces you can choose from and they are fresh. So many options on the menu and all the time you can find seasonal options👏👏👏","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Remia Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmpY-11b6uW1ElYcP-MQ3nN5fllulzAmTZx7kDqDgJ0KRRYIkH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My food was so good I never want to come back, I had such a great experience that I’d never want to experience my food cooked poorly. I had an amazing breakfast. I was more than extremely impressed by my food! Usually when I go to chain restaurants I am not usually impressed but my food was wonderful. This was my first time eating at de Dutch.

I would love to go back and I will only go to this location as long as whoever made my food still works there. They should get a raise. [{"Name":"Shmaggiez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVltXubsS28Ti6Fh0XdvEYqxCU1nuQ0Ffk3FfU2JQ-rizdlwXK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Super cute little restaurant with very filling food. The burgers were amazing and I loved the yam fries! Delicious apple pie milkshake too","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMB-vakx72wtFvOKwocI9PCdYz-d5xCcEXwaEst&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Eliza Kko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwoyeWKfgWQNFxWps1CjAwTSHlOvp2SgfrfG_JfKWQ8Pu33Anvbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The atmosphere was lovely, and the service was excellent, but unfortunately, the burgers were not to my taste. It was the first time I found myself unable to finish a meal, which was disappointing. I genuinely tried to find something positive about the burger, but it just didn't work for me. It's unfortunate, especially since we had chosen this cafe to celebrate my fiancé's birthday.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNY2ZMkcDO-hh02QsOd0DXzqgW7jSLVrf22URTZ&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Jamie Barker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpp3gr1K3Pd6nLcJQDJ35I3vRCKNDaw6zsuAeJ-l2q45KXcT8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We showed up at noon and were greeted with a friendly smile and a "welcome, how are you 2 doing today. " We were seated and given menus, asked what we wanted to drink and left to figure out which yummy burger to eat. There are so many great ones,sometimes it is hard to decide. I ended up getting the Hawaiian burger w/wedges and the wife got the Greek God burger w/loaded wedges which has Cheese and bacon added. I also got the gravy that comes on a stand with a candle underneath to keep it warm. Great Food, Great Service and Great Atmosphere. I have been going there for about 35 years. Everyone should try this place at least once.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkneFx3c_QLPGSQS9Wo41DYEZu9g225WdIBunZ&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"Gordon Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnOHfHwIw8kjctiKh-90eXmGbeJxpWdlmu9akMh5nixHMR0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An amazing little burger joint. The portions are definitely worth the price! I got the Insanity Burger and had to take half home. The only thing that could make this place perfect would be to serve Coca Cola. I will definitely be going here again for more insanity!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwCTIMOgc1ycL8lUiXJrZorQfR6Ivkz2qdbZXx&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Vanessa Mckenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-K9hBL7FvaAVpoj9V0DxVZ2oJ_XPHr6voSvjc5WJQ__VCUlaw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A must If you are looking for a burger restaurant.
To me, portions are big (I don't eat that much), but it is worth the price. You cam Pickle between salad or potato wedges.
There's a shame and fame wall for all those who can eat an 8 patties high, 3 pounds burger (if you dare).
Service was nice even though it took a little for our burgers to be served.
Despite that, everything is delicious, but the place needs a little bit of an upgrade. We paid 60 dollars for 2 burgers and tips.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2lk4lommzANYkXop1_nSRHCiM-yBDcoImy_5z&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Jamie Coo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMtT8SYH3ODglSdZyhsIz5N_cesns6jNpwE2VJCXq0WPBgF9EA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here on a regular Sunday night, the shop is busy but we still managed to get a table right away. The atmosphere is quite cozy, the walls are decorated with photos of their patrons which makes it quite homey. The servers also seemed very down-to-earth and friendly, which definitely added to the whole homey vibe.

We ordered the Insanity Burger and the Chicken Wings with Mango Habanero Sauce & Ranch dip to share between two people.

At first glance the price seems a little steep for a burger, but the portion definitely justifies it. The Insanity was a huge burger with the buns substituted by a full grilled cheese sandwich. For a sense of scale, half a burger is way larger than a regular burger on its own. The burger itself was good. The grilled cheese was simple yet it is everything you expected - crispy bread, cheesy center, and the patty was done well, flavourful and juicy. With that said, I found the 4 layers of bread a little too much carb for the burger's proportion, so we ended up eating the top "bun" separately. Needless to say we were STUFFED after the meal. The wings are pretty standard, what you will expect at most pub-restaurants. The sauce is sweet and tangy with a bit of kick but not too special.

Overall, a very decent place for some specialty gourmet burger. I would definitely be back to try the other burgers on the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-5Cymi9Fa4Vx6aTOC6-1qHxJ1bipABZDNlPuE&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2024-4-14"},{"Name":"Arvin Tirk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYh2FT5cCPc0ARnWSgClckRe_ibZeJioJnK0VkkynD8VXZilEl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We got quite a few recommendations from people around and even google reviews were good. So we went here for the B’day celebration and ordered three Burgers and two free flow coffees. Nice ambiance, nice decor, loads of photo collages of previous customers, and we liked it. Hostess told us we have options for sides: Wedges, Salad, or Onion rings. She did not mention that Onion rings would come for extra price. This came as a shock to us when we saw the receipt later.
Favorites of the day on the board were super expensive.
Our burger plate looked beautiful. Crispy potato wedges, but they were cut a little too thick. So, that was a bummer.
Burger patty was roasted well but it had that meat smell and also was bland with the meat’ish taste. Something has to be figured out that the patties are flavorful and doesn’t have that raw’ish meat taste & smell. We had to add more and more ketchup and sauce to make it flavorful. This experience did not match with the recommendations and hype we got about this restaurant before our first visit.
Just to be clear, we have been to more than 15 countries and have tasted good burgers. We know how a good burger should taste like. If there’s a raw’ish meat smell and taste in the patty, then it needs improvement.
I hope cooks will pay attention to this constructive feedback. Maybe we’ll return in the future, but not sure if we’d be willing to pay the high price.
Our kids got candies while going out, so that was nice!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKAdoGyMDW1Nb9wxgVbCbgWw3wTyKIvss0pXEf&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2024-4-7"},{"Name":"Jennifer Sujin Jeon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2x7NBj_j-gLckp-nciIaSNSNBBYb6sz_fmEYIT-PfK8Z62Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a famous handmade burger restaurant in New Westminster. It has a long history with a cozy atmosphere and retro sensitivity. The food is generally large in volume, and it's really delicious. We had a really happy time. I highly recommend this place to you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcB92jZ1iiJgYumFBtSOAFkMvISDKbaVDGjYsC&fid=0x0:0x658604f2a36fde58"],"When":"2023-6-14"}]

I was already on the Skytrain or else I would have turned back and ask for it to be done properly.  I wouldn't go back to this location,  staff looks disinterested in giving customers a good experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXWCYgNnWA1NdJVI4tHHUJYUo4wDLMW5-HIzVG&fid=0x0:0x900ebbb76bdeb92e"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"M A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJk5fsjA3O0DPAe75HOZMp7mkuGkp5tDJh59URPRnoDQbgWstr5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I used to think I understood why people liked this place— donair Dude seemed like the best and healthiest option compared to other places near the SkyTrain. It was my go-to spot whenever I needed to grab "fast food" .But after yesterday, I’m done. This was the last time I'll get food from here. The staff don't seem to care about what they’re putting on the plate. Instead of proper food, they just fill it with oil. Look at how much oil was in this small dish!
Very disappointed","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8DibmjGxdGc1bBrAybS2dJHjLorU01Iw3K239&fid=0x0:0x900ebbb76bdeb92e"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Eliana Ducuara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJC0eaJxUQG_lYzV3i7gZQvL8DP80igRyXW0Yh2qGazYSOSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely the Lamb Donair Platter was super delicious, but Felipe Lobos' service was excellent, so we will return","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMH5x2Qjv8_r4Hpw6EqWqFMaKMl2b82vpbwnew1&fid=0x0:0x900ebbb76bdeb92e"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Marion D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-10rsPncDnDxeEHrrNFufuXBiSk_1Fp_0XaXkBZDfbvlt0R04=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered large chicken donair (bogo) via Doordash. Very minimal filling and sauce and super dry pita. It took several bites through dry, hard pita to get to the tiny bit of filling in the middle, then still lots more dry, hard pita left that I threw away. Very unsatisfying. Probably the worst donair I have ever had. Judging by their reviews, this seems to be a common complaint. I tried the second one because so much of the first was thrown out. It was obviously made by someone else. It had more filling but not more chicken (minimal). The toppings, i.e. onion, pickles, etc. were add in individual spots, not throughout the pita, so one mouthful was all onion, then another was all tomato. Overall just really bad and I do not recommend this place to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJYsqsfylRWb2qB-xJh6bN2jntU-d5BqDo5FMP29y23P0aTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was passing by and decided to try the donair at this location.

The shop is inside the sky train plaza passed Safeway.

Service was very good, fast and friendly.

Donair was not the same as the downtown location but it’s not bad. Depends on your taste I guess.

However this location does not have Beef meat and no pepper spread, which is disappointing. They only have Chicken and Lamb.

Since they were honest about it I won’t be taking any stars off!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOx20Z2Q-LYmVbYykybuYzFSGVY_Cr8kU1VYVR-&fid=0x0:0x900ebbb76bdeb92e"],"When":"2020-12-17"},{"Name":"Andrew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaltkSlV2VF0VRW4xbCvizkdd1bWD5fhF0YOg4DxXeF9PcOn4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going here since it originally opened. Chicken pita is my go to as I enjoy the sauces and the just eight doneness of the chicken. The pita is finished in a sandwich iron which gives it an extra crunch.

Dec 2023: The shop is reopening after a fire. Everything is repaired. Do give some courtesy to the staff in training. Help a local business get back on their feet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6wsz8qflZUv2IuNzOEbdGt0bemV0dXkjc4Sh1&fid=0x0:0x900ebbb76bdeb92e"],"When":"2023-12-28"},{"Name":"Nicole P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_hMBqVmPn-ivShuVmEj9Fd6wPI7TJMIizPn7HJ9DiKb9e4ew8dg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food, super fresh. Yesterday was their first day open at this location and it went off without a hitch! Our family had rice plates and pitas. The pita deal was excellent and the pita itself has huge compared to other places we've gone. We specifically drove out to try this new location. Staff was super friendly and owners were there. There was a bit of a line but they went through the line really fast. Great service, great smiles and great food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYPHw225zvgx5V8hc8byMj_-WOXNO__PGKTCBp&fid=0x0:0x900ebbb76bdeb92e"],"When":"2018-6-10"}]

[{"Name":"Personal Coach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhqstV1InAkU4YOtXhoy5_IdbmLI1Ia3Xrxh6VaLMEccCUFBRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Great Find. Real Mexican Food, Fresh Made Pico de Gallo (Salsa). I had the steak dinner w potatoes and salad.
All extremely good. Friendly Service. Great prices. Will return. Recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWSg3MdBAkdqS8SyBRSPG1WAIgkCMeEfQDN00P&fid=0x0:0x17754bb1b88a4001"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Gagan Ghumman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvNrtNON_FeLzpzPMPt2ekwfF3UFwVthowrQjtk6nFa4CG8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The veggie burrito was a flavor-packed delight—filled with a hearty mix of seasoned beans, sautéed peppers, fresh avocado, and crisp lettuce, all wrapped in a warm, soft tortilla. Each bite was vibrant and satisfying, with the perfect balance of textures and flavors.

The veggie nachos were just as impressive—crispy chips piled high with melted cheese, beans,veges all topped with creamy guacamole and tangy sour cream. Every chip was loaded with goodness, making each bite a delicious and satisfying treat.

This veggie meal was a true feast for the senses, proving that plant-based options can be just as indulgent and flavorful as their meaty counterparts.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOU_81paW1kJ8n78aRXtVX5kvbg2fnWzt1qqJwS&fid=0x0:0x17754bb1b88a4001"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Carmen Aboytes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCCLFKJlS62-34BUpujZzDsaZV9yysTxPBmk8fhCY7OoETeMyS6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Come by on the weekend to try the best birria from 10 AM to 3 PM (not 100% sure on the closing time). Get there early because by 10:30 AM, there's usually a line, but it’s so worth it. The menu is simple: birria, quesabirria, drinks, and dessert. Definitely a spot you don’t want to miss!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM39v6TbScP7LcT331VPqxMicfOS11BNwK7x8g6&fid=0x0:0x17754bb1b88a4001"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"KULVIR KAUR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYtj4vBjeTKkByNvaZmuRhxNuc34z4KaUTwMHvV21acFTUIJPi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was decent mexican food but my expectations were really high from this place. The owner was a funny guy and he made us laugh a lot. I would say if you want less spicy mexican food, this is the place to go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBPMZZlnT8yLk6MrbGtkgLL9f1pBocEi-pG8G9&fid=0x0:0x17754bb1b88a4001"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Bob Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlQlhpa1SNwfStyGzOzqbfoT-oWcTX3JDyUr80Xt5Q5hyMwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything about our experience at this place was phenomenal. The ambiance was lighthearted and fun. Most importantly, the food... I don't even have the words to describe just how good it was. From the first to the last bite, it just kept impressing me. Definitely will be coming back every chance I get.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzZ6_7M1dIT592BwBaXrBd9GcfXmLWOipd6_rI&fid=0x0:0x17754bb1b88a4001"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"F DV","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHm8fUUESZ36eo-0l6OHPFqwHgjC6fOfsNYfNI2-NWBK_nf24=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic experience and food was really good. Love the ambiance and of course the owner is very friendly. Would highly recommend coming here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxSMh6ypmwV0y7JqHxiI15-3xR3L1jy7XDLiln&fid=0x0:0x17754bb1b88a4001"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Anita Navarrete Baker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrzBc5f9_I5ooCiE4lRxbYgQi2vAQoscKKfYYNp_IOdobPBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really cute place, Authentic dishes, well flavored, Owner is super sweet, makes sure your taken care of.  My husband is from Mexico and he approves the Flan desert is amazing! Definitely should check it out!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Celina Arenillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPvcNqjpmtihcb5J8miFlC4lw0H-EdaSQUtLM4u3kh0_GMHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We ordered nachos, flautas, and a plate of pork carnitas. The nachos was different because of the white cheese instead of your usual cheddar. Flautas were served warm. However, the carnitas meat tasted a bit old.

Price point was good because it was affordable. Homey ambiance. Service was friendly.

Overall, it was just okay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUUGxRCDMrXnuiuBBm_sVX9LU_bXhOitH6Rayh&fid=0x0:0x17754bb1b88a4001"],"When":"2024-3-17"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The restaurant was very empty around 8pm weekdays so I was a bit cautious when I walked in. However, they're better than our expectations, especially at a very affordable pricing. We shared a couple dishes and I would recommend their tempura udon on a cold night, hearty & clean flavour. Their tempura batter was very thin & crispy, tempura weren't oily at all. The salmon & avocado roll was simply good. Tbh, I don't like the beef teriyaki due to sweet marinate but each of their own. Our waitress was very nice and efficient, and the restaurant looked clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDg5jZ9-2VRk-sO9XRE_r58lwOkM0vrdD20NYf&fid=0x0:0x3f97299220d84818"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pleasantly surprised by how good and fresh the sushi is here. We ordered two sashimi dinner combos for $21.95 each to go and it was quite amazing. It came with so many different food items for a fixed price and the portions were great. It saves you from ordering items which are more expensive individually if you are craving different things.

Our dinner sashimi combo came with a choice of terriyaki chicken or beef (we chose the chicken which had great flavour and fire wok vibes), you can then also choose 2 out of 3 of gomae, agedashi tofu, or chicken karaage, and you also get assorted tempura that was crisp and freshly fried with shrimp and pumpkin and more, a bowl of rice, a bowl of miso soup, and assorted sashimi with tuna, salmon, and surf clam, and 4 California rolls! It’s a great meal and deal!

Everything was packaged so perfectly and with care to go! Loved it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4sXCsAkrEGFYOvBpWI8up3dZvgSYth7DTbSzj&fid=0x0:0x3f97299220d84818"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"Paul Chun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3ITFMkRjux6RalFJQWUV3IMb22ncsLJJHhwjW3LK2G-wT2e7P=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sweet and tender texture of the fish and meat comes well together. Try crispy shrimps that still hold all juice inside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMokqKlPclk0bPSliZuvlT6W-slrk58s_t2OnBu&fid=0x0:0x3f97299220d84818"],"When":"2024-2-4"},{"Name":"Ro The Artist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPRGpSz5k6TBY-Jzwb0atPYYwnJkcdimPwAx5Kg-jHm18YMeZ0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very welcoming place & staff are very sweet. Easy access for everyone and including those with special needs. Good is amazing and you can even see it being made.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMn5fkwQ5FmRX0kYHVocPJAW2QLJ57t1Am9wOP5&fid=0x0:0x3f97299220d84818"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Leah Thompson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCXYB9oK-Z06SZU_lzEywuCtZ1xfJTSwFkSkz9M0cjkDO58Ok=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m new to BC and this is the best sushi I’ve had in Canada. I really like the real crab California rolls and their chicken karage is quite good. It’s usually pretty empty there, but I think most people do take out like me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Hwang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXM8uHkSNQ1f67I6kzgiBGArFLjuzwkTWQKJg_2bHlV9k1h7-rn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Three of us visited for lunch, and from the time we entered until we left, there were no other customers in the restaurant. Although it was a bit unsettling, we decided to order the Sashimi Bento, unifying our choices. I was surprised to see the rice served in this manner, especially when not ordering a Teriyaki Bento. The reason for choosing the Sashimi Bento was to consume fewer carbohydrates, but I couldn't help but think it would have been better if they included a few pieces of California roll. Unfortunately, there were no side dishes to accompany the rice. The plating is not up to expectations. Even with only three people dining in the restaurant, there was inconsistency in the size of the tea cups and soy sauce dishes. I find it hard to comprehend the high review ratings. While the food was not bad, there is a need for significant improvement.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7YgnFB9EW_pTLXCoemU99xohfqAG7AiCg3HJ-&fid=0x0:0x3f97299220d84818"],"When":"2023-11-23"},{"Name":"Buddcar Cook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXaSQFmbpqRD6ou7Yd8oGS4KxIWfsJLLYZ6hajlWJ0_J7klXKT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent place. Great service and good food. Had Monkey Brain sushi.Tasted fantastic and really good presentation. Go in and ask what's in it.Also had the Udon soup with beef,well presented and tasty. Prices are average.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWFotHfGlxUBJ6g9keiu6A2eKBC27tpSTz7DCZ&fid=0x0:0x3f97299220d84818"],"When":"2022-6-15"},{"Name":"Angela Jeffery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtGyld6d4wIU2Lb7oe7xsoiq4r77iaBdF6nkFQ8ek01eF1q7c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Restaurant seems nice. We got take out, and saw many other take out orders.
Portions were a bit small but good quality. The miso soup was creamy and had nice big pieces of seaweed. We ordered a variety of nigiri and had their House roll (regular tuna instead of spicy), which they easily accommodated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzbpLBxEk0sLnOLPXTHrF035RoTOckJwNmcoC4&fid=0x0:0x3f97299220d84818"],"When":"2019-12-9"}]

[{"Name":"Aom Hildebrand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqzk0-t2eCJ3dWbzxrmO1EFkEGk94crNKQpEhBC-DrbexpqzAYfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always saw the good reviews about this place. Finally, we made it there. Really friendly service from a lovely thai girl who gave us a warm welcome. Really delicious food, fast service, nice portion with good price and a nice patio outside on a sunny day. Thank you very much again for a free rice for the girls and a free thai tea for me, very kind of you! So this is our favorite thai restaurant in New Westminster","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPu60Uycdsw92ldW-aM9QpU-FF3pgrV3Ijx1E8H&fid=0x0:0x391decfdfda73afa"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Maggie Chanthavong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyXv5niwBMXAQ3mUqyO5AV_LwAAx8y2zeLrzmI5BuBRxMJsTY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great experience!! Great tasting food, quick eat and reasonable prices make this restaurant our new favourite!! The outdoor patio allowed our pups to enjoy a little snacky snack with their mama after a long nice walk on the pier. Great service and the atmosphere are on point 💯","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNO_rJr-A_m6FN2tEt5XEzQGHKQTDNBWV4IscVS&fid=0x0:0x391decfdfda73afa"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Nate D. Suppanade","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT5GIFT3fWisDu-ffUjuVaDyKrj5NqWSJjl9Ok7m5pMmYxWgpmJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cute little shop with a nice outdoor seating area, good food, good service. Can't here one afternoon and literally everything on the menu sounds fantastic. They were sold out of the squid dish that sounded most appealing to us. We ended up ordering the mee gorang and a couple of beers. Sat outside and the view was lovely. The mee gorang was really good, I would definitely order it again! They have a self serve water station and a few kitchen items to buy in their market. I use the same Thai tea they will here at home, and the fish sauce as well! Overall great place, I would love to come back to try more things!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGj5EELt9xyOPYj9T5PH3x4g6pjy8MnyVLF92h&fid=0x0:0x391decfdfda73afa"],"When":"2024-7-11"},{"Name":"Lashesbybrailyn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuWEu80YRuqkbzllMoFQQzGglp1IKFrxju518Sq8zkcr353ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Longtail Kitchen is one of my favorite spots for pad thai! I’ve lost count of how many times I’ve ordered from here, and it’s always amazing. The flavors are spot on, and the balance of spices is perfect every time. Whether I’m dining in or getting takeout, it never disappoints. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Island Girl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbJGwIG62aQA1csb4fnlABcLNnj_cBRZiqDGK6Io0jurINt5-pag=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So glad that we found this Gem for Thai food. Taste was amazing and the proportions were pretty good. We would definitely comeback to enjoy the taste. Today we came here with no expectations just to have Thai Food, but definitely this was amazing choice. We had pad Thai and Basil beef.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bruce Luu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRaf1m45VYyCGlp50uH-2rHvYNM9RdGoAjp3PIAgLWyz7pPnyN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good wings that were crispy, salty, sweet, not very oily. Delicious tangy pad thai, the prawn was cooked perfectly. And the chicken was very flavorful. Service was very kind. The only gripe i would have is that the cook time was 20 minutes, but they were busy, and for good reason. 100% would recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdipDzbbJRgbP48nWrmB6er7P_CVyNcEgjg9rK&fid=0x0:0x391decfdfda73afa"],"When":"2024-2-17"},{"Name":"Jovian Radheshwar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6BkKosIXRpD5joim3nwn-X1T2-d4Cr3EfNh_jlxmEWtj8eefUUA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best restaurant in New Westminster. Their food is art.

Everything on the menu is amazing. Gluten-free options. Very spicy and delicious. And nutritious!

Honestly Longtail Kitchen is better than every restaurant in the entire Vancouver region, and is better than much more expensive places, too.

This is what food is supposed to be.

♥️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUuG3e1CIxNISfRzsOThLipZmQbNFXZ2rfmBKx&fid=0x0:0x391decfdfda73afa"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Youngeun Julie Oh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGqMG7wX3bWe0FCTqZQmeWgxKuqmTFP56OGgQy2z38HaPrGOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I fell in love with this place on my first visit. I've tried gailan with pork, pad thai, pad see ew beef, fried enoki, daily curry, and mee goreng. They were all amazing. The place is clean and people are nice to the customers. I once came here three times a week. Their limited business hour is thw only flaw.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObHVTKS3hsAkxNMUbbeDGIKHzGbWRkfnmcOtwF&fid=0x0:0x391decfdfda73afa"],"When":"2024-4-23"}]

[{"Name":"Jackie’s Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUszzOqI_r931gkNL0kGramN4TG_x4gsqPklTIBKTOEpgOmyBOj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small but very tasty. Came in at a weekday lunch time and it was packed, given that this place is for a quick bite in the subway attached mall, table turn over was fast. First of all the service was extremely warm and family-ish nice. Strongly recommend the boiled dumplings, it’s out of this world. Dan Dan noodle and the sizzling oil noodle are as exciting as you’re eating overseas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1AnWwNse_R4YEn_5vNCaZFK6k1NWNbPfGHush&fid=0x0:0xaeda9401ede2ba0d"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"Marie Su","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVTjd4tommTaPgE5hMHV85zCR6h__alpO_s2dVPHMuv0RGNc78=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the most delicious dinner here! Came here curious for the handpulled and handcut noodles and they were amazing amazing. Chewy, spicy (not too much) and also a large portion. good bang for the buck.
Unfortunately our stay in Vancouver is ending soon, otherwise we would immediately come back to try the other options on the menu☺️
The staff was super friendly and even let us stay a little bit longer than their usual opening hours 🙈💗 this place will be a reason for us to come back to Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdV--n8rCKXvYXCgpAMGiQv0b2spTOhF_Ocz17&fid=0x0:0xaeda9401ede2ba0d"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Elim Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXylBjyg1c-6jnckttIQfKw8KdxF2vyIJh_ldP8bjS9Gwia62gW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The restaurant is just outside the skytrain station gate, so it is very convenient for people who take skytrain. The food was delicious. Another benefit for my son is he can watch the trains come and go and never feel boring.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKhTwq07Oog3t9UShfrrUrElMajv4MqCzn4232&fid=0x0:0xaeda9401ede2ba0d"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Luke Weng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn1tdfwXfRnZVszKV8bZBNwooyRqfHv0VT8T0EAQWyUrqTrrO6aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I've always passed by this restaurant and was curious to try. I'm quite satisfied. The price was pretty cheap and the customer service was pretty good for a Chinese restaurant.

The vibe from inside is a little cramped, different than what it seems from outside (a Shaolin restaurant 😂) but it was still quite comfortable.

The only thing is that the kitchen took a long time with our order. We waited nearly 15 minutes for noodles with sauce on it. Meanwhile our friends were already finished eating. That part was not cool. But we'll give them the benefit of the doubt.

Next time I'll come when I'm not pressed for time (and definitely not with 15 ppl)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKWI9RCBGcSn5rhza6ha2ZRNRP0Un6Q0wL-M5I&fid=0x0:0xaeda9401ede2ba0d"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Christine Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkB4dvOmGlgUXv4nPa1bFiSBAzjpEWbU0k5_3eMXMgA7r07DZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The noodles were pretty good, but I found the dumplings to be a little mushy (yummy, but lacking in texture). Portion sizes were larger than I expected and they do takeout and sit in. It’s a cozy spot for lunch, and I would come here again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCn-LL0p41xNUtLILrTKexR565IQG5XJAGNudv&fid=0x0:0xaeda9401ede2ba0d"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Evan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItqym_b8p4Y-FW9783yYhbbkXgbWq5yo1i3Fyi_bB9_Q1tlIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would give this place like 4.5 stars (rounded up). Me and my friend saw this place and came for dinner cuz it's close to the station. We ordered the beef noodles , lamb noodles and a beef roll. The noodle dishes are like top notch , the meat is like really marinated has alot of flavor , the soup is light yet flavorful and the noodles are like really really good best part off he dish. Only complaint would be that there wasent enough meat. The beef roll on the other hand was good but it seriously wasent crispy enough , like other places make it alot better. I will be back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzo4O-zhqxaB3b7CsauqZUGepwgsMpyXurqfVZ&fid=0x0:0xaeda9401ede2ba0d"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Kalvin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYzAZd-0_JeniSNljNxgImCwzlXWbe6PzaDeAXT6_nhg5vP5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious soup noodles, noodles house made and tasted amazing. The dumplings are also house made on the spot, very delicious and good price","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtJpQm5h9kD9OD18ZYbMj9gRDc-nz9EuMctDEm&fid=0x0:0xaeda9401ede2ba0d"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"Grace Wen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2XIkznAUYrEkmi4dBQzmfkfRqMmVpacMvYCIu_ECClxdDnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favourites in the neighborhood. I have tried their chili oil noodle, beef noodle soup and pan fried pork dumplings. Dumplings are bun-style with thicker wrap and juicy filling, super big portion and yummy. The chef, also the owner, is passionate about his cuisine and everyone is so warm and nice to the guests. We are so lucky to have this noodle house in New Westminster.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jenna Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGg-e6BxN2g-88okWKllKncviH9CH4B0qrexuTEO6DPzzBQDh9nA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a delightful spot!! I came by for a quick bite on my lunch break and was pleasantly surprised by just how tasty the chicken sun-dried tomato pesto panini & tomato basil soup were. So much flavor and freshness.

What made the experience even better was how warmly I was welcomed by the female staff member (I think her name is Melissa based on other reviews). The atmosphere of the cafe is already relaxing, but her kindness and hospitality really made me feel at home.

I will definitely be making this a regular spot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOU3zFdPFGkskAlqyHCtkBAMYIco-JT-8c9AtpP&fid=0x0:0xa8134001dba6540"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"David 04 Make the World a Better Place","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXmkrAyRsAwad4uDl0EKEwpsCVMLq51IOxmbley55h_iwJzGo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Discovering this quaint local cafe was a serene delight. Its intimate size creates a cozy and calm ambiance, providing a perfect escape from the hustle and bustle.
The simplicity of the setting enhances the focus on the delightful beverages and treats they offer.

Whether you seek a peaceful brunch spot or a quiet place to unwind, this small gem delivers a soothing atmosphere that complements its charm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8i56TIJovZVLpREyY3L_hp4-Ix4FyPhVkHxM&fid=0x0:0xa8134001dba6540"],"When":"2024-2-27"},{"Name":"Luvina W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQWK4cF_q7kCtZwvWfw_HwrsFCWzYDEPngMlhgC4A78mfXttr_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Coffee is average (also overpriced) and food is just ok. Their Thai chicken wrap is extremely sweet and rice-heavy. The lady is nice and greets everybody warmly. The male staff doesn’t care about customer service, unless perhaps if you’re a long-time regular. He is straight-faced and very uptight about their dine-in seating. He also pre-enters your tip amount for you before handing over the machine. Atmosphere is nice inside, but they may not give you permission to stay in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuwqWHaziIl6rYJ6IApKg0ZYITtQHqdjINPoG60zaM0i5tCDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wraps are seriously phenomenal. Packed full of deliciousness.

The lady behind the counter is so sweet and friendly.

I only wish that the hours were longer or it would be open on a weekend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Selena Jamie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3tWtt6PnSTFx_XvNEAakqyJI7cSRi4CXxeu0TjR0EDaooGUOnWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Whenever I work in the area, I always make sure to stop by this spot! I absolutely love the atmosphere, it has a chill, earthy type of vibe. The staff, I believe she's the owner is so kind and welcoming. I highly recommend this spot over any other cafes in New West. The pricing is fair and they have gluten free options","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Efremoff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTiPVQ-9JXTcXzRQdN9-9SCkK0WqJ8cCwTASx109bgxgREwe_B=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just came in and got two ice coffees and 2 cinnamon buns… let me tell you… I always complain about leaving tips nowadays as there is no service. This place proved me completely wrong. The lady working was extremely nice and you could feel her souls beauty. She was super attentive and sweet. Things like this make me have hope in the food industry and with tipping. Thank you for being the place that makes me enjoy leaving a tip! May God bless this cafe!

Let me tell you, the Cinnabon buns were just perfect, so delicious and if you have a sweet tooth like myself it’s the perfect treat especially when warmed up. I will make sure to come back here with my wife again, what a fantastic place! Thank you for your service!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4V4NDNxWBLq96E5_rDxTz09yEUPhSSn_SvFYO6l8UFGvbAodf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"good atmosphere here, friendly staff and great food, the coffee smell so sunny, love it👍❤","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2z9HYXO19yskkr4fpZXoknpmhe6dMFDXt5yT3&fid=0x0:0xa8134001dba6540"],"When":"2024-10-17"},{"Name":"Adam Pilolla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUumyC8O1a8Pr5l5Ubiy18FHxVqUIV8ByKhS5sO1D6erKul1M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pros:

Good food, good location, great coffee, kind service. Patio seating is really nice.

Neutral:

If you come alone you may be asked to take counter/community seating to make room for people that come as a group. Tables (including patio seating) was reserved for groups of 2 or more. Not unreasonable and doesn't bother me, but others might disagree.

Cons:

-Limited/no access to power from some seats
-Interior decor/vibes was a bit messy (some supplies cluttered about the space)
-Lots of insects coming in from the front door it seemed like. The door was propped open because it was summer time when I came.
-Wish it was open more (currently just open in the morning/afternoons M-F; I'd come more often if they were open Saturday at least)

Overall a nice place and I'd definitely come back once in awhile.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Andrew Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWO71O-6vtxy0oWqlkgMTL_1fXX0zuePLUhWltL9zkToFe7FadaGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mongo Bongo is the best.  For a reasonable price (not weight-based) you can choose your protein, noodles, veggies, and sauces, which is great for salt restricted diets.    So delicious and healthy!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0lRlVHdJQ5gCBY5w7WrbsSlrDHklpen-rmUCM&fid=0x0:0x713970a5d22759ba"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Lucy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhpoyGoo7QAzIZdMVZdM1P2RbFiWZgrwO3qms3wrV1pta1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing good food, place, and workers! It was really good and my sisters and I loved it! Will come here again for sure:)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8hsx_bhQOXzZonbctFVvwY9dq6-3lPSdC4s4&fid=0x0:0x713970a5d22759ba"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"Joshua Thoreson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViINSp-qAeNjHHAYdfZ1jW4LMmmhXyKCa-6rgdNOIJ8sPOfbMd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"That meal was so worth it- I can't wait to go back again! Not only do you get an option of trying your first bowl for the single price, which is already WAY more than enough for one person to eat (we took home 2 full boxes of leftovers), but also has a great selection of ingredients that you make yourself! It is basically cooking, except all the ingredients are right there and the chef prepared it in front of you and serves it fresh off the grill.

I was so full by the first bowl that I couldn't go back for seconds, but next time I will eat nothing in the morning so that I have more room to try out different ingredients and flavours! Very decently priced meal for anything in the area, and great service as well, plus extra rice and soup on the side! The 19 dollars spent was extremely fulfilling. Thank you, Mongo Bongo for a great birthday meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMog9GyN52XoZHM7HK56AKICBkjQ-yc3cbMkO22&fid=0x0:0x713970a5d22759ba"],"When":"2024-2-25"},{"Name":"Silvia Rocha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSXVbGeerAerrHPTq1pOWDk75ZZgvb_3UvGL4tcNp_-mbN0Aorfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We went there because of the reviews. But I didn’t like it at all. The meat is frozen and they just have a few variety of meat, vegetables, noodles and sauce. The kitchen is awful. I sat facing it. Service and portions are good, and the price is reasonable. Mondays they have all you can eat. I won’t go back there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jameela A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGmIjT4W8Bo17-ggNSzxcoDgtO-KQSSmnpYgy_oZo7qm1k2w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My boyfriend and I come here very often. The food is always amazing, the service exceptional, and very reasonably priced. My boyfriend had a choice where to go for his birthday dinner and with no question chose Mongo Bongo!
We are sad that our favorite and regular waitress has moved on to pursue her career, but we will still be coming here to eat for most of our dates. Highly recommend if you want a casual yet delicious meal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2JDEzEmV10TdATgOUgbcRZ7qcEUz5gkRDSwhBgPxuqDQJPiyH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really great option for fresh, delicious and customizable food at a great price! At the time of posting it was only $15 a meal per person during their lunch hours. You can customize your own bowl and get it prepped pretty quickly. The system they have is really straightforward - fill up a bowl, write your name, and wait for it to be cooked. Lots of great fresh options and endless combinations. The free soup and rice is a nice touch too. We were super stuffed and happy :) we'll be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbWGq77upTi5p294ky5eBBcR1E7GfKvd12OcNW&fid=0x0:0x713970a5d22759ba"],"When":"2022-11-6"},{"Name":"Aws Haddad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKZc4anGaTN7EwsuclQNhPc69i6yrSwswg5y08QcIg-qC4Ns4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is amazing and the price is even better. Staff were super friendly and experienced.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9-tcM7clpoIqRtlhvWec0zo4iYAr_bU7xboow&fid=0x0:0x713970a5d22759ba"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"John Pavich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuyEz1HEhAOzXrL--Nq2rogi1FwxGuUuJszVZlodj_off4yg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little restaurant very friendly staff super clean including washrooms and great value for the money.

This a Mongolian style cooking restaurant.

You pick from a large selection of meat and vegetables and put them in a fairly large bowl and you can watch them cook your food on a large round heated metal table top.

You pick from an array of sauce toppings and have a choice of soup or salad and coffee or soft drink.

I had the coffee which was really good our server said it was a blend of regular and expresso coffee.

All this at lunch for $12.95
A very good price for the amount of very tasty food we received.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBv-RNbIHBggIhdhl-7MqAQFMpfovxR587rWIN&fid=0x0:0x713970a5d22759ba"],"When":"2020-9-17"}]

[{"Name":"Eddie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-x1D_gTsXAUjtRy3WP7DlmiBhS2kpEqnCMKvZ5-dJMacv5RbT-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the lamb on rice and portions were just right ✅️ 😋 👌

Really fresh with an array of vibrant sauces plus the hummus was very smooth and tangy!

The lamb was really juicy and fragrant!

Definitely coming back when I'm in the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFxwloCIntwwwPRRlPEsGodzsHgV1LAW_S0IR0&fid=0x0:0x27e46df87331793a"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"Salma Dehaybi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeBzrAyxy8TsPtlfyLy95iExOCgDCfc_1AtHCrTNKtTVaqFeiV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were attending the job fair in the neighborhood, and after being done we found ourselves starving as we looked at shawarma corner. We decided to give it a try and ordered the beef shawarma wrap and the beef special or exclusive? We thought ther would be a difference in sizes, but not really. I added tabbule to my wrap, thought it would come on the side but it was added inside the  sandwich. Honestly, food was super tasty, and for a good value. Highly recommended. We hope we'll be in the neighbourhood soon to be able to try new items","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiuf2DRldVA_1zAunH7FYQD0NVeVmmrA2iRNkw&fid=0x0:0x27e46df87331793a"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Eduardo Gutiérrez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCf5SMWULQ_Xi4NkYNoBJ3lzxdcPw0LEANBIv7mAAZmLyCnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've had shawarma in many places, and these ones are among the very best. Big in size a flavorful. Reasonable prices, very clean place, good customer service. They could add a TV or music and improve the atmosphere, I guess. Eating there is pleasant,  nonetheless.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great in portion and taste.

I ordered Chicken plate, that came with rice, chicken slices, hummus, salad and a pita bread.

I couldn't finish the whole plate and it was so filling.

Shawarma comes in 2 sizes, regular and special. Special is double in size.

Friendly and pleasant customer service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOf9MRB4u1o04qGFCmutqWjBG83VSTcXcit8q0Q&fid=0x0:0x27e46df87331793a"],"When":"2023-12-26"},{"Name":"Melanie Sia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_uRz_gX9bXrus0cIflXojI71ZjvU7thmxsdkuuOTqIHZ0OZbb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Grabbed a lamb plate during a work lunch, which contained lamb shavings on a bed of seasoned rice, a tabbouleh and cucumber salad (you can add feta for an extra fee), and yogurt and hummus dip. It was great and the portions were very generous for a lunch that is very reasonably priced at $13.99 before tax. I also learned later on that you can pretty much choose any meat and put it on a bed of fries, which I'll be trying next time (and of course, you can get it wrapped up in a pita of course)!

I'll be honest; you won't be here for the ambience (it's set up for quick grab-and-go takeout meals in New West) but service is fast, and if you happen to dine in as I did with my friends, the staff will bring your food to your table which is nice.

This place is around the corner from where I work and I can see why my colleagues keep coming here--the food is incredibly tasty! I'll be back!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQ5wbOX5XXmiSZVbr9h9qy0DeZSqCXHnk-fO_v&fid=0x0:0x27e46df87331793a"],"When":"2023-12-2"},{"Name":"Puja Raniga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8bef_PNJhUd65FDiyjsMWNOGXuZMZupiWpVcMJRpkiK8Izjfmxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome place for a filling meal, service was quick and efficient and didn't break the bank. A great place for a substantial meal combo which cost $16 after tax. Definitely recommend for anyone who's on the hunt for great ears that are open after 9. They close at 10 and are also available on DoorDash","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPN6IOfmCJIJC80edz3SdVplK04QB2D8MHKNfKy&fid=0x0:0x27e46df87331793a"],"When":"2023-6-30"},{"Name":"Baran Amadi (Matar)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwppJBpMJor5RwIZG7JZvUzhGTwxIV5YO9SWD-HC8qUzfz7gf5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I decided to try this restaurant for the first time exactly half an hour ago and it will be the last time, just because I ordered my dinner without onions, and I repeated that more than once that they do not add onions inside sandwiches, and when I returned home the view was like this, how much in the picture, this amount of onions is enough to make a large amount of food, this is the first time I write a negative comment on a restaurant, and I gave this star only for the good manners of the employees there, they were very polite in their dealings, but I think they have a hearing problem, I am sorry to say this.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0IiYPd3vTmPvVKtfw7z7JAxXvrmbXrqC644iK&fid=0x0:0x27e46df87331793a"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Ohad Okon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX302A6boj9UFqYFCOB_0YcTBmLRgnIO_ais5CmlKeAJ4Yfyn3o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely LOVE this place!!
I’m a regular - I always receive the absolute best service, and no matter what I order it is always just so delicious. The prices are very reasonable.
I’m getting hungry and my mouth is watering just writing this review haha I think I’ll go get a shawarma now.
Whether you’re a meat-eater, vegetarian or vegan, there are several delicious options for you for dine in, take out or delivery (more about veggie and vegan options below 👇).
You don’t have to use a delivery app to get take out (it’s slightly cheaper if you don’t as the restaurant/you won’t need to pay delivery app fees). You don’t have to sit down when going to the restaurant - they will make your food in 5 minutes ready for take out (or dine-in). 10 minutes at most, if they’re super busy. Seriously this place is a gem! I cannot stress just how much I love it, and how much I recommend you try it and fall in love like me.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I think they wanted their price point to be more affordable. Diced chicken were used in the biryani and butter chicken, instead of the usual cuts.

Service was friendly and prompt since it was the owner who served us.

Overall, it was just okay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNW6eRh5oG8s8MYPl7TDKx16pxuqRYsXxNxIOiB&fid=0x0:0x22214d82cbb830c3"],"When":"2024-3-17"},{"Name":"venkat b","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0BldN8SwI74duIlAJrGJ-ur0FeLyXVxyNF_J2LXg2hGrWmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is terrible please read everyone and spread this to save some people from this poisonous food

We ordered lamb curry yesterday, it was so  terrible they just added some pieces of lamb and added tomato puree and added lot of food colour which last in my hands almost one day. Just think if it last one day in my hand what about in your stomach.

Forget about the taste we can cook far more better than what they served

I request this restaurant guys please don't make money by putting public’s health in risk.

I am adding few of those pictures for your reference.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaDKNG1dRvcXkyYI03q-zR8KMQFWF-SObym_OL&fid=0x0:0x22214d82cbb830c3"],"When":"2024-4-7"},{"Name":"Spencer Phillips","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpyCrdyfNDrHh-7cRvRCDG7zHE-43gdhOFrDpcAJpYST7_hfy5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Four of us went here for the first time. update: we both got extremely sick from the food poisoning and have had a stomach bug lasting multiple weeks 🫠","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOf_5jQ8Y_aSltgwguh6lsumdIPa-fVM9kWJNJK&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Jason York","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2KL5JJiTZL1QVt_3AcqILQXXBIuqDWdYOdj3lYENvavlAma6S8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Not bad, but not amazing.   Pho is a decent size, I got the rare beef with tendon... Rare beef was great, but tendon isn't worth ordering, too chewy.   Spring rolls are great, definitely get those!  Beef skewers tasted great, but I wish they were grilled.  I have yet to try their grilled meats for vermicelli noodles. Fast service, free WiFi. Booths will NOT fit larger people.  Cash or Debit only.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCK5OS-tuC6cLwPzbXhc2IS8i17_4exwsSHSpC&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2022-8-15"},{"Name":"Yasmeen Vaquerano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwvjWR8MYm9tRtuJ7TUkjN8HhxeEjYb5-UgNAK4hmv3OhFFn4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The meat did not seem fresh. It had a fishy flavor. The meatball was frozen still on the inside. I only ate the noodles because I was skeptical of getting food poisoning. Never coming back to this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAaPkvXzl-VcFJCQ7RT8Ec201iuo96GTsjY7LW&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Gnarmar89","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj7N-kM5hY94VvJOxzFeNU6jBUfqr5FXFsdzPTdN97cusHdzDu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered the #30 special spicy noodle soup and Vietnamese spring rolls. The soup was very tasty but I found it had a lot more oil/grease than other places I have tried. Only comes with Vietnamese ham and beef brisket. I added beef ball for an extra charge of 3$. The spring rolls were all cut up into little pieces, which is not good because they get very cold very fast so I would suggest to have them not do that next time. Portion size was good for price. Asked for chilli oil on the side but only got hoisin/siracha. This was a take out order but if I was to eat inside I noticed the door didn’t close properly and there was a draft coming inside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiqfWP71YNefL0L1BMtyEx8yyE_m4omzvGuhXl&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2024-1-19"},{"Name":"Gina Rivas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3yc0ff4SWtB94Uagxg9g0tLV3s-B7nr-qP-WvjdMQcMx6uuxo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Salas rolls were dry and chewy. Did not taste fresh. Pho was surprisingly tasteles","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6wOtceH--SFWfnbwEPgE_AYb3vJaaTzonO491&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"B W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJp85P5JohieEKJOfTMzyjH1aTNit_eIhBL3dFVyxf0xS2BxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The missus and I have eaten at Pho Angkor twice in the last 2 weeks and both on Friday evenings.  Pho Angkor is located in the  Columbia Square Plaza shopping centre in New Westminster.  We learned from the owner that they had opened only for about a month now and is affiliated by family with Pho Express Angkor in Queensborough.

We have tried the Vietnamese spring rolls,  Lemongrass Chicken with Rice and the Lemongrass Beef Vermicelli bowl.  We found the food was excellent and the service was prompt.  The restaurant was not busy for a Friday evening but that may be due to the restaurant not being discovered yet.  We enjoyed our food and would be back to try other items on the menu.  Payment is only by debit or cash.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMar1L6lGRHzj8WJ9tFp_18hf4OrhUlg1s91JIW&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2022-9-11"},{"Name":"robert luchene","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjjaxNMjjElbJIf3rYl-fXCWERoK0kjepSp9EFVgxa44LmfWiniQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location right outside my building 😁 the food is delicious, me and my son always get the pork chops or pork chop and chicken combo my wife really likes the Pho the skewers are tasty and there Banh Mi are very good as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHfOOA-xNSWORtrnhOY9dwxK-nVBG2vcuf8Qes&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2023-4-15"},{"Name":"Jaime M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnLmikw5pk5avLE4RKKbToTp5J3u8IfXAtjsepV-SRQPBdQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food is here is not good. The spring roll was filled mostly with taro and seasoned with too much pepper. Pho came with 2 slices of meatballs and the other order came without any meatballs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBk3HjY3TGZ7mWVAiCm_1ZoApgEnX7mSxs4Crs&fid=0x0:0x8b96d474e1771197"],"When":"2023-4-20"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Elizabeth M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuhhJ3L27gYQJMwvKARhYEqE4v9PowLqfpDtvNV5G-CUir9-oeQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was finally able to visit this place. Let me tell you the food did not disappoint. I was dying for some pupusas! The queso con loroco was amazing. They were thick and full of cheese and beans! Loved them. My mojarra frita was delicious. My husband ordered the carne asada tacos and he loved them too. I will definitely be back. I wish it was an actual restaurant. It's only take out but the owner is very friendly and she definitely knows how to make pupusas! I live in Maple Ridge and I had not found good Pupusas near me.  I will definitely be back for more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs9nZC7zuH6CXKjZCNuqTB2HWbBqzr9DXfgJyM\u0026fid=0x0:0xf6bb8ba4a88f147c"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Caitlyn Bernal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKyesmljBRKCbllH2nf4HBk9fwepFwm6536BmnRot4wvc6-Oqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"order pick up about 30 minutes before they closed. quality was 10/10, and the pupusas were authentic and delicious, especially accompanied by the pickled veg and sauces. recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"eduardo sanchez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVFdBXmV6p_SwOx8Jn5o2Ih-yQHNZnAyr20Q1L0QdeokHzYoM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Recently bought from here and ordered the pupusas. But to my surprise they didn't include the sauce or pickled cabbage salad. Those two items are essential to that dish. Very disappointed with this restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Francocrs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJA7ui-IkAqZpLndwGyUnRUVP5wLc2kpaRMYdplxr2ppDGIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Thought I would try a few dishes here because of the high rating. Got everything to go. Steak fajitas and the revueltas. They got the protein wrong on the fajitas and gave us chicken instead. The fajitas were average tasting at best, the homemade tortillas need work, just a thick doughy pancake that was slightly underdone. The revueltas were pretty good, decent filling and texture.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"karla-with-a-k","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLv--Dmj0g5GDoYdyjIhbr_FSfKc-dXhsptdnww5nIldVYkkw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best place for pupusas are number 1 in b.c. Vancouver burnaby new west, I give them 5 stars because the food is authentic and made with love. I love pupusas and they make the best ones out there for sure, plus the people who attended me where super nice and very sweet to me.....not sure if there a dinning area because when you walk in it's a big kitchen ....never saw tables or chairs, so this place you just order pre hand and then pick it up. So worth it everyone I'm telling you the best !!! Xo","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Farrah Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWS2qu1UW8d4EM-wYu1KCiV-jJq0YkOzMP2eCyFnb2JX7IjLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Don Chepes has the best pupusas hands down. The revueltas are my favourite. My only complaint is that it should be made clear on google that you cannot dine in and it’s take out orders only. The entrance is also confusing as there’s no sign that says the restaurants name.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"selena d","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4SCNl4Hdr-cWJzr_5hdYWW14lPfePWYsOnmo6lqbW5flCVto=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A friend told me about this little place, tucked away in a small plaza.  I love pupusas, so I'm glad I found this little gem! They were cooked perfectly, very cheesy and full of flavor!  The curtido had little finely chopped jalapeños, I've never had it this way before, but it was a nice little spicy kick!\nThe tamales were lovely as well, I love that they use chicken and not pork.\nWould have given 5 stars but they don't have a full menu right now so when I tried to reorder they were out of many things....Maybe do an updated menu online?  Either way, will definitely be back!  Yum!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUkiN4uhOoc3PKV-za6Ho97kLT8pbsgy2glRNx\u0026fid=0x0:0xf6bb8ba4a88f147c"],"When":"2021-2-15"},{"Name":"amy murdoch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYDEIhqMzZE0QL39eFDKLqOjRB1uEel97EJ76DFPk8CfAgCmTz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really enjoyed everything we ordered! [{"Name":"Victor Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiXHgqLCDJOb_oS5LpVCenoXq_5Jcx_YWlZAdgmsfWXReffBmb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food was very good and service was alright, we noticed the table next to us waiter was more tentative to their needs than ours.
I do recommend the food because it was very delicious without complaints from the appetizers to the dessert. Also the waiter paired the wine with my main course very well.
Would recommend booking online,  because I tried to book a table on the phone but we left on hold for better part of 25 mins.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2FdUxpSJTfUJubVI-KRREQAf-FDhiEuCwVn-H&fid=0x0:0x176c2f2a906ffc29"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkLPbuR2Lbk_N-PtXNVGF1nDc7UOQmEl0cDxsJheipcOTu3i85=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It was the evening of Sep.28, we had a reservation for a birthday party, it wasn't busy (<50% full), and many people from our party paid for 2 hours of parking to dine here.  Service was so slow that we ended up purchasing additional time approximately 30 minutes after expiry.

Reasons we sent dishes back: ravioli was cold, bisque was cold, additional $ mushroom side had no flavor.  From the other guests, the steaks were the best things on the table.  However, I was hoping to come here for seafood dishes.

Desserts were also nice, but overall, it was a disappointing experience and I hope it can be improved, since Ive had good experiences here before.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmUELtgaQIF98KwlXoBpdZSEZx-1MVRnPW_KXn&fid=0x0:0x176c2f2a906ffc29"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"Virginia Barazzuol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLL7wkWLIn3uxnKGJhdMyd6yiile32ZYmw8MVcgdfWI-jdUHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went for happy hour and it was such a great experience!
