[{"Name":"Therese Mah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMo1JPqqcp4z0dj0TcHyRbw0CqVFoZWUF8q9F1kQNB37ywhjGHKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Stick to the gelato. The pizza was super disappointing. It's marketed as fresh Napoli-style thin crust, and the reality is a pre-fab crust. The margaritas pizza also had only 8 small basil leaves for 10 slices.

They also don't allow gelato samples, which I get... but I wish I could try some of the experimental flavors first.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1dBXKxSj256c7BlrianLRIWVV3PZGkZ0u3jLV&fid=0x0:0x10f67da4d97148dd"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Sabrina Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjsvCF2w1oI567TghlIVOR2ivk58LTQ9RlsDCAwySmN9B-Fxsgkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friends recommended their gelato to us, and the gelatos are really nice. We ordered a Lotus biscuit flavor and a cannoli pistachio flavor, which are both with a richness of aroma. They have their own dining area, which has a glass roof with it to make it very bright and chill. The staff are friendly, and they will serve you the ice cream cones with a cone holder, which is very tidy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuvlCNc4oCL7NCLZJSm3dJqqzHe0X3HziHO-O4&fid=0x0:0x10f67da4d97148dd"],"When":"2023-4-23"},{"Name":"patt pat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3em3F7V8J5xqv_kQFCNex_3_c0PtIDSE4Lv3XbwsF0nDKyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"For a quick bite of microwaved snacks, it’s ok as it comes with a river view; but need to put up with the nasty attitude, belligerent look of those Asian staff!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNP9segp-GbWJWxIw3yLEQ9gt_xHWTMx0XsgfHB&fid=0x0:0x10f67da4d97148dd"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Tanpreet kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU37Wwuh1twAo7eaN7uPjNC2simJAut6YFF_aGgPXMF048cpgxr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It was my first time visiting the River market, so my friend and I discovered this Gelato caffe. We decided to try one scoop of the White Chocolate Nutella and it was pretty good. The portion size could've been bigger though. I would definitely come again to try more flavours.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0IbAOut63Jxr4l7y_JAkTEfefV2MIMno4LIFD&fid=0x0:0x10f67da4d97148dd"],"When":"2023-8-23"},{"Name":"Roxi EE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKImbf5UMv5TkEjZdIeEhJWnVrjTA5L31Ye3RIm7SxKRU39VmW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here for ice cream with my kid.  Service was friendly, but our drinks were disappointing, and the gelato was hit-and-miss: my panna cotta was the hit, and my son's lemon raspberry was the miss, unfortunately.  I thought he was being picky, and tried it, myself.  We're both fans of sour things, but agree lemon gelato should be sweet-and-sour, while this was rather bitter-and-sour.  Poor value for money, as well.  We were unfavourably impressed, all told, even though the panna cotta gelato really was fantastic.

Edited to add a star for classy proprietor who accepts criticism with grace, and also because that panna cotta gelato really is amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOibAIrCesKmD8bKK-dxNfj8S9VnJyWyfnlOoxc&fid=0x0:0x10f67da4d97148dd"],"When":"2022-6-12"},{"Name":"Angela Jeffery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtGyld6d4wIU2Lb7oe7xsoiq4r77iaBdF6nkFQ8ek01eF1q7c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ham and cheese quiche was light with large pieces of ham and a solid but not heavy crust. The smoked salmon quiche, however, was mouthwatering savoury. We would have taken some to go, but they didn't have any left.
The gelato was rich, flavourful, and creamy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeQ916A0ZD7eOYitEXIchQllEfK-36S_DyVASA&fid=0x0:0x10f67da4d97148dd"],"When":"2023-4-23"},{"Name":"Millie Cheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWG6lyJsvFpdy5fooM5ZYPrxE7rcUxLdtvq-7uAOHWC-RWcujOI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Nice Panini and Latte
Enjoy looking the view and walk around in River Market
Hope to try ice cream next time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCcS8zazNpTcaa4zgOWrW-6TRlwpHASt_uxaC_&fid=0x0:0x10f67da4d97148dd"],"When":"2024-1-23"},{"Name":"Maisha Haque","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVi-CglkkXkpH5yPCPVMLEMVtb3gIo_97pxp33RiaiGVrT9Hd6dwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a Really great latte and tasty gelato. [{"Name":"DANICA DG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj8yVKC3dNCSLVLekHGiPlGf0ppRbR1ZDLgf-FYq7onHLSuVle=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Newly open restaurant at the Quayside. Big patio seating and indoor as well. The prices reflects the portion of the food! Generous 🙂‍↕️

I love the Prawn Fettuccine from their dinner menu, I’ve had it few times since they opened = doesn’t disappoint. It’s a pesto based with large prawns amazing (if you’re a seafood lover like me) &

The steak was cooked to perfection , medium rare and the peppercorn sauce definitely added to the taste of the meat.
Shout out to the cooks for these amazing dishes! Cant wait try more 👏","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMB76K-ZsmAMqpjDN4PSo7fd_xwN8vtRXK4K1qa&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Andrew Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWO71O-6vtxy0oWqlkgMTL_1fXX0zuePLUhWltL9zkToFe7FadaGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We loved the renovations for this great new Italian restaurant which managed to be classy but still maintain sports on the TVs (muted) and an extensive tap and wine list.  My 12oz ribeye was tender and delicious and the others were really happy with their pastas.  Also, you can’t beat the river front of the Quay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyXk9qlO3Nshnz2aS2JjpJy5oIaDfTsbC2Ed75&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Sophia Ternes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXO1dc99oxKn5BsdM7aiUWZd4aVboUsqV54V3bOh8nQ2VF9fPTS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I come here once a week, everyone is great. Katie is a wonderful bartender, friendly kind, beautiful and her drinks are fantastic. Richard plays live music on Saturday, his voice is amazing, transports you back and is like a dream! Food is fantastic love the spot","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPInMTa80aPg55nKwPVj6IOweoKHFXmx92NMu6X&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The lunch menu is very limited in choices. There were not many customers around 1pm on Saturday, guess the hype is over? We had prawn fettuccine, chicken wings, mozzarella sticks (not very tasty), and beef penne which was made wrongly, as there's no beef 😂 they decided to give a discount of $4 for that. My peach bellini was tasty, I like it. There was room to improve service, no water was offered. Without the benefit of that location, I don't think I would return to use that service at that price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMV6TrwhLRKRodlRfiaSHWxtwMw_A8tShYYhFAJ&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Kevin Needham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW091KnP2Cr4T7TVe2u7UM8j8scer3C7OU4HkskIF9bkg_mmAas=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food quality was way above expected. I’m a new west person and like many adored the patio of old. No changes inside. Would love to see changes there to solidify this place as a year round draw.

What we ate:
Fettuncine ai gamberetti = Pesto cream based with seafood. So good great taste, very fresh, would 100% get again. Affordable relative to what’s around NW and crave worthy.

Pasta con Filetto di Manzo = tomato based with beef chunks, mushrooms. Also super flavourful, a close second and order-again worthy. Beef was a little tough but not enough to ruin.

Toast skagen = unique fun and light, sauce heavy. Dilly creamy with full prawns. Would order again but more polarizing than other dishes.

Fries = unique, good when hot. Maybe a bit undercooked but I really enjoyed them. Friends said they were a bit sweet.

Drinks:
Old fashioned = great
Itilia fashioned = gorgeous presentation, tasty and what you want from a alcohol forward gin-based grapefruit drink

Apparently more pub favourites to come which I think is a needed guilty pleasure of the residents and this locale. Not available at the time of this review.

Overall seems like management and stuff care. Growing pains like always but good first  impression.

Verdict: Eat New West needs to chill out, give it a chance","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVT32IIw7xw_uSUr1CMq6px5_k4fQI6shUhX-6&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Akhtar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPe1cXkOxnt5e1kl7DXOVX1TkTwivQgahK_8RtarhociYnQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I noticed this new restaurant open up and gave it a try, it exceeded my expectations. Staff and servers were very friendly. Food came pretty quick, I ordered the salmon dish and it was on point. I'll try the pasta next time. This place has a really nice atmosphere and great view.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNufsI3PSfLvXlpmCsMB83c_mCdFKkMLANB-QuV&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great restaurant in New Westminster on the Quay. A perfect place to enjoy a happy hour visit or sit down for a comfortable dinner. Great view and a heated enclosed patio.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhSlaLSM4D8V21v2x9TzpVCcN2SA0Z8Jt7I1px&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Sherzad Seddiq","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1kW7Qya75wg7novgIythqlzAnA3zFhpvsU-k2jwRv0bRJEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of having dinner here Saturday night and have to say loved everything about it. Food, service and atmosphere was awesome. The beef penne was so good I just had to share this photo. Definitely coming back, thank you to all the staff for a great dinner experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMM3Gvke09RpqEbQhlNhKCA4_sJqHbF0gyQwTlG&fid=0x0:0xebe7a8e53cbad2ed"],"When":"2024-7-29"}]

[{"Name":"Xanat Guiot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWn9mA0A5Hy_yyrqA2UDD-rwiAN4Y01cjYiN1ER3FYVM5kgBkh6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really tasty pizza 🍕! The marinara sauce was delicious and well seasoned. The crust was also very yummy. We also tried the chicken butter donair, which is one of their signature dishes and it was also delicious and flavourful! The owner was very friendly and attentive. We hope this new business does well and we are happy to support local! Great addition to the neighborhood!.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZfkruSqh2xNCTzkZ-xoFoetMef0MS1S_aUTdh&fid=0x0:0x997ad46b9c22f66d"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"Makbro Foods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRFF38LVlFd8WWpvanTvHgok4hDqsY7Z4yDPbIFCX93WASFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is under new ownership, and it’s clear they’ve brought fresh energy and creativity to the menu! The new offerings are exciting and a bit different from what the previous owner had, making dining here a real treat.

The flavours are bold, the dishes are beautifully presented, and there’s something for everyone to enjoy. Whether you’re a long-time customer or visiting for the first time, I highly recommend checking out the updated menu.

The service is excellent—friendly and attentive, which makes the entire experience even better. Don’t hesitate to give them a try; you won’t be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shuja Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEBorCT1xB53Ohf-r3sasYNY3f1aLK2cvkUGn0blmUthajlwZj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Leila donair previously, now New West Donair & Grill. I used to live one block away and eat at Leila’s often before moving out to another area and couldn’t dine in again. Today I was in the area again and saw this restaurant with a new name and new management. The staff is warm and welcoming, they greet you nicely which makes your experience better. The menu offers much more variety than previous one, they have different types of donairs and wraps on offer. I tried Lebanese and it was an absolute treat to my taste budds!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOv8Y0BD2xL29HvX1TnI0mgk00hoj9B71DIaeYt&fid=0x0:0x997ad46b9c22f66d"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Sonya Carter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVc6ipv7m0Aab8z9ow2SjCE1LAznVIpAcvR2vnz4WTQyZsFxxH1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best donair platter that I have tried! Lots of flavour, chicken was great, a selection of fresh veggies and rice was cooked just right! The Owners were very friendly and helpful ☺️ definitely will be back","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNH8FRwbGsyRwHknVxdvejrFRPHv-HBHJCip2iO&fid=0x0:0x997ad46b9c22f66d"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Julian Del Balso","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsq6MBT-XC7Rl-iCqAOi-osekdBSIoXw6eBjQonfFcDItA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I went here because of the amazing reviews and I have to say it didn’t live up to them. There’s really nothing special about the donair here, and I’m in the area fairly often so I was hoping it was good. It’s very spice/herb heavy and has a homemade flavour, if that’s something you like I’m sure you’ll like this, and the portion was fairly large, but flavour wise it’s honestly standard. I did see the lady behind the counter (as sweet as she was) offering people in the restaurant Baklava in exchange for reviews so maybe that explains the inflated number here","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7NvgGDqFK-16SpQnx2zJpWO0yQA0Oou0J9iY&fid=0x0:0x997ad46b9c22f66d"],"When":"2024-2-18"},{"Name":"Harmanpreet Harmanpreet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0XUdTMUKmQ6dQr2Z1DZfVZoDo6iJlLgn2YCVhX0Pnp_b0xn2x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered the paneer pizza from this place, and it was absolutely delicious! The flavors were perfectly balanced, and the paneer was fresh and well-seasoned. Special shoutout to Nav, who provided exceptional service. She was very professional, friendly, and made the whole experience even better. Highly recommend this pizza store for amazing food and great customer service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Devan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJdtRvHijPQImYbth1kbWO9_A2QzWeRJClKa6buxr6SkSgiWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can’t say enough good things about New West Donair, it’s not often that I leave reviews but this spot is a 10/10. Excellent food, service, and experience… I would consider this the best donair spot in town, definitely recommend checking it out if you get the chance, you won’t be disappointed!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDkrA-XJ6OKmW8udWr1Lw0maK-RWGEB3zh8tuV&fid=0x0:0x997ad46b9c22f66d"],"When":"2024-2-9"},{"Name":"Hillbillytc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV833YeKMKJfxtYeKhRHVRSrikZoFOcCapKBwyEFBOnxiCMeXAZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There is no atmosphere, but you don't come here for that. The food was amazing the portions are big lots of GF options really fresh ingredients the humus wow. The owners super friendly. Best donair in Mew West.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0SI23-K6I5A7ROAlA8P6ZkKH52PoJTXTo15OE&fid=0x0:0x997ad46b9c22f66d"],"When":"2023-9-9"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sky Eyes Video","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2JXXl5yK-thMqk8EUNl3FWmyw5SFqlc_KvzAMt-0MdDn-UuKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We always have a great time at the River’s Reach Pub. They’ve renovated since the last time we were here and everything looks really nice and updated. Both our server and bartender were super attentive and friendly. On one night we came for dinner and had chicken strips and fries (not pictured, because we ate them too fast!).

On our second night we came in just for a few drinks at the bar! We really liked the Spicy Lime Margarita and the Zero Proof Heineken. Definitely the best non-alcoholic beer we’ve tried, tastes just like the real thing. We’ll definitely be back when we’re in town! Check them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsQpGUyuQwqzHNb3UIx_YurZzPJVvGc-R7ONNK&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There were a few things that left room for improvement. The drinks, including the Old Fashioned, were served in plastic cups, which felt a bit out of place for a sit-down pub experience. The chocolate peanut cake was unfortunately stale and overly sweet, as was the coleslaw.

On the bright side, the smashed burger and fish and chips were solidly average — nothing mind-blowing but satisfying enough. Overall, it’s a decent spot for a pub.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEkgw30iit-JywxVTtkfnCgL988HvJ2e6gTFNc&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Carmen Aboytes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCCLFKJlS62-34BUpujZzDsaZV9yysTxPBmk8fhCY7OoETeMyS6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A decent spot to grab a quick bite if you're in the area. The pizzas and burgers are fairly good, but I opted for a bowl, and the portion size was disappointingly small. I ended up having to order something else to feel satisfied. If you're looking for a light meal, it might work, but for heartier appetites, you may need to explore other options or order additional items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaknz9FbPkJUiC6a1IlqgOJuBE62sZxQ22ToPP&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"P G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJSQy-hEJFpR-6M_rhWQtV4ho3OA5uBTDPVIdU7lH_VajQsEDm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited The River Reach in New Westminster for brunch, and it was an outstanding experience from start to finish! The new brunch menu is impressive — the dish I enjoyed featured crispy bacon, perfectly seasoned potatoes, and the most delicious poached eggs. The flavors were spot on, and the presentation was as appealing as the taste.

What made the experience even more memorable was our server, Lexi, who is hands down the best in New West! Lexi's warm personality, attention to detail, and impeccable service made us feel right at home. She truly went above and beyond to ensure we had a fantastic meal, making our visit even more special.

The River Reach has nailed it with their new brunch offering, combined with the exceptional service from Lexi. If you're looking for a top-notch brunch spot in New West, this is the place to be. Highly recommend, and we will definitely be back! Five stars!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8pfkNMdbN--mTxr8w4PuMdq8WojBb2E0i8ERU&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"zaheed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYpN5rN_eV90bqMqPZsPI4m30xKQ0LQqQTMnw8mZAgVdQxiFXP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you for an amazing evening Rivers Reach New Westminster crew! I very much enjoyed the amazing Thursday All day happy hour! Good vibes, good people, great specials!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTqyLFceyMDzYmk0dwk-mjh1TE0Hk8sDRXsnVy&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Angie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyUjdZQkz0bhaDppuQsySaOzrLROWSfhKe7zzOgxtMex30Fg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered a burger and the paddy was really bland. No flavor at all. Chicken salad was passable. Service was slow and disorganized.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOe-nxV5Ea88RaZSSLqiuTPAEVhPmoPY1IjnRy5&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"65choco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjUShwBbCq1OgQZUrFEZlGQDxK7kNUx0_Bo6QqLm15VbBTFPED=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place turns out very nice, the service is excellent, the atmosphere is very good. Only that I didn't enjoy the Crispy Chicken slides.  They cold down very fast and hard like hockey pops. I would like the slides with brisket or pull pork. FIrst time that I tried with  chicken and not good. We asked for something else and was excellent. Thanks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcUzSbEDZNw-_6FHfXWZbOL6pLlPUXl1Ddwa6e&fid=0x0:0x717f44207ac997b8"],"When":"2023-9-25"},{"Name":"T U","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0fqYSgi-Oa1ZxHKMAgkTIjdzOCoN9dbq8TIyQm2_XMOry1AQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our first time at River's Reach & we will definitely be back. We ordered a few appies, including nachos, and they were all delicious. Mary was our server and she was so amazing - friendly, professional & sincere. Thanks Mary!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"leesa tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsWaHyhzcw7kKPh9V3HkvTK5TTa81TdmCDp9IylYllx4puXIy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice place to come with friends for a bite. We ordered a couple of appetizers and main dishes. I enjoyed the “best fries ever” dish as it was quite flavourful. We also ordered nachos and thought it was average.

I ordered the fish and chip for my main and I thought it was average as well, can’t really mess up fish and chips! We also ordered the cookie jar cheesecake and the brownie and I definitely enjoyed the brownie dessert more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpJfMSnZbmGSAtOuJfsPlOBebm5A3RtY3Ep9gl&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Ju","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2D3S_u34v_pqpi-TAMe_IIQ9c28OYIl0iqN7ewQuPCIydQdyDuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went with my kids for the first time today, and it was awesome! The staff were super friendly and made us feel so welcome, especially our birthday boy. Our server Gui was great, made sure that our glasses were always full, gave us some great menu suggestions, and everything came out fast and delicious. The kids loved their meals, and I got to actually relax and enjoy mine.
All in all, very happy, definitely coming back. Thanks again Gui for making his day special!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edward Desaulniers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoP1wTU2-qZu4-kyQmMbasgYbLJv8tKfq6HxU12Zm-ypnqVMIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Like that friend who never lets you down but rarely surprises you either, Browns Social House delivers exactly what you'd expect from a modern casual chain – no more, no less. Stopping in an hour before closing on a weekday, we found the familiar comfort of a well-oiled machine running on cruise control, but we felt like the staff was getting ready to leave.

The nachos arrived as they always do – adequately portioned, properly layered, neither inspiring poetry nor causing complaint. They're the kind of nachos that make you think, "Yep, those are nachos alright." The drinks followed the same path of calculated adequacy – they'll get the job done, but they won't make you forget your favorite cocktail bar.

Where Browns does shine is in its consistency. It's like that old sweater you keep coming back to – not because it's spectacular, but because you know exactly what you're getting. The patio offers a pleasant escape, and the service maintains that professional warmth that's become the chain's signature.

This Browns Social House isn't trying to reinvent the wheel – they're just keeping it reliably rolling. For a casual meet-up with friends, whether it's lunch, dinner, or late-night bites, it's a safe bet. You won't walk away with a story to tell, but you won't walk away disappointed either.  FYI, the late night Happy Hour is a good value.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Mutadi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGSEocPQRhojQVtaGAuDTqmG1sDbHNEX-Qcv2iO6jQqf5vEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were here after a long day at the hospital. We were a group of nursing students and instructor. I asked our server if I could gift my companions by paying part of their bill and the manager and server went out of their way to make this happen. Everyone loved their food. Drinks were great. Our large group was seated right away. Server was attentive and lovely. Thanks Browns for a great experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3wj8Ne3ngI4eg9ouEU6zPmvERlQuudbckz4ma4Vg6pfYrsWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice patio, decent service, and we’ve come to this chain often (for lunch, dinner or late night drinks/appies) and haven’t ever been dissatisfied with anything. It’s consistently good.  We tried brunch for the first time and it also was good. Solid chain restaurant that is consistent as expected.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_pkdKS7YmDL5dGe5B4aNMC9NmfygtZ9pAnkW4&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Vero Vero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJqM6z3NvGgp8fOHPNYXy_sxK1l4a3Acl0A1wGDJ4i1AfuQXig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good place to enjoy with friends!😎
Calamari was crispy and delicious. I like the deep fried jalapeños with calamari. Chicken lettuce wrap was not really impressive. I tried Cactus club one and that one was much much better.. both taste and portion. But still not too bad. Alfredo fettuccine was okay, but maybe if it was more creamy, it would be better. Fish taco was the best among what we ordered. Toppings were all fresh and the portion was great. Deep fried fish stick was super crispy and there was no bad smell. And it came with French fries. (* we ordered an extra fish taco for friends. That is why ours is 3 tacos). Next time I will try happy hour ! No wonder Browns Socialhouse is everywhere😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzK1tp4BoGHjTbQX4Baffg8ca3PcifGn7fB_8e&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2022-1-28"},{"Name":"Michelle M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeetN-W20mnzvtvgZG8vAeDlWwG6zd354oPCvc1I4B_3Cjy_PI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They had a covered patio and we were able to get a seat right away for lunch. Everything was delicious. The nachos was great, I had the potato crusted cod with cowboy salad. The salad was fresh and hint of sweetness. The beef dip was amazing as well. Will come back because it wasn’t busy at all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnkhW3JAKURHPaOApBnp7xuIc5f7mrpLgzylVI&fid=0x0:0x598485d25f22dd36"],"When":"2021-4-21"},{"Name":"Cynthia Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICUBRND6v4jdjd62BXfRMAYoNx4reXnrOnSeKx6kAQJoR74g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We went to the New West restaurant. We go about 1x every 2 to 3 weeks. I love going there! The food is good, the music playlist rocks and the servers are friendly. They usually make the most tastiest, well built Loaded nachos compared to  other places. This is our go-to for amazing nachos!
But today was a MISS. It was built ok but the taste....none or very little spices...taco seasoning. And it was cold in some spots and warm in others. NOT as impressing as the last 5 to 6x we have been there. The lettuce wraps....that was off too. Very little chicken and on the" dry" side for the sauce. BUT the partner's eggs Benny was good. it was a disappointment for me because I love nachos and lettuce wrap. Will go again in a few weeks for nachos and hope it will be back up to par.  And I will Order the chicken burger.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Angie h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUK5-Eyg-HKdLqH6Sh0Yu5AouPT5bxsEAkZr27lVeLcEluqhYqm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Hipster spot for a coffee. Indoor seating with a few benches and one table outside. They sell beans, books and some vintage clothing. Got a flat white ($4.50) and it was a wee bit watery but still decent. They have mugs “for here”.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMk1TOOedG1e8yf8-RKXeh8rW3fMiUkNKoxaLeD&fid=0x0:0x8a7625871ac0ff41"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"S P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3H1hwIfN6Bp7TC6p9xHt7oE4AtZuMSz6HUmbD4gLsn19Lvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What was ordered:

• Oatmilk Cortado
• Caramel Latte
• Vegan Butter Croissant
• Vegan Chocolate Croissant

Despite it having a hidden location the cafe was fairly busy. The cafe has a unique ambiance. Croissants were nice and flaky, although I wished they were warmed. The drinks were great quality, smooth, and had perfect amount of foam for both drinks. Parking was convenient. Worth visiting if you’re in New Westminster.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSirM74wvZmvynZ45bb4MUYJD95IU5qjvGi1dN&fid=0x0:0x8a7625871ac0ff41"],"When":"2023-11-19"},{"Name":"Suzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI22wX1KZ9TxZUs_tdziOxzufan2M9vLUehl8t2WYvIIQ13Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm glad I found such a wonderful place. :-) A place where you can enjoy coffee in the morning and taste various cocktails in the evening! With perfect service and friendly staff!! If you go to New Westminster, be sure to check it out. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZNKPMRyj-Twa7pQOHYCQmJFJiF26erJUVRKiX&fid=0x0:0x8a7625871ac0ff41"],"When":"2024-2-25"},{"Name":"Ronan Flanagan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhyoJ6lTWosiWAbVYQi49ge9LAsllRtNIuQ5xgiUM26HnzbGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"By far my favorite place to get a coffee. Moodswing has wonderful fun artsy decor that I haven't seen anywhere else. They have a community bulletin which is great to look at and see what's going on. It's a unique place with a lot of personality that is a great place to go to get a goof coffee with a friend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAFq69iTIcaZDekD27us44d8ngDu8WdKsqDyyYnNu7GaC-OA8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have mixed reviews about this place. I think because I really want it to love it, but didn’t. The coffee was ok, I got an iced americano. The grilled cheese was missing the cheese for sure. I added avocado and overall tasted good. The Ramen egg sando was not bad, I would just probably leave out the ham out next time.  Also for 2 coffees and 2 drinks my total was $37… a little too much for my liking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkHf-_qKlX4eiUBwiUzs67zacW4EwuxRDUIhNX&fid=0x0:0x8a7625871ac0ff41"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Jason P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwQ6VrAafrL568UtVUXBwRugwDfBdgtXm5PLgDAxdMUbNAFin6DA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice little coffee shop along Front street. I had a cup of mocha and a Ramen egg croissant, definitely good sandwich :) I would definitely swing by if I’m ever in this area again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXmqqra0lHHdf_1bq250gAXMfbr9TidPKMUoKO&fid=0x0:0x8a7625871ac0ff41"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"Sarah Elawa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlPrusrI1olUCmNi-hQk4fOc-cIuHJ4EQ3P2FP7rGCORrC5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a wonderful time here! The decor is super fun and there was a DJ playing ambient music which was a nice touch. The cocktails were great and the Manero tacos were also really delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTBpxpf79D2YoVoDWHwfBhiT8gb4b02U_LhDav&fid=0x0:0x8a7625871ac0ff41"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Amey Bhalerao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMv55StxlVXYYWoEE7RnDnRseJdvhWRoDe9YMJF7N8vxGAJL4cHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of the very few places around where you get good cortado. We drove here 2 times. The first time we got, cortado was amazing but next time it was equally bad. I'm giving them 4* because I am giving them benefit of doubt. Probably third time if I go, it will be better? Feel free to consider this as 3 star too based on my review. Having failed once, I wouldn't specially drive for 30 mins to grab a cortado here, which is what I precisely did last time and I got disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOts4ZECZIGsFQMuEr7IE50xR1zKSXYY1SO3h_e&fid=0x0:0x8a7625871ac0ff41"],"When":"2024-2-22"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Wendy W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIT_NsjaeZ9_aRQ2hW1qAJhwmY0ztCvf8mUpBdGTJYY7T12ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been wanting to try this restaurant. We got take out tonight. When I picked up the food, the young lady was very nice. Lemongrass chicken and pork chops and rice (more than enough for 2 people) pork spring rolls ( so good ) and Bahn mi sandwich. It was very large amount of food for $36. It was very delicious. We can't wait to dine in and try other items on their menu. Love to be able to support locally owned restaurant in my neighborhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTBrcMdDv03XLCvCMXhyufb304Fz5Z3ZO92vl0&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Jim Chambers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXB9yTWikWo6YsCusf1mR3h6sPS14ZqSL085B9F76TWDEAH1gxv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"7.1.24 WOW!!! So glad we chose this place for lunch.  We had the pork spring rolls, rice chicken & sliced pork, chicken & shrimp vermicelli, and fried chicken wings.  EVERYTHING was prepared and presented perfectly.  DELICIOUS!!!Prices very reasonable for the quality and quantity of food.  Staff was friendly, dining area clean.Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmFrAj5VdcviFB_xIfyCRptssF0Vj_3hMbVRJe&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"Hayoung Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLb7oucGpGZ6hmmUFABXnR6QAUl2Ng87_yf6bzQhXXd_v814g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Co Chau got a brand new name but everything else has stayed the same - in a good way. Atmosphere here is really good, staffs are friendly and gentle as always, and most importantly - their pho is ridicuously good for the price. Which are fully loaded with meat in a huge bowl.
If you're visiting New Westminster and looking for a place to eat, just come here, sit back and treat yourself with the best pho in the area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMonXOiYSGiaGd5z3jP3zPeuqJU1HmKjfMt2b8U&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Mj Baltazar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1995LtB0r3ZpHOapaKCJ-pzP9O0nLnMjl56b2YuunoXxbZ1o-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was surprisingly delicious! We ordered the grilled pork and deep fried egg and it was one of the best i’ve had. Their spring rolls were huge and tasty. Service was +++. This will probably be our go-to pho place from now on.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOShLEpB8NQeibPFbHAC5R7Izibwco9Txp9Ditw&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Livia Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVie7wYIYnTNy_iOqvWMwiX-xgJH8Iz1_hWskpK-wZj63ZZMmbP6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"EDIT after second visit:

Finally tried their BBH the soup was delicious!!! I am a BBH lover and love trying out this dish at different pho restaurants. I love the flavor and could drink all the soup! Again I ordered large and had lots of left over to pack.

My husband ordered the special rice combo and Mom had the lemongrass pork with spring rolls vermicelli bowl. Very generous portion we really enjoyed the meal. I can safely say I will be a regular of this restaurant 😊

------------------------

First of all we were also big fans of the previous restaurant. I waited and read reviews from other visitors and finally decided giving it a try.

I knew it's not the same restaurant anymore and not like new owner assumed the same name and took over so of course food should taste different. To be fair, I left myself open minded for my visit. We ordered the house special pho and lemongrass pork and spring roll with rice, and chicken wings for appetizer.

I think the wings might need a little more seasoning in the coating, but the pho and rice were pretty good. I went greedy asked for a large. There was lots of ingredients I couldn't finish! The broth was light yet tasty. Also, I did not feel thirsty after drinking the soup! Those who said it's bland maybe are more used to very strong taste? Spring roll was actually good (though previous restaurant always had the best spring roll in Vancouver theirs were hard to beat!), they used broken rice for their rice, pork was juicy and tender.

Servers were pretty friendly (looks like family run), Overall pretty good experience. I would return to try other items on the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIzWVSv4PMBnaj9aKxJLtCE8ebbPi9BcKEwJkS&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Thu Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRRzabw1YXldXdzQGJEybM3uYOeYeKxlo74-VDyZtSerGHcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently decided to try this Vietnamese Restaurant. I had order a #28 which is hot and sour seafood rice noodles, and it was a delightful experience. The broth was a perfect balance of tangy and spicy, the seafood was fresh, featuring shrimp, squid, and fish cakes that were tender and flavorful. This dish is a must-try for anyone looking to explore the dynamic flavors of Vietnamese cuisine. I definitely will be back to try the other dishes. Highly recommend this wonderful restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPA0QECIgkW4qtS2ZJbxBMIcr17c5m5Hl3ecqW&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuk86eyrKzFCxN3fjC2Gh7WVgfPs4ac8RQel74iDY6fKVzQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amex accepted
This is a quiet, tastefully decorated Vietnamese restaurant in New West. You see flowers, traditional oil paintings, conical hats on the wall, and the wide screen TV shows the beautiful scenery of rivers and mountains in Vietnam. The service is courteous and efficient. They were closing soon and asked me if I minded that they mopped the floor. I said I didn't mind, but they waited till I left anyway.
The soup for bun bo hue is a bit different from the traditional one but tasty nonetheless. I especially like the smooth Bánh Canh they use for the noodles. Will come back to try the other dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoVCmfcS4SGVIgw5kUwT_VDXfL9iSm-84KqF6P&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I like this restaurant more than the old one at this location (Co Chau). My husband had beef stew with baguette (bánh mì bò kho) and I had pork chop & rice (cơm tấm sườn). Food portion was huge, both pork chop and beef were tender, and the flavor was on point, 9/10. I'd rate 10/10 if it's a little bit more sweet and less salty. Btw, you must try their salty coffee (cafe muối) and soursop smoothie (sinh tố mãng cầu), they're specialty drinks that are not even available at most Viet restaurants. The sour & sweet soursop is so refreshing for summer, loveeee it (trust me, I paid more for this drink at Tina cake and Pho ACE has it waaaaay better).
The staff were nice and the washroom was clean (which wasn't the case at many restaurants in New West like Georgie and Tropical Play).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMY9Gs2gInMftjMw1rKF9f8tetAIHorSfIXv_vj&fid=0x0:0x692072c793a82c28"],"When":"2024-6-30"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jesse Short","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_QnK6aCuRyloJkdMhF6-7Z4djVnpJZpfP8W46czbb57mXpyb7dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The service and atmosphere was nice, The beers were well priced, The food was really the only issue.

To say that this was pub, food is stretching it, I ordered nachos, wings and a chicken burger.

The wings were tiny, overcooked, very little meat on them, extremely disappointed.

The nachos, The top layer had some cheese, but 90% of the dish was me dipping dry chips into salsa. The $3 guacamole add was terrible In flavor and portion size, assuming it was squeezed out of a tube, I managed 6 moderate dips before it was exhausted.

The chicken burger actually was pretty good, I was surprised, and if I did happen to return it would likely be the food I would order just because It at least was satisfying.

I watched four other orders of nachos come out and all appeared to be approximately the same subpar quality.

Do yourself a favor and go for cheap drinks and go anywhere else for food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQ9ahN2E8LjKURfs2X7wJXD-ZvixWFfWF-kLWb&fid=0x0:0x7071d9217f354947"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Gavin Sawle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLKXhLvSjLukpWbwISwzG_LZo19X4tY7GMRNFiHyB4E59XSvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A HUGE shout out to the Terminal Pub last night: we were in a large group for our annual Christmas get together, and the one server we had in particular, was phenomenal. The bar and kitchen staff were great as well, making sure our food and drinks were served as fast as they were ordered.
Thanks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mouse Behave","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJljCheKy1R6LD-pnnLdWkCANUS7SejobG8NXgusm9Jl6gs-gU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I did not like this restaurant at all. The location of the restaurant is pretty sketchy at night with rats crawling all over the ground also it is next to a pornography store. The food was very bad and tasted like it was from the freezer and the portions were skimpy. Do not go here at all costs","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Proctor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU4reTki5_DKZ68y-D-U91LkDlip7ln3Ocfw5-ZSYEfQqSejCW2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very old watering hole in New Westminster, B.C., Canada. Newish owner and beautifully renovated. Very nice ambiance. Expansive beer menu & great food. Our server Astrid was very pleasant & engaging 🍻🥂","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNstrj1dB1m7URoScdnNbh2vZIBjErSh9yIhDxK&fid=0x0:0x7071d9217f354947"],"When":"2023-3-25"},{"Name":"Doodle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCnlmDZcGE9OF2_ELIGqxTNYZaUi5B2FQYO6pK44e8F6Xq3jyI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy and wonderful atmosphere, food was good. Handmade burger patties, and pretty sure the onion rings are made in house as well. Was surprised at first that I only got like 7 onion rings, but they are deceptively filling and really good.

Kind of farther off from things, which means there is a quieter crowd","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dean Rau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtvbv_2m5DukfoxGm0h-R0KwmwKsEIh2vPZUq-TO1J_DjAcLZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Moe is a charming man. Smooth and cool, quietly deserving respect. Represents the Terminal Pub most proper. The menu was most reasonably priced although my visit was too short to sample all that was offered, I will be back. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Maral H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv9KWxZkzAlGbT8_izCalAvL5ZD65gRqiUFXh0ROKqHLjdrt07=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not gonna lie . I was a little hesitant walking into Match (New West location) because it’s wasn’t busy but  I love how it was so  spacious ,I also noticed the different party rooms .
Glad I got to check it out tonight !
My Bartender “Ally” was very attentive and super friendly .  I trusted Ally with all the recommendations because Ally’s input was genuine and honest.  .

Had the Alfredo and shrimp dish and I wanted extra mushrooms and Ally was super accommodating and made it happen . Food was delicious and I got dessert to take home with me . I would definitely come back again. …
🤔 Maybe even book a private party there in the near future !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOILSgSYR27Y7HUtI0rGuXDTKFvxY4WCYvVe0CB&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Lydia Nathe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLN11wGOZlYbj2mxrkEpJC0C13ReaBejQPo_-hozaWwTeXumA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food was terrible. The fact that there were so many different menus should have been the fist clue. I went for brunch and ordered a blackened shrimp benny. This consisted of 1 single tiny shrimp per Benny with the tiniest splash of hollandaise sauce, no flavor and dry. I couldn't even finish it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5Ofik1qCst-RcCDgqacobl-OdpLX4He1qrVJq&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Dan Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbNeFUlLkRmjcX25zxpAW7H_0IDjY0P_SfdPGvxnigSNv-OQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We stopped in for dinner after an afternoon of shopping at Queensborough Landing and we were seated right away. Food is always reliable here and there are multiple sport screens for your entertainment. We ordered the Thanksgiving special turkey dinner and the 1/2 rack bbq ribs with chicken and subbed mashed potatoes for fries-both were delicious!
Service was efficient,food was hot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPy_FTWHqZosJkliAtnezYOU6EW6icdWxym65ZV&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Jordana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJvxqFr8nGL8vok-SCRwxhp2_EJmOiFDFc3qAUH70xw1rrHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for a Saturday lunch with my family. It was fairly quiet which was nice. We were seated right away and the server was attentive. Ordered nachos and the beef dip
The nachos tasted great, not too salty and just the right amount of toppings. The chips were placed on a piece of tortilla so once yoyu've eaten all the chips, you could fold the tortilla and eat it with toppings that fell into it. Thought it was a great idea. The chips however were not crunchy. It was like stale chips that have been re-baked.
The beef dip was good. Good size and flavor. Ordered it with a side of ceasar salad thinking who messes up salads. Well, if you like eating whole cloves of baked garlic, then this is for you. I was not expecting to find a whole piece of garlic clove when I took a bite off my salad and it threw me off. Not sure if it was intentional but not a fan. Who wants to walk around the casino with garlic breath anyway.
Being it was a slow saturday afternoon - there were only about 5 tables around us-' we expected the washrooms to be clean. The ladies room was kept clean but hubby was disgusted with the mens room, described it as if it was not cleaned from the drinking that occured the night before. We had to tell the host about it and while he was quick to call someome to clean it, it should have been done without us having to ask them to do so.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZplm2z0ayKrtqPeLabwFidkci-dviicRQiEx7&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Lisa Avery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0uWvek94xw9hceZaor7-wGRHhxzIOVcSdxuCqWSKZC0HUDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly and efficient Gill was our amazing server and she was on top of everything. Super funny, very nice and fast-fast. Nashville Hot Chicken is my go-to here and it was as delicious as ever. The Tuna Bowl and the Heuvos Tacos were great. Thank you Gill!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPja0ZyExbuOpK6-_c4t4Ar2zI6M-Rrf0V76to&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Pam Delfino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVou97WNj_X-lZ_I6WAUZr7ELzzqVVEd-LYy7ydp9dEDslErRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely place to have a nice dinner and drinks! The fried ravioli is a must-try! So delicious. I was so happy to see Goose Island IPA on tap here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOKwXcakWHjZc55vrWM0xXJa9UZj-GGFoIyOPc6&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Harmeen Grewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6oMbvuFAad35H3E9C4dkq0m-eZv18ucrsWsuAfPgn07nMwE8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Horrible service! Asked the manager there who claims he’s the general manager for his name and he said he doesn’t need to share that. If you stand by your business, you shouldn’t need to hide your name. Very unprofessional. Just look at the picture of the water they service and instead of saying sorry about that and tries to explain the situation, he says I changed your water didn’t I? Very rude and unprofessional. Clearly too young to be able to handle the position he claims. The staffs are overworked and they need to do better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWh2R0zBT6XXtwHvK2q9AFBas0V51wghAawjKP&fid=0x0:0x960938093c50e642"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Lilian Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeGvMKjLmGYYsJTNuBD99YNR1QBuoPNEayiKi_IYfH8GzSOqXQSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Match Eatery and Public House is an underrated treasure that has much more to offer than your average pub. Everything is always fresh, delicious, and thoughtfully prepared.

The happy hour deals are great, and the service is always friendly and attentive. They have private rooms that can be used for hosting events, making this place very suitable for gatherings or celebrations. If you are in search of a great atmosphere, excellent food, and versatility in the available spaces, this is the place!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Aswathy Suresh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKR4DNly6qkrVukYEpwNeGLo6K3j-A3IXF_3S8Thv5C4UG9m5MDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing pastries and food! Loved the wide selection of baked goods. Their soups are a must try item too. A little expensive than a regular place but definitely worth it! ❤️ they have a few seatings as well that makes it perfect!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFGPROsk2eyL7kJh7YsEwvKtHKniriS7MEINdm&fid=0x0:0x794342313d9db356"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Lili","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXQ1YDJ3vKwnOGdGauq84pYUty9Kxg-WhSB7nK7iE6p3_NQzEb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came here on a whim and we’re so glad that we did! The selection is amazing and the service was impeccable. Everyone was very friendly and welcoming. We got the frappuccino cube croissant, the cheddar green onion pastry, and coffee and all of it was delicious. We are eager to try their sausage rolls, lunch special, and napoleon cake next time. We will definitely be back and recommending this place to everyone we know!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMte7PSJJoA46TIt6e_eMD1d-MWgZGeNB4tbCh3&fid=0x0:0x794342313d9db356"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Sarah Krause","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZFN0jiGeG1c32AkF_EU0Xm1U_pcjd6TG768XDzbm7kzvC6HdAQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Found this cute spot off of sixth street as part of the croissant crawl! I was hoping to try their offering but it had sold out by the time I got there (definitely preorder if you’re interested). I instead chose a cheese and green onion pastry out of the case and it was delicious! Fantastic flavour with a nice, flaky pastry. Make sure to have it heated up. Staff were very friendly and the place is very cozy. Limited seating area so perhaps plan to take your food on the go if you go at peak hours.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxijOoArGCrGod6V8P5PXIvJklxm03Ka1lTNxF&fid=0x0:0x794342313d9db356"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Found this small spot that’s right next to 106 bus stop in New West. Delicious cakes and baked goods available.

Limited options for people who do not consume pork, but they have same dishes replaced with mushrooms and a few dishes with chicken.

We tried chicken and mushroom crepe, great in taste and napoleon cake that’s not sugary, but delicious.

Items stated in menu are descriptive with the ingredients making our lives easy to decide what to order.

A few seatings are set up for about 10 people inside the store and most of the chairs and tables are available for dine in.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLse40VPo7psOb2Xb0CMhKZy3XhpsrT-QmrcbZ-GpwAJ3xY-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Thirsty Duck Pub, locally known as the duck, is a pub style restaurant located within a 2 storey commercial plaza located in New Westminster, BC.

There was a dedicated parking lot located on the west side of the building, along with plenty of street parking available. The business can also be easily accessed via public transit, with 3 bus stop routes within 1 block for buses: 112, 101, and 155.

Visited during on a Sunday, we attended in conjuction with "New West Bar Bingo" a summer event typically during the months of July and August where local pubs fill in bingo cards for our visit. This review is independent of this event.

My server was Sanya who was attentive, provided the menus, and knowledgeable of my inquiries related to specials and food items. The included photos are of the 2 piece fish and chips and Molson Canadian draft. We have also included the specials for Sunday and the specials for the other days.

There were other activities available within the pub: golf, pull tab, pool. We did not partake in these and are not able to comment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPuxPScwzVf9Wxds4AwojOlwCJilmeqVb5zPrw&fid=0x0:0xf4faab3b99eb0b32"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Lin Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkZxWl4sTnV0qUNCKgH6Xz67aqb6wJFDJMEKfZK-SKxlPe0Jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friends and I love this place so much! The food is really good 👍 so does the beers. Cheaper price better quality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzURDEWiB5DQI64aDha0h38q0lYEeG5v8Hzi7J&fid=0x0:0xf4faab3b99eb0b32"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Paul Emm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrHN6ljObkZCHQSZglsXTYFI5wNGoNb9MdtyTrcMx7f0WYTq6v=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"honestly, Tara is the 💣 like a ninja she was flying from table to table; dropping off drinks/food, pouring beers, cocktailing, and entertaining guests. the burger 🍔. cheap pints. it's no BS. no corporate attitude and a genuine atmosphere all around. if you want honest, genuine service from human beings this is where to go. and if you come in with that in mind, you begin to notice reality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEmXayqkVRKOhjqsEsPkjTjsyxcDkeCONFF9jm&fid=0x0:0xf4faab3b99eb0b32"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"Danilo Parise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEmaN_tvXQA_zBcPC31zgEgYBytQhr-WQVRdcj1Qf3aggiY-jLzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, drinks, and service offered at a reasonable price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvB-KH-gTXkmHvx9qnMM_E52h0I7I1d7aJeW0p&fid=0x0:0xf4faab3b99eb0b32"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Deb PS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2JrjvxBJWPrjHCwBxV9NiRybb9V5GJpynDBuSW5sd6snYZiMa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A casual pub.  Pretty standard pub fare. The server, Tara, is outstanding.  Never seen such a bubbly, efficient waitress!!  The owner is a very friendly guy who I’ve seen checking in with his patrons.  The building itself, while very clean and well kept, is a tad outdated but a fun time can be had by all.  Lively music.  Gotta try the Duck burger!  Not duck meat but it’s huge and delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpZ5C3v2H-NwAVrNsaYAoUd9rJ2gWtp-R33fv5&fid=0x0:0xf4faab3b99eb0b32"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Harry Peter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPJbxBQfOg_NN8f0S3Er_-PRFWV1F7v7D1hg9JTf_XgvWotpsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I personally enjoy the good liquor and atmosphere at very fair prices all day. There Is happy hour on Wednesday and Friday where a shot of Jack is 4$. The fish and chips were superb. Overall a very decent bar which sports a pool table(or snookers, I'm not conversant in it to tell the difference). Although I found that the main waitress/bartender was very prejudiced to my friends and I. Hence the mid rating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtCJUCwY6TKfNNR32tOr3wgIazfSa38kkVW5ma&fid=0x0:0xf4faab3b99eb0b32"],"When":"2022-7-8"},{"Name":"Kyle Giroux","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHOLsWEpFCtHEVOX_wy6D8L0NN6uiLxWungvDHrEWqWsEryWed=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great service. Great staff, friendly but blunt.   Typical dive bar vibe.    Food isn't as good as there other locations like  juniors on Commercial.  But still great specials and good meals.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terry Confooscius Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFJ-aXdJZsVUNNyzHlSFBMggl7behBpRZh9uV7Gs53TQBEno8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Though I'm not a fan of marching up stairs to get to anything.
The Thirsty Duck is a comfy little pub.
Has a pool table. Free on tues I believe.
Food is above average. With daily specials.
What absolutely stands out. Is the do it all bartender. If the Flash was a real person. She would be it.
It is fascinating to watch her crank out drink after drink. Serve food and clean up after a group has left.
Hey! Tara! If you see this. Pat yourself on the back. And treat yourself to that Mama burger.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Elizabeth Ming","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX33RyY8-iglCLkdHTZbk2rTuFja_RqThRy2Lcpny3eTiwJImVo_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moody Park in New Westminster, BC, is a beloved community space offering a mix of recreational facilities, lush green spaces, and amenities for all ages. Spread across 23.78 acres, this park serves as both a historical landmark, established in 1863, and a modern hub for outdoor activities. Visitors enjoy a wide variety of amenities, including tennis and basketball courts, a soccer field, and a popular outdoor pool. For families, there’s a spacious playground and picnic areas, making it an ideal spot for gatherings and relaxation.

One standout feature is the park’s off-leash dog area, where pets can play freely, which adds to its community-friendly vibe. Moody Park also has walking trails that provide a peaceful escape, appealing to those looking for a quick nature retreat in the middle of the city. The park’s well-maintained landscaping and open spaces make it a popular spot for locals to unwind or get active. Known for its welcoming atmosphere, Moody Park serves as a vibrant center for New Westminster residents, offering a balance of sports, relaxation, and family-friendly activities in a beautiful, historical setting.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hetav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTEABluu0ZHydd-_pKzy9AR1Q7QNXTfCiCNEppfSliIPlyeO53OA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best park near me! It has a calisthenics gym, children's play area, a beautiful soccer field and a dog park. What else could you ask for!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Quan Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-pZoPYeXOZPMkFMWnt3iHTw-bLVVD4nPlpNeu5CixkZ08tZvrEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moody Park is a nice experience with seniors and junior. Big field. Versatile games. Easy commute. Close to everywhere including elementary and secondary schools, walmart, save on, shopper drugmart, few gas bars, banks, and so on so forth. The parking is availble from everywhere. Tennis courts and outdoor pools are also available there","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyevEEhXLmQsO-4poSWpGtPOtXFAC4t0oij2WU&fid=0x0:0xe787c0be445e1b74"],"When":"2023-10-1"},{"Name":"Karthi Anbu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTx3rY_GsKdr7No74d0YOU2O5bUPpBPGGzV67ouiS7JqR5GBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice and big park in New Westminster. Loads of activities for kids and all for adults as well. Even a separate play area for dogs. Table tennis, swing, slider, seesaw, water fountain for kids, football ground, swimming pools, basket ball and tennis court. Baseball ground as well. Also dawn till dusk washroom too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHaMv_WC17E_LxKiLhap-tR53NkjLnb1N0HOhb&fid=0x0:0xe787c0be445e1b74"],"When":"2023-9-15"},{"Name":"Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtVbw3LWLaMOs-vKrJqAoq5Q15-W3unDzK3u_6GbvYxZoaMlY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"a big lawn with lots of tall trees in central of the new Westminster city. good for walk and kids, family and even dog, there is a dog leash small area inside of it. Beside, it has restroom.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmn8s6-V6Bypx-OYDE2YYpMItL6RXvmFrOSJcd&fid=0x0:0xe787c0be445e1b74"],"When":"2023-2-14"},{"Name":"Ives Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYolnMQQL_5qKu_rJogqd-EJBONc9sjWWbbss_4UgIZLch5rJRVg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great playground for kids of all ages. They will likely spend more than 30 minutes here swinging, making friends, playing on the sand, sliding down, spinning and running around, or letting the water flow out of the gates. There are plenty of benches for parents/guardians to sit and watch. Parking lot is close to the playground. Nice to have a washroom nearby and free city wifi.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPX8WHVi1oGMWBTh8OUPzJN5CMTdOOg2--gHC30&fid=0x0:0xe787c0be445e1b74"],"When":"2020-6-27"},{"Name":"Tiber Dacicus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFAC90h_rnjLf5Ha7MJZYeSIUtb6PxWlPr-ZqpuK7nlRMW2RF_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Locally,  the perfect place to spend your summer.
This place has recently suffered a series of modifications. The children playground was rebuilt. Closed with fence, there is a place for domestic animals. The park has a soccer terrain and also offers the possibility to play basketball or tennis. The pool opens in the summer and is very popular, attracting many kids. The park is a good place to organize potlucks or other anniversaries.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVYuGEGDM6uzd3NnLAAuWZENzqOcx56kvnldPB&fid=0x0:0xe787c0be445e1b74"],"When":"2018-2-8"},{"Name":"Patrick S Callan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRLiozUAOanyO2HomvPc0QqnbpZ48n2oTTO2cQXhLSd4fUFIxh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The idea for Moody Square and its park came about in the early 1860"s and soon developed into a recreational area with its first game field constructed in the early 1890's.The park progressed quickly with its first playground in 1922,
the Kiwanis Clubhouse 1938,
Century House Senior Centre and
Parks and Rec Office 1958,
Lawn Bowling Club 1979,
Commerative Stone Monument 1984.
The park caters to multiple sports including tennis, basketball, box lacrosse,swimming, soccer and baseball  and has public restrooms, concession stand,super cool outdoor romper room for kids, outdoor off leash area for 🐕 and the WestMinster Youth Centre.
The tall iron Clock adds a nice feature to the entrance of the shaded diagnol walkways lined with various mature trees. The parks tree varieties include Horse Chestnut, Oregon White Oak, Giant Filbert,Western Red Cedar, Northern White Cedar,Monkey Puzzle,American Holly,Big Leaf Maple Douglass Fir,Red Maple  and Western Hemlock.
Colonel Richard Clement Moody of The British Royal Engineers,responsible for the early development of New WestMinster as the capital of the Colony of British Columbia , has the honor of the parks name.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJsKBIL-sAU5Ont7VguLMCByr1E64YpdZINq-N&fid=0x0:0xe787c0be445e1b74"],"When":"2022-6-19"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"ToothGirl95","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn0pBE1Ul3bbrdANB5-s3pApc-nG2NQfEfySUkvLdPRY1ctuON=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food every single time. Japanese restaurants are usually expensive so considering their menus pricing, it’s worth it. The presentation of the food is good, and the signature pink rice is cute. The quality of the sushi matched the presentation, which made the meal overall satisfying to eat. We left feeling satisfied and would definitely recommend this place to others. 🍣","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSDvDXUYT5MGpLQGBlyboapzzBHwn-lqRmK1WM\u0026fid=0x0:0x97b035f9eac120db"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Chris Kwon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQHaMHN9MM3-tIDhR3o7wscanLYvGVlZeWbXSV3N1HKmullA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Sushi Well with my wife, and it was a fantastic experience! The sushi was fresh, flavorful, and beautifully presented. The service was attentive and friendly, making the experience even more enjoyable. What really stood out though, were the handmade sauces. Each sauce was incredible, enhancing the flavors of the sushi without overpowering them. I would definitely recommend Sushi Well to anyone looking for top-notch sushi and a delightful dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiMpE0N_zvNdGCECYQ6tiLCtHoucnbJ7S4FfvI\u0026fid=0x0:0x97b035f9eac120db"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Yulim Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgBbgLR3e1fllxpGCqpj6FIubu1JlbgIFcSx9FWVKJrCMoEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best sushi place in town! We started with gomaae, and the house-made sesame dressing was so incredible (everyone should try this as an appetizer!). We also had sushi - the house special roll, hot night tuna roll, and toro aburi nigiri. They were all fresh and flavourful, especially the healthy pink sushi rice, which made them even more special. Not to mention, the staff and owner were friendly, and the interior was clean, making the dining experience a pleasure. I would definitely return and highly recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM00rmDrQ4HgJ-G8HPiHmq-6xxWf0lXr71w707\u0026fid=0x0:0x97b035f9eac120db"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Ellie Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEWFMvxBUq1XfREveUfx30eYCbio6d3g6g32o_T9ft1pRBFA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was incredibly fresh, and everything tasted amazing! The sashimi was, of course, delicious and fresh, and the tempura was so crispy that I could tell they used clean oil. All the staff were very friendly, making it a wonderful dinner experience. A big thank you to all the staff~^^","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZRQ7AII_P7WV-NLTnFL8-umnSl8PiYGdzXhMZ\u0026fid=0x0:0x97b035f9eac120db"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Philip Koo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFXlTIEzx0GCrROnCf9X65djCyj8540d5JS-5AJQ1Se3bTTA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great sushi place! The food quality was exceptional and every dish we had was delicious. The service was great as well. Only positive things to say about this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJwsDgPJcH1zhvUsOEZ8XKDVckexHcm4DBgppm\u0026fid=0x0:0x97b035f9eac120db"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Connie Rim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsZiY3uVBXDaDLoBsDpMrytczfI49R5dBVoMzl88snCz21-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a gem of a neighborhood sushi spot! Every dish we tried was fabulous, and the service was exceptional. The staff were super friendly, and the sushi was incredibly fresh. The appetizers or dishes other than sushi were also amazing. My top three favorites were the gomae, angry jalapeno, and aburi toro nigiri. I would definitely return and highly recommend this place to others!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0CZFSzjKAHy2cnTiVPCQWe1wmSDIbvn9yLtUT\u0026fid=0x0:0x97b035f9eac120db"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Denis Santos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF32K7mKkPkKCpGUSEjmRXhqYloH84bwlSW6sQJ_X-vjOnAtXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a regular costumer of Sushi Well since its days at the previous location, and they consistently deliver a wonderful dining experience. The sushi is always fresh and delicious, and the service is consistently attentive and friendly. Whether you're dining in or ordering takeout, you can expect prompt and efficient service. Overall, Sushi Well is a fantastic choice for anyone craving great sushi in a welcoming atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPENSinmJagT--2vZUCCLgmyW5dN6VDzMuHM6dL\u0026fid=0x0:0x97b035f9eac120db"],"When":"2024-5-23"}]
