user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Shirley Ann Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTufZ1O7YNqmevegFQNEbK68BixarB9ooeJyWD92O9OkSBiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went to the Starlight casino with some friends for the first time in years. The band famous players was on that night. I wish I had the words to describe how amazing they are! From their talented voices to the theatrics and drama on stage , it was incredible. The chemistry between the two lead singers kept all of us engaged. The dance floor was full at all times. If you want a good night out with some good music, I would strongly recommend the Starlight lounge when famous players is scheduled.
Unfortunately, I wish I could say the same for the service and the food. I had the South Beach salad . My avocado was brown on places and I asked for Caesar dressing and I got mayonnaise. One. I spoke to the waitress. Said she would bring me ranch. The waitress was very sweet but not very good at her job! She would take one order, walk away, do that, and then come back and dig another order as opposed to taking all of our orders and requests at the same time. She would bring us our food but not come back and ask us if we needed anything and we would have to literally wave her down. At times people waited in extremely long time to have coffee, refilled or even another drink order. Because the band was so amazing. I will go back to the Starlight lounge. Probably not to eat!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuxVAVKWcz16jTNjmBEUTUSbTReqDKxeWQwJRk&fid=0x0:0x20a80f1560b67cf5"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Larry LaRose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXppqlLBfylyuqrBhgeVpR5HGRMyNCMuGdQGyTi4df8Serhxj2xPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at the restaurant in Starlight Casino. Although finding the main entrance was a bit tricky, the moment I walked in, Terry the bartender warmly greeted me and offered a menu. Since I didn’t have my glasses, he kindly helped me choose a meal. I requested a chicken burger on a whole wheat bun, which wasn’t on the menu, but Terry accommodated my request without hesitation. The meal was excellent and served promptly. Terry checked in on me several times, adding to the positive experience. I highly recommend this place for a great lunch!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQSY4I0Cv6hfBblrIAanYSr1or9UY91RE6pvLv&fid=0x0:0x20a80f1560b67cf5"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Mike Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS3TomIjeVsXZOdRPO53t7f3UGdwg-yRZRaS5bbXh_A7qbV4E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"1.  The facility, services, and foods at Starlight Casino in New Westminster BC are inferior and way below bar.
2.	Services have reduced at Starlight Casino in New Westminster BC  drastically over the past six months. Three of the five small coffee machines have been removed for good. Only the two near the washroom at the far end remains, often broken. IT IS INSULTING TO the patrons when the Starlight Casino in New Westminster management CLAIM MORE SERVICES and were "excited" when they REDUCING them FROM 5 TO 2.
3.The swiping incentive is useless these days  The rewards have reduced to a few silly credits are insulting . You might as well remove and dump the swiping machines.
4.	Buffet is practically closed - some snacks remain. Buffet used to be a very popular and well-liked place to eat and drink. But since the price has doubled, services reduced and poor foods, Starlight casino practically “killed” the popular venue.
5.	 Most popular slot machines have been removed for good and more card tables added. Less and less patrons could be seen at the Starlight Casino these days. My friends and myself now rather go to River Rock Casino.
6.	In sum, the management of Starlight Casino in New Westminster BC should be reviewed and replaced. We do not want to see it closed which will happen if the present management continues their unpopular, unfriendly and ridiculous services.
7.	I am so unhappy that I did not even bother to check my typos and grammatical mistakes as that would just waste more of my time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNReVZP-w6JDEcHhpnXDFAf0jy6f1qVIOjodzw&fid=0x0:0x20a80f1560b67cf5"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Frank Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqU7w4lL0DBsy1BjK_cj8vbNltIdZkHHYfmHo3u05AoSN2BGW5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for lunch on Sunday. It's a reasonable price for $22.
The one you have to try: Asian Stew Beef, Asian stew park with black bean, corn soup and potato salad. Eggs is also great which is right time cooked with soft and fresh taste.
Bacon is not so well, and it's over cooked and too dry.
I came to Riverock and Delta casino for buffet before, and I have to say Starlight is the best of those three.
Starlight buffet does  not have too many people which I can really enjoy the meal.
The working people there are really friendly with nice smile and warm welcome. They even become old friends with some customers.
So, I give 5 stars.
If Starlight Casino can see this, please say thank you for me to those nice persons. And see you soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPShKkrFsdJhTAb64WvnwatE7muegcFe1OUn3AQ&fid=0x0:0x20a80f1560b67cf5"],"When":"2023-12-31"},{"Name":"Kiara Dhriti B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjIdcmsb4752DBdUPvsqf8OBoEihtSuHtnYM3td5WC3zQt_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yesterday i wanted some takeout lunch  and i met the kindest staff member Chichi, who recommended the crispy tofu and bbq pork fried rice. It was absolutely delicious, thank you Chichi, i will be back! :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOr91y2orpmjR33Vj-_d0n_AWD_CefID3IrsAQn&fid=0x0:0x20a80f1560b67cf5"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Hernan Chacon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOKgwShKFhnqzMOzCLMkVoCNqPRkVKtDEDbLYXjQWoIDk19BV2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Starlight Casino in New Westminster, BC, and had an amazing time! The casino offers a fantastic variety of gaming options, including slots, table games, and a dedicated poker room. The atmosphere is vibrant and reminiscent of retro Vegas, which adds a unique charm to the experience.

The dining options are top-notch, with several restaurants to choose from. I particularly enjoyed the food at MATCH Eatery & Public House and the elegant dining experience at ATLAS Steak + Fish. The service was excellent, and the staff were friendly and attentive.

One of the highlights of my visit was the live entertainment. The bands were great, and it was a perfect way to end the evening after some gaming. The casino also features REPLAY, an innovative gaming area that combines traditional games with a party atmosphere – definitely a must-try!

Overall, Starlight Casino is a fantastic destination for a fun night out. Whether you’re there for the gaming, dining, or entertainment, you’re sure to have a memorable experience. Highly recommended!

Feel free to adjust it to better fit your personal experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cristina Buan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2ysFkRBNb41MIJrpe7elu82HIi6CEJZsABL-60VrtsHIh1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really enjoy the food specially the service  .  CHI CHI and CONNIE is the best. Rate them five star.   coming back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUjLq72eY16aoG-RU9iBKguT2uJDaX7vEzar5I&fid=0x0:0x20a80f1560b67cf5"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Rjk Sinn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXLmMIw3IFKjkCcr_Y7hfuqWtQXprcb7_MC8VgL2j0pJc-wg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It was boring as h. They removed lots of slot machines including Kenos. It looks like it's a ghost house no music just people chatting in the background and that's it. People come here to have fun. $500 in 20 minutes.
Avoid it if you don't like empty casino","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPz9mr-kf4v36B004Y6oV0fmIMMHzNSCjJnK438&fid=0x0:0x20a80f1560b67cf5"],"When":"2024-6-5"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Stacy Bohun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7qzTk0Z_bh312ltTEPQYsTQ_AchFTo1bVXqCNkOxE5OXtj0I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Elisse was my waitress. She was amazing, love her energy and quick service!

Will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCOHTRnSyYNgFFt_82UmoryMXs7gisM61aMRw&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They have extremely expensive wings. It is advertised as 1 pound of wings for $14.95 but they only give you 6 wings (which is most definitely not 1 pound of wings). The wings did taste fine though just very small portions. The calamari was also good but came on a very small plate. Drink specials were good.
The service was excellent. Trivia night on Wednesdays are fun.

Overall great for drinks but expensive food and small portions.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpjmcPA2bKzLVxuCdnF7CPGHXvlzTMdk1u0Ud_&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2023-1-20"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We visited this pub a few times, usually in summer to be seated on
their patio area. It offers quite a decent list of beverages. I found their choice of IPAs to be a bit weak, but after pandemic re-opening, they introduced Mariner IPA to the list, and it's a game-changer for me. Service is slow at times, mainly because the place is packed, and there's only one waitress, but it's bearable. We never went past appetizers, but I can tell that wings are good, and mozzarella triangles are nice when cheese stays inside, which doesn't happen always, and you get triangles with no cheese inside. Also, I'm not sure if it's a post-pandemic measure, but now the kitchen closes at 8 pm. For us, somehow missing the last kitchen call, it was the end of the night. One other thing that I really liked, which is not available anymore in COVID-19 reality for very obvious reasons, is that they used to have a popcorn machine where patrons could get a free popcorn – it's genius. I can't say that this pub is perfect, but they are trying to be so, and I can see why many locals like it. Give it a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZEqfi9l4WmpCuAoVPlab--oxMV1YFPfQzXgQi&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2020-6-29"},{"Name":"David 04 Make the World a Better Place","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXmkrAyRsAwad4uDl0EKEwpsCVMLq51IOxmbley55h_iwJzGo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really nice place to drink!
When I went there, it was movie day.
They didnt serve food;; But service was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCoro3kVbx6q0upeAPkj2vFcHskUDIx7khzCA&fid=0x0:0x9c9003e401143fea"],"When":"2023-7-13"},{"Name":"Sean Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjbgELxR0qim_ljk8eaK8OgzP61UXXAqq-zknTzwLJdAueKkc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I like this place. The fact that they have Heineken on tap is a big plus for me, because it's my favourite beer. This place has a great selection of beers on tap. I've never tried the food here, so I don't have an opinion about it. The staff is friendly and I have had nothing but good experiences every time I've come here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Spoke Spurr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6SBXwfGoUXIMfCRHI82vggrz0MEiQ4COzIjzyCQuY_w8CfkTv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We must’ve picked an incredibly poor Saturday afternoon. A dozen lonely, sad men sitting at individual tables. It was as if we walked into Moe‘s Tavern of Simpson fame.
Dreary.
We left.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chowder Head","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwlpI7DoMMgrt2BIfQlFGVP_FkXyOuSIv5tzHDvkSUHslBPM4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"My big pet peeve is places that advertise beer special prices that don't include alcohol tax.

$5.45 beer special? 4 of them plus tip ran me over $40. Dirty pool Hops.... Dirty pool..

Service that was completely indifferent.  Thursday just after 9pm kitchen already closed.

It's really close to the skytrain and that's its best feature.

There's superior options to this place within 5 minutes walk.

Really disappointed as I'd seen it there for so long. This was just my experience and with some like this I won't review until I've gone a few times but there's no way I'm ever going back there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Straver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWToLMyoie5tYNi3FxHCGKh7tJbpoBo5POEd0V1juGjM4ChsMJT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New to New West, but come here often for drinks. Never had their food before but their customer service is so great I didn't want to leave a bad impression. Really friendly staff/locals and great prices.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Sheren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwgWVtP6HKMkhFLCP4_q1L6Sudo7ufb7ryQD3i3kJwLQlCuUZm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another hidden gem in New West!!
IT CHAR BURGER✨
We tried 6oz beef patty and regular poutine~ we pair up booster juice at the corner of the plaza (best combination!)
Overall, IT CHAR BURGER is a delightful experience for any burger lover. The combination of caramelized onion  and poutine truly sets it apart. Highly recommended for your next outing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSoI99r0D6-VzhlimhJ7yuQUQCddWEWdBkpEM3&fid=0x0:0xe238a4ca33d05c44"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Mitchell Santaga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGbT6qBhnvTLMkeYSrzDT742LG11G2ZbTbwbsUENtd3qFk3CFj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Burgers are delicious. Staff is friendly. Service is pretty quick. Ingredients always seem fresh. And I find their burger easy to eat without too much mess which is nice when it's to go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOylK1ZZH5LyOp5kStSkGL0cbOHZVZNQZBVF-jj&fid=0x0:0xe238a4ca33d05c44"],"When":"2024-8-28"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I think it was back in 2014 that I first came across this hidden gem of a burger joint in New West. Located in Royal Square Mall, their signature IT char burger used to cost $7.85 and came with fries. I've been back many times over the years just to have this burger.  They do have other food here but you can't go wrong with this burger.

I came back in April 2024 and their burger was still fairly reasonable given inflation. The fries were super crispy (pro tip: order a side of their thick gravy). While the fries had lots of little bits (instead of big fries), I love those small crispy bits. The burger was as good as ever with crisp bacon, double patties and caramelized onions.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFiVHQSmFqq2EhzLgegqn6OdjdeECW_eFUAf5P&fid=0x0:0xe238a4ca33d05c44"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Clarke Stanbra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWR0Bc-A4VL6RoU2ST5sfMK7jwFbuXT7nZVkkjSWVQYKzegb2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I regret not taking photos, so maybe next time. I had their IT Char burger and small poutine. I have read reviews and heard good things, but I tried to go into it with moderate expectations. Honestly, it was just delicious. The reviews were right, the burger tasted so fresh and perfect. The poutine is actually as good or maybe even better than Anny’s - mostly because the fries were so crispy/crunchy and had so many little crunchy fry-bits mixed in with normal fries. Looking forward to going back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfWCb-Y3ju3_ohgtgfTv7gwO2193KdzHGaY7xO&fid=0x0:0xe238a4ca33d05c44"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"Jackson Pisony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwBZuk96e8Qu9zQ_PHreC6GMfXsqbXMM55OAWZq5i5zceGtAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Korean burger was unbelievable! Had to get a chili dog to wash it down because it was so juicy and fresh. I'm still hungry but figured I'd write a review before ordering another burger. Service was top tier and for a local burger spot in the mall I will be back to eat all the burgers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lekha Reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmJGhl1-4gmLsjhODLv0EBv4db0I65Xj_LQ4N38nJXAbHQF354=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Finally got to try this place, ordered IT Char burger with garlic fries and grilled Chicken burger. ITC burger for my partner enjoyed so very much, with double patty which was juicy. The grilled chicken burger was good, would have liked it but more spices. The garlic fries were very very disappointing, we picked up the food and started eating at food court, yet they were so oily and soggy. Lots of tables in this quiet mall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUqNXp60j2bMxD_OdSt6hQ4-LfhzqVAGnMeoiQ&fid=0x0:0xe238a4ca33d05c44"],"When":"2023-10-21"},{"Name":"Grace J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbSm3Y5q5Ek-OjRs_emYL_wsewOI3LFkKwt62VrypDp0G7BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"OMG!!! Really glad I got told to try this spot out! Absolute GEM in New West. I got the BBQ burger and garlic fries. I'm so happy to find a place that nailed good food in this cozy city! Burger was so juicy and gobbled up in a few minutes. It's so hard to find handcut fries that are crispy but look no further!!! Every single fry I had was so nice and crunchy on the outside with that nice soft texture inside. The sweet lady helping me made me feel so welcome! Definitely a go-to spot from now on! Do yourself a favor and go check them out!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daytona Bleach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRaHoyOfUXZIdM-K7u63iFvg3c_i--vYDOcPSkbIIkQI8s5-6r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"IT CHAR, how I love thee! Best burgers and fries in town. I don't live nearby so only eat here every few months but I lust after the delicious taste. Juicy char grilled burgers oozing with sauce and omg the garlic parmesan fries! Delicious. If you get takeout the trapped heat will steam the fries and they get soggy (but still delicious) however if eaten fresh they are very crispy.

The past couple visits I ordered the spicy BBQ as the It char burger is too much food at once for me. For two people, two orders of the spicy BBQ burger and one order of garlic fries comes to just over $20 with tip. Amazing value for the quality. It didn't take long either under ten minutes and all made fresh to order.

P.S. I don't get why people diss the mall, it's actually beautiful architecture and really nice sculpture in the middle and nice natural lighting. Exudes a pleasant vintage vibe and I love the small vegetable fruit market, dollar store and of course liquor store. Various other utility type stores I haven't been to.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9tymp54OBhn11hHqoa6SOfhf1ElKjL_cDjZPH&fid=0x0:0xe238a4ca33d05c44"],"When":"2021-7-24"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Nancy Matheson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk5JapRWJRE3sgf_dJc_0VJ626j2pZIK6ClGFC9OU0izL5Pg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We initially started eating here during COVID to support a local business.  They did excellent takeout, and we have been regular customers ever since.  Fresh, tasty food and really lovely people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1mgA_VcTPZ-qgfngoy2QN3gLNZDQC2oeWpWn3\u0026fid=0x0:0xe0893b2f51a5f111"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Angie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyUjdZQkz0bhaDppuQsySaOzrLROWSfhKe7zzOgxtMex30Fg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We ordered tom yum goong soup which was passable, and pad Thai - this was extremely bland, missing major ingredients such as fish sauce, lime, bean sprouts, garlic, shallots, and peanuts.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMllZl27xAieQqOaxQax6XYM8m2tDV0uB-Fq5fl\u0026fid=0x0:0xe0893b2f51a5f111"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"R M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_fz1ppRTsIp4sjPAQMlDnN0i9UFP0hSxVQWeP4OaNSz_YsQXRew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We randomly stumbled across this restaurant, and I'm glad we tried it out. We were greeted by the owner and promptly served with menus and water. The menu is relatively small but packs in the main dishes you're seeking for within Thai cuisine staples.\nI've dined at many Thai restaurants and am always quietly impressed when Tom Yum is done well and has a good balance of sweet, sour and heat! The spiciness is accurate, so go easy when selecting how hot (spicy) you like your dishes. Thai iced tea and coffee are always a must, and now that mangoes are back in season, the sticky rice dessert with mango is my favorite go-to. Thank you for the excellent service and great conversation, Teg. Will definitely be back to try out the massaman curry!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTAuOLtVWKJYgaZYrY5m1nhy_6HZ-QkcFfC-fw\u0026fid=0x0:0xe0893b2f51a5f111"],"When":"2023-4-29"},{"Name":"Caroline F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFeqi-yOkJqxICGJeCmlK4j8ZRrRYo85n_bkRB4GiJhIL8HJP9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is a small place but it felt like we're in a fine dining restaurant minus the white linen with a spa-like ambience. For a moment we forgot about Covid as this place is extremely clean. Food is superb! Flavourful that you could taste everything was prepared from scratch (except the ice cream). The Thai New West Restaurant is now my favourite Thai restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqm4PSd89B1-fOrPANUviN_hOZ3rMAzWAywa_J\u0026fid=0x0:0xe0893b2f51a5f111"],"When":"2020-7-26"},{"Name":"Ronnie Fuentes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_IBfCGDDPlKvoPzChsWn1cYiD0BLL-FbNvkztm1LQLWKNGPF8AA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is our new go-to restaurant for Thai food. The portions are smaller compared to other Thai eateries, but the flavours make up for their lack in size. Our regular favourites like curry and lettuce wraps taste better here! The smaller servings mean there's room for dessert. We tried the deep-fried plantains and they were satisfying. Needless to say, we're definitely coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQQRnrWLwLkleUJ3jXFbXoyej58yInMkuULSGW\u0026fid=0x0:0xe0893b2f51a5f111"],"When":"2020-8-4"},{"Name":"lisa price","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsu5QjBnqL_f3adtqVTqJaZEdzF8hsrmHAwnhS_YiCP858zg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We just love Vara and Teg and this family run restaurant and its warm atmosphere . The food is always delicious and can be tailor made for people who can’t handle spicy food ( we order mild for my hubby and she brings out chilis for me to add to my plate). We especially love the red curry , the lettuce wraps , and the massamum curry, but everything is delicious . Support this family restaurant , you won’t regret it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNejeR9rGOTs4muKQi5CCRxC4ngDWxZYPw41o81\u0026fid=0x0:0xe0893b2f51a5f111"],"When":"2023-12-23"},{"Name":"Jacob McKenna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHRaMEXUe7PB73-XrtucnrYWgzt_WVsPfdlvk2Sc0AV8_4vRLn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So after seeing so many reviews of this place on the eat new west Facebook group it was time to try out Thai New West. The dishes were very well constructed with lovely presentation and tasted so very good. Our server was very kind, friendly and helpful. I had the Pad Med Ma Muang and I thoroughly enjoyed it. My husband had the Pad Bai Horpa. *Big* bonus that our dishes had more meat than vegetables which is not the normal and the vegetables were very fresh tasting. My husband finished with Black Rice Pudding. He (really) enjoyed it. I was too full to try it. We will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8VMQY0_60MlgWZDrXNhq0uAA25iItGaUYof0Q\u0026fid=0x0:0xe0893b2f51a5f111"],"When":"2020-8-28"},{"Name":"Debra S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTYLdPBtEcDEMVxJVptB4k7pnVENuzg4bSivAoKMDe15sf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We found this little gem on a long walk and decided to give it a try after wandering around the area looking for a place to eat. The owner was so friendly and the service and food were great. We really enjoyed our lunch and the wonderful chat with the owner. Portions are generous, prices very reasonable, and we each had leftovers to take home. We’ll be back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Priscilla Pizarro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5Yf0cv1kEeMxkrQm3TQr3gbvKHirAYZBqqLuc2nVFcoTVP4uXGw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I had an issue and the owner reached out to make it right.
It was not an issue with the quality, but an issue of a new employee stating the pieces were chicken breast when it was mixed dark meet which I unfortunately can't stomach.
Kindly the owner reached out and explained that the nice girl was new and just not properly trained yet on what the protein cuts were. I will send my husband to try a lunch on the boss when he works in New West some day. I live an hour aways that's too far to go for the kind
(olive branch) refund.

Presentation
Cute small fork was all nice-
Just unfortunately a no go for me due to being mixed dark meats.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_al0-qu_dxG3gMdRU_70tU-j6IihFFXSQmEQg&fid=0x0:0x120414dc7286aaa8"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"only4 android1","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7M7Xvem0vhnrqhdrfQ3QjiwSznQTye4paDizCMcyNxGxyCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I love Chicko Chicken. The locations are pretty consistent, too. Everything is cooked nicely.  The fries taste good.  Love the pickled radish.  Minus 1 star because the green onions are not always fresh so I stopped ordering them. Other than that it's a solid place","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food ordered for take out was hot and fresh. We ordered the yangyeom half chicken, the shake shake fries, and the pickled radish. The yangyeom had a good amount of flavour and the chicken was crispy with plenty of sauce. The shake shake fries came with a packet of cheese snow and you combined it in the paper bag with the fries and shook it. Quick order and pick up, took only 15 minutes for everything to be made. Lots of parking in the plaza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6Y0vG3dalQfwHVadPS0vvMx-MW_W-XphYUwAU&fid=0x0:0x120414dc7286aaa8"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Ada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_tT85lO7aZKFfq17wWpo8ldgI_n0GJFJfBhG1nWiEa2zXCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've always had positive experiences with Chicko Chicken. I love that each order is made fresh when you order, so each bite is juicy! We ordered half half (snow and original) along with the shake shake fries. The environment was clean and the workers had wore masks. I appreciate that!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKn9Tgz8FGYR1j1ONh2nQi9umjx5zWpwxlyYXF&fid=0x0:0x120414dc7286aaa8"],"When":"2023-1-26"},{"Name":"Timmy Tanger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjj89wDlWhpg-Tm-z8WSIq-5VVIj54AcvwWJU6Fbn0Icsirg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’m a regular customer here. Placed an Uber order today but usually I pick it up most of the time. After delivery,  was shocked to see black and brown, smelly and dry cheese snow chicken. It was not edible and if I ate the old chicken I would get sick. I wouldn’t even risk giving it to my dog. I will never be going back unfortunately.  I called the store and I got a refund on the order through Uber thankfully. In general food is getting more expensive everywhere and the quality of it does not match the high costs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyygr8wuBvcYEim2cgyOGC0MQskrYbn6cgivaB&fid=0x0:0x120414dc7286aaa8"],"When":"2024-1-7"},{"Name":"elissa christiaanse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV084lbgrexQuEjKAMRtCGfhwu01Y7VhhtSPHxKqFRjPKS4a7ss=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and great food! We always walk in when we go. We never have too long of a wait and the foods always good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jude Evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwWTfoiVpwlhMMr4PWosEcWGAa43bLsLrA_MQmA0fmlRyFvAwR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The chicken here is delicious, I mainly go for the orginal flavor. I come here all the time and the staff are super nice every time.
This is a takeout restaurant, while there are tables and chairs its best experienced to eat at home, the "dinning" area is pretty cold in the winter.
Phone in your order, its cheaper, the delivery/pickup apps charge more for the same item even if its just pickup.
Almost always some parking in the small lot infront of the store.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMG56qK-SrXm-tz8ae8Vhlig8EASqR79JwsYBTi&fid=0x0:0x120414dc7286aaa8"],"When":"2023-2-4"},{"Name":"Justbeing Sam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM9hiJK-AfVP-qSHlK2ogC-KKU9aHv9jB-f8Zpy8fNkox9PG5e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Loved the crispness of chicken. I ordered soya garlic n it was super fresh. I really hope they give a signature dip on side or add more sauce to chicken . However it was still very yummy","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2Ay6OG1aG5aYoRnogfMx_5BcbsFARpiNuirPy&fid=0x0:0x120414dc7286aaa8"],"When":"2021-12-20"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Yash Raj Chowdhury","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOHGC7JETruo0Shn4B5gDavOg_xgXSQJbB0nIaCBxjTpujHZg_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited The Babs and had their chicken bowl, which was absolutely delicious. The ambiance was cozy and the place was spotlessly clean. A special shoutout to the staff - the girl who took my order was not only beautiful but also incredibly nice. Definitely planning to return for another delightful meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZhiKm8W133eWW22yW8ct0uW8CuN_EkT-B1MGS\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"Emily Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEvwebxzOOvHfn2UnHwr4i_lsQ_4WBBcdmwEUmGOtZoyfwO9Mg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute little Korean fusion cafe in this area. Their Korean flavour is spot on and the price is quite affordable. If you wanted grab a lunch, at the same time escape the tedium of bland flavours, this place has quite a selection. I tried their bulgogi (spicy bbq pork) sandwich and it was delicious.\nThe place is spacious and clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfTXoP1x-dtA2EomfEHp1m3i2d26lt3i2qh7-x\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Madison G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZsEld-Yz5a2Swm5LesjF83lo03ZXPGgujeQvQiLn6WLaIuGx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cute little local kitchen. Very clean, lots of space and easy to get to. A lot of menu food items. I personally went in looking for a latte or good coffee not knowing that they don’t really carry it. ( They only had regular black coffee you put ur own milk and sugar into) So if you’re looking for a iced coffee or latte this is not the place to go. The breakfast sandwich I had though was delicious though. And the chocolate chip cookie was very gooey. Yum. Hoping I can come back another time to try out their sushi !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOO4N4WzxB9Jq7pit6fLZ4aF07zzuMZzlaApPC4\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Matthew McLean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlhfPx57S7q016i_f_WQBP6Uj7_52S3nX95qUw5zWXIjPFEraL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A cozy little bistro-meets-cafeteria  establishment tucked into the corner of a commercial area of New Westminster, the menu is curated and simple, but executed extremely well. A mix of brunch and lunch items with both North American favourites and Korean staples, everything was made to order and came out hot at the counter/tableside. The prices were extremely reasonable and the portions were sizeable. It felt like I was being cooked for in someone's home in the best way possible. If you're in the area, it is worth checking out. Just be aware that parking is limited so you may have to get a little creative. I ordered the Bulgogi Burger with fries, a BLT sandwich, and Cheese Tteokbokki; the rice cakes were the standout for me, but everything was hot, well seasoned, and made from fresh ingredients.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYQDQeemAlew9Q2oGqZ4ypZcApb3cFNLutorQm\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"JAMES C. LEE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWofAV9QRyUPXqeCXHwXtETshPn8Pq_ozbBWOIXuXDjzfcwl0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I Loved their $10 Chicken Burger! Delicious food and cozy atmosphere! The burger was juicy and flavorful, paired perfectly with crispy fries. The service was friendly and attentive, making for a wonderful dining experience. Highly recommend for anyone looking for a great meal and warm hospitality. Will definitely be returning soon! 3 Parking spot at the Front.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrwy230I7EpWgXUiZb-gW-rxxbTcua4KbGQY8\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"R Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdl_u7y7-NTGig23XmLhjqfUtzqSjas2T55bEhbCohwfYtng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food is simple, home-made and very tasty. Place is very clean. It was deserted and we were there on a Friday lunch hour. The location is off, not in a commercial high traffic area. No visible sign of the business from road, so it can easily be missed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFZw6obBKy453tBqpfhR7ZbeKH9pG_QBerGUl8\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-11-1"},{"Name":"Kelly Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkdgbpd3IeipWCfyOGsnZ1FTFf_gjjwHYa2e7vrPYatmjivQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the spicy pork bowl and it was awesome! The new k-rose tteokbokki was creamy and delicious. Perfect for korean lunch option :) the staff was very friendly and kind so highly recommend if you're in the area and looking for a cozy lunch spot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqe1Ga2-TYzjHXvk6xTqficwqWvAjZAweWmBgR\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Jay Song","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5TzoTAOu86-lU5iS9fNjLywI9NpVlyBNh_KpIJlaySQ84cOS0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such warm atmospheres and friendly staffs. Tried Bulgogi sandwich, cheese Tteokboki and Galbitang. They were all amazing!!  Highly recommend!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdDVh_JA-y17aGMiEfJtpVh3Klrxb68gqqLMsj\u0026fid=0x0:0xca41b8f0850b48ba"],"When":"2024-11-5"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ember Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMNJB74aKKAepkYhrktOEMZlPmYsfglhSTftpz8C9kzNV20Yo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The second we opened our pizza boxes, we knew this was the place for us. Absolutely AMAZING pizza, fresh dough,  tasty ingredients, and impeccable customer service. Highly recommend this pizza, and the location is the perfect distance from transit. Very informative and transparent about ingredients, and accommodation is available for vegans/dairy-free vegetarians.

If I could rate higher than 5 stars, I happily would. Give this place a try, you will certainly not be let down!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONDKMkR-k03sQFoj6VumJc_1lbnk7CZSIft3zi&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"K Volk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdqoSqm_pTdlU9e8Fq66CyWqpdPGbj2-ikus-uGI2GgFFLOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time ordering from this place, one of the very few places in new west with consistently high ratings on google.

Pizza came 20 minutes before their estimated time, and they include a real time tracking option with your email receipt allowing you to see exactly where your order is in the process of being made and delivered. The delivery driver was super friendly, all smiles, and courteous.

The pizzas are heavy weight for all the right reasons, hot, crispy on the outsides and not burned, with generous toppings from edge to edge. Did I mention they weigh a ton?

Highly recommend this place. Great pizzas for the price.

(Taco pizza / tropical Hawaiian with added chicken)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYxzTW97KDrmwWId3pa_EdznzVPU-FKihxTYeQ&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Madeline Yeung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8xXkr3rdhtaU3CcLy3f0wDzhbxjacMKsMkIuTbIcC05n506g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was quite quick. Within 20 minutes of ordering at the till, order was ready. We got the Family Combo which was 1 large pizza (customizable toppings) a pasta and 2 cans of soda. Pepperoni pizza with extra cheese was great. Not too greasy & crispy pepperonis.

The lasagna was.. Not really a lasagna. The top cheese layer was great. But it seemed like the whole rest of the dish was lacking. It seemed like linguine with tomato sauce. No flat layers of lasgna pasta and no layers of ricotta cheese in between layers. Tasted fine but looked like an interpretation of lasagna for someone who hasn't had one before.

Would visit again but just for the pizza. Staff was friendly. Can't really say much for atmosphere since it was a quiet mid afternoon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuNN2vNmSalgI_ytLI1Jb30GUMhCDtF7BcloeQ&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Justin Turner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDNKnLtu91NUBVuNAL7AtG3Ix0GDRjtEMYDrnyWtG-OP4CFjOl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quality pizza. I got a meat lovers. I was seeing all the good reviews and had to come try it for myself.
If anyone has ever had Round Table pizza before, it is the cookie cutter pizza of that. Not that that is a bad thing! Very good cheese, decent ingredients and great crust.
Price is very good too. Would recommend in a pinch, can’t go wrong.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnss7wETzPYm0H8wwD7odAF6lvCWcO9JcYyfP1&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Margaret Kwok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIN1PfctzO6HuL62iLRLZr8SliaKB1Hl5ynuYUIUqWdl_cBcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Haven't had pizza this good in a while! Good amount of toppings right to the edge. Not too much so the crust nicely supports the toppings and does not soak through. Really good flavor. Ordered the chicken pesto, paneer, cheese, meat, and deluxe. All were great. Service was quick and timely even though they were busy. We will definitely be back. What a fantastic deal for their grand opening but their pizzas are absolutely worth full price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK5ssZB2bD2SnpfxUidGsG-ILQFiWzXYr_l6S9&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got a Hawaiian and a garlic chicken pizza. Love how the toppings are filled to the edge of the pizza, generous amount of cheese. The thickness is just perfect. I hope the restaurant can last at this difficult location. So happy to have a good pizza place close to home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_HRKj_19de50vsJDNRNW8LAh4JGUy5oodzF0W&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-6-14"},{"Name":"K S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNs9D6cXyVPfmtabGvLUCC9wYXXIubSNTSPgQcaNUCxNDbHK9q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered 10 pizzas for a birthday party with an early pickup on a Sunday, and I can’t say enough about how fantastic our experience was! The staff were incredibly accommodating, ensuring everything was ready on time and exactly as we needed.

The pizzas were an absolute hit with all our guests! The butter chicken pizza stole the show—it was so popular that we ran out towards the end. Each pizza was perfectly cooked, generously topped, and packed with flavor.

If you’re looking for delicious pizza and exceptional service, this is the place to go. We’ll definitely be ordering from here again for our next celebration! Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Henricksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkHUinAfyrJxB5VfntT8_gnt2PVnJS_entoTesQV1q8EAX0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Affordable and good quality pizza place.

I had a small deluxe. Lots of meats and cheese. I wish the beef was broken up.

Star deduction for the following:
Upon entry to pickup, there was a man behind the counter sitting and doing nothing. I said “hello” and then “hi” with no response. I assume it was the owner. I had to wait a short bit until staff from the kitchen who then came to the counter. I assume it was the owner. If you’re not going to even acknowledge customers entering, then don’t sit behind the counter.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnn7Qa2nRyD4ir8fGJG0L_vJGMB7lpLs0haz_M&fid=0x0:0x20fb377893ffb7d2"],"When":"2024-7-2"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"wah chi yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBykHMUbkrtJ4cwRRXsjOnAzAcOzwrpq-XVjovUt6A3trFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a new location of Shiok Singapore Restaurant.  It's a family restaurant.  We need to support our local and family restaurant.
The new bright renovation, the food, service, air-condition, the patio and the price are unbeatable.
If you never been to this restaurant, you must have a try.
The unbeatable price are $13.95 for a curry chicken with rice, $3 for a iced coffee or tea.  The taste and the portion are good.
May I have a little advice.  If they make the order plastic sheet in English dish names, maybe a big help for the new customers.
So we don't need to look the big menu then go back to the order sheet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyDO-6uZRz2S-vMj3-A8uGYw7EVbQCMnH9VdFU&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmgoFQrGMjTU1qQTL4G07bvioF513c9HVkJY_GKQpIXUgF4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a small space, but was pleasantly surprised by the prices, food and the friendly owner. The owner came and helped us decide on what to get and gave recommendations. He was very friendly and accommodating, and the food tasted good as well.
We ordered the laksa, the curry chicken, the curry fish as well as the skewers.
Would highly recommend you give it a shot! New west needed a Singaporean cuisine and this is the best spot right now!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOI7CsVEhX9oekBJtMimnR-PtPE-BO2j4Dw7O3Z&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"柴皓仁","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDHLhzhIePFnKjokxmRTW35ZkREa_RSNsAfy7IPpC-D6Q7n4Yj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a very nice Singaporean restaurant. The food is delicious and very Singaporean, the service is good and the price is reasonable. It is a relaxing place to sit down and eat, highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMx8JUvilu5lKVAR3QVvOITeDAAlRoAjmpn3SU9&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came at 6pm Sunday, the little restaurant was busy but the service was fast & efficient. The premises is clean & neat. We had satay beef & chicken skewers, roti prata to share, hainanese chicken rice & bandung (pink rose water) for me, beef rendang & calamasi drink for my husband. The food was delicious at good prices. My chicken was super tender and I love the rice that is cooked in chicken broth, it has very nice ginger aroma. That pink rose drink is yummy at $3! Shiok Canteen reminds me of those food stalls in Singapore (without flights and heat, their AC works very well haha). Will come back to try their laksa & chedol (our next table had them and they looked mouth watering). I like the way water is filled in continuously and the friendly owner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONwLIJt6JVei6TY9wnr8XQYdmtWlC8EZ0Ljg1I&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Cheuk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViyaLSrOR53wIdh-1tPL1EO-fv4jJiDA_NDJQYVAHprBRcIndGIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely my go to place for Singaporean food, cannot be more authentic than Shiok.  Glad they opened a location in new West. Food is excellent, laksa has the same taste I had when I was living in Singapore.  Hainan chicken rice is very good as well, chicken is so soft my son loves it!  Service is excellent, always makes sure you are taken care of but never too much as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUcUDGfodSKBjMqtJp_2rPLwuK8rA6IgF8Oi39&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Jessie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPwp36N1ftgRNl5Ql-GlVvcrKKUkfRjvh7SllcIwq6UnTH7Yaq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"ordered the seafood laksa, beef puff pastry, chicken rice and calamansi drink! everything came out pretty quickly and the family was super attentive and great with their service!
the food was very yummy and satisfying ☺️

will definitely be coming back in the future!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJxFro8tWqQgtwFAMn1SqTrkF5i_3oieMA6Avc&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-8-28"},{"Name":"Kasumi Okajima (Kas)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3m9Zzz5V40ZOlaImUkn3ZQp6STmmVav3AD_8yRA8CBB-Hy749=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The owner there has great recommendations so you can ask him. It was my first time having Singapore foods but I eventually found great choice. Just watch out the business hour","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNP-3HMBepsyXNziMZOolYcuOCKvt9PzhKsg8sh&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Hiep Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMRHHZ7t798igHqhwEObqqiXXBYRe7_vTRRS3-gXG7fOgZlXSH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food and service is very good! So glad our team came here for lunch.  Definitely coming back here more often. Price is very affordable 👌.

Came back here for lunch with our wives. Tried more items on the menu. It was delicious 😋.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPlJiamysW65gkrBklm6sOzDcjbg24BmArZdsj_&fid=0x0:0x32e21295ac2c2675"],"When":"2024-5-29"}]

I love the new drink menu with all the old timey 🍸 cocktails. Drinks were great! And I think food quality has improved.  The only downside to the experience was the unengaged service. Perhaps it was due to lack of experience but the server seemed bored, inattentive. Just plopped our food down and left without asking if we needed anything else. When asked about items on the menu, we were met with a disinterested "I don't know".  Had to flag her down in the end and this shouldn't have to happen as your food sits getting cold.   Lack of stars directly related to service alone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M Copan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6IuP11xvJLV_LAcICSOpVAPA2i0lEKHSWUzxGQU3jADCAhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Eat at your own peril as the food was horrible. Now I know why this place was empty when I've walled by the last few times.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stella Stone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWiwOLPA91h1nSRncqHRS0qib_VmmyRolNqqODNG7WYqfGpw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They also do private parties!

Try the Paloma and the Espresso Martini","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amjad Palitana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoqRch3gVhvxAqCkxmIw0_nQIxBpFi_mSXmHEDeWS8Z0uoPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing time at the Sapperton District Taphouse yesterday. Service by Sultan and their cocktails were excellent too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPO3b7Qa07-HVwObRl9ZpkFDW9VEVqO5M36cDh9&fid=0x0:0x1512aa5780619740"],"When":"2023-7-29"},{"Name":"Sanj Sukerkar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1TlcfDhiGbYCgLbWzynmtbH93hdSbysA2MYgEXKrmj4rCOtGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place to hang out on Friday's. Overall a must-visit locale for Friday!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNjlRTup29KHgd6Y8RegYg7oPIh6mJwvrWx9vJ&fid=0x0:0x1512aa5780619740"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"Freee27 (Freee27)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItGEE6mSYhaV1mDVzl6RQpCu5typl6QMnqOSkOQmKhEQnCVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gabby is awesome! It’s pretty low key here and love the atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhTiR0jBWeHL4m0FaVosJnkxz7Ya07b3CCzRzK&fid=0x0:0x1512aa5780619740"],"When":"2022-10-23"}]

[{"Name":"Gen X Surrey Girl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnz98iwXPE1DskfLpfNg-zDV5mDy1tGmvmbNcHWdRqf6q4OTmNvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good food. Good service. The char sui protein add-on was pretty gnarly. I wouldn't recommend that. But the Bombay mac and cheese was excellent.

I ordered medium hot but the server warned against it. He said he'd give me some hot sauce on the side that I could add in if I liked. He didn't think I'd like the heat level. I appreciated the advice. It wasn't too hot but I like that he cared enough to mention it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp6lQFWAUK-GmbFqVshtnkXdFOIk9pv_ezO7wT&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Aarna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyKiPt9xTa8ZNQM2KUPVsXHP40b2Zu4rW1CyCzcZ5rQDcsYM8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for brunch with my mom, we ordered the spicy peanut coconut box, kids mac and cheese (we got some spice added) and chicken bites. The spicy peanut box was 10/10, amazing. Flavour was spot on and so was the spice it was packed with veggies and we both loved it. The mac and cheese sauce was not thick, very cheesy and spicy because we got some added. This was probably one of the best mac and cheese i’ve have in the area. The chicken bites were well coated however there wasn’t much flavour in them so I wouldn’t recommend unless it’s for children. The service WAS quick, the bites arrived before my mom even settled down after ordering and the boxes arrived 5-7 minutes after that. Overall good experience, I would recommend noodle box!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMk2re0WVUDNIrUQe0soobkkfHebMl9Rhnu0BWY&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Hemant Saini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnmX5eLp24nybXuyZKU4sp5QN8w1CUMmnlsJvpw07_6Eo0ghWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Noodle Box can't be termed as a classic Asian Cuisine restaurant chain. At best, it's Asian influenced fusion food.

Having sampled 5 dishes - I think this chain offers some delicious concoctions to try out.

The food presentation was pretty good and value for money.

I had ordered my serve Schorching Hot and was supposed to feature Ghost Peppers but it was more of some kind of BBQ sauce poured without restraint.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQG8c6t7gVFOZujskLQCim3r8mKmuRA_YxrRyj&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Alberto Galleguillos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKT_Q6hbseR7v-tM50X6qEUnu3mVTWAX810Jeq_5U6UQFoucA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered thai chow mein 2 weeks ago and paid extra for crispy chicken.  When I got home, there was no chicken.  I emailed New West noodle box the next day, but did not receive a response until later in the week when I included the corporate email.  It then took an additional week for the manager to ask for my email (via email...) for an etransfer for the refund.  I received the refund a few days later for an unusual amount (more than the cost of the chicken, but less than the meal), and NO NOTE to confirm it was for the refund/inconvenience.

Granted, its a small/insignificant error/issue, but if this is how they respond to simple errors, I am afraid if there are more serious issues (allergies?  I would steer clear!)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSCvowRm1PR2pRr5aPztjkXkUzQwq7z7q7fuZo&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"Jordan Neufeld","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjQE-jQG_WgoPRW4CWcz9vy3KPy-Zbm5Iztq9YA0HiNiVURg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the bubble tea for the first time, great addition to the already great food and service! I’ll definitely order that again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPB1fr8eWUCfSk0eamtiSg8KlI6om3mS2JxJ0e5&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Desiree Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpDJR9Mj9o1RGFO9johAzcs2KM18_w_VdKQgMNlj54DnV8cQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered on Uber eats last night and as my husband was eating he bit into a METAL STAPLE and his tongue was bleeding. So irresponsible, won’t be eating here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN02rVg516z7SxsofMfen05-gYUjhwjzhCHLNCt&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Clean fast food restaurant with a good number of options. You can customize the noodles, the protein, and any extras. The cheapest option with just the noodles was $11 so it’s not a very cheap meal. Taste was very fusion and not authentic. Medium spice is too spicy so wouldn’t recommend if you’re usually a medium spice person. Great to see compostable utensils and bowls being used for take out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOn7gw65c0Ed5DaYep_0cH0F_KtQ6fWes90ISv7&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2023-6-12"},{"Name":"Vansh Gupta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGRQ140XH6qO4ThNnpj_V8jmag98uQWPh8phhDHDuBwB6IXmY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried their recommended Spicy Peanut and I loved the box and their customer service was quick","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6dMecpcd0GYFTaSEKNvG57TIqS9W9W5oPcudw&fid=0x0:0x1ee81d68fb5c3756"],"When":"2024-7-28"}]

[{"Name":"dan roxas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9Jx1R3xmxZDUxzfyTjLL1LGbeewFEwWBaNs-uwgS_zYD2DheenQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"first time experience,  the  service crew benz made it easy for us to decide which one to get. also gave us the freebie when you by 3 even though we didnt see the promo. over all the food is excellent, service was fast. price is somewhat ok'sh. i suggest having a wings sampler menu for everyone to have a chance to try all the flavors since a wings order costs $17.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZIeNjxbM-tR9I-YvOuxatOQ7cm_NOMsMNUSXW&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Brittany","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHTcuSM-4ly1uIP3q2-jgQ_2Vqi7GhBmGO9JykCcOlnN1NYOmqYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The BEST late night spot to hit if you’re getting off the train in New West. Typically service is pretty quick and the dogs include all the side sauces/seasonings. It’s hard to choose between waffle fries and fried mac and cheese bites, so we often have to order both! Such a guilty pleasure!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM41tZ5W0AjbBYXyLwMGv0klbu2dAlQKBWJqbvJ&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Daniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvd6-q0LFLnT6Fjanc2ymc9JLptLuzcaQqNrOdzOGpx9n_bEE6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recommend the half-mozerella or whole mozerella, really delicious. And the cheese pull🤤...
The Mac and cheese bites were nice to snack on, but I would just get another hotdog😂

They let you pick from a wide selection of condiments and seasonings to add to your hotdogs

The service was really nice, and they gave me a free drink to apologise for the long wait.
The place is quite busy right now, so wait times might be long, but compared to other locations, it's not bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-fq-kCGWmIOATVNRTAW1mTJyE0zaBqZRV8z4Y&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-4-9"},{"Name":"Jessica Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTqZgPj0eXg_JYgAnVgUcTOilpA24BvBnkompjw1nEkEUn2g3_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely girl working alone today had great service and got us our food very fast. The assortment of sauces and seasonings are great. Yummy crispy rice dogs. I recommend getting the potato, it’s very filling. Mozzarella cheese is a good one too, but I don’t like the cheddar cheese as much (it’s sticky like American cheese).
The establishment could be decorated better. There’s definitely space to have one more table or some barstools next to the pickup counter.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSFMVArH2yxq3-FLs1dMdgbAJd2nQRHW9_hgBa&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Candace Garbo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIz4G0UgSTRcj-d0G0Yvf7FpvBUnX_kFnIsUdQ4GLnjqTtr5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love this place. I think I’ve been here four times in the last month. I’m extremely happy with the quality of the vegetarian dog and to know it has great ingredients in it. I’m so happy that this place is in my neighbourhood  Staff is very kind and it’s extremely clean.
I highly recommend this bite of heaven and the dessert don’t get me started!!
Yummy licious","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYPO_iaXKz3WxJ34vUhc413113W8-mmIlsj2FB&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Praise Jakaza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiJqtVgnP0iluJnviL28PaDnawcXoeY-a8e4QVJetmAYycdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was my first time trying Korean rice hot dogs and they were good! I recommend asking for extra sauce. The customer service was amazing and we did not have to wait for too long.

They have a great selection of condiments so you can really customize your order! Ordered the Gamsung and Half mozzarella (with potatoes).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2VG8czgdRzHUEzAgz2IUkcyIVRNeN6IGZF0pM&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Miss Mayhem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGowE1po-uzevgz4y-llWcltZGBd0Jj1Qx_2rqJzm0bNHjXwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Interesting twist on the classic corn dog. They have a variety of hotdog/cheese combos to choose from with sauces and seasonings to add as well. You can choose a combination of sauces or make your own, didn’t see regular mustard as that’s my go to for the og corn dog. I am all about the sauces but I like mine on the side, would have preferred that as an option. If you don’t want a dog they have wings and waffle fries too! Very tasty overall.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXKXfhFZOKNRqGVMYdoFV3-R1zzK_mEKdYOKQP&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"KOMAL MALHI","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHEXfS5dqHARmE9xrNWAi-hNXRfBxTO5cdKpx-qMsFiXdtX5o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went there by just looking their ad on TikTok and this was my best decision. I love love their corn dogs. They are the best in the town. Also, the people working there are super friendly. They try to give you their best service. This is my favourite go to place now.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdyG83JPdmJ7gjgdCcZNqn8P303imOqfmU3poL&fid=0x0:0x46ba0e9a27cef231"],"When":"2024-7-30"}]

[{"Name":"Kab Kbaas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5U0xr3upvQTURbvXCvcu5mgHu9kAs3kt9vv_C4iuqaE8mdtRkEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Captain's oven pizza strikes again! This is the new edition to this up and coming franchise. The pizza here at this location is as excellent as it is at the other locations.

Everything from the time you enter the restaurant, to your order being taken, to the actual taste of this delicious pizza is a treat!

If you haven't eaten at this or at the other Captain's Oven pizza outlets, what are you waiting for?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPV70YShrbRJD2YqmIe8uPFYnLjCouLZk2yun9-&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Johnny Hsu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnJCpeAf_rNo3J-P8wYYkAus79ikEYQpAwrpY7-h_p6gndGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great new place!   Awesome pizza and everything tasted so fresh.   We tried some of the veggie options, of which there were many.   Really great menu and there are so many choices that sounded delicious, it was very difficult to choose.  Will have to come back to try some others.   We had a Caprese and a Chef's Special.  Both were delicious.  We had meatballs in marinara too but forgot to take a pic.  So good!   Tiramisu for dessert was a perfect way to finish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsi10IKu8HCHISk-3zxG1fymIk_lnnWdcApuWq&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"sanjin ramovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWao3NCDoBfu96Y6YVIck2LSuOpB-Wbt71v94bbUF_9zLIh6UJQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza, helpful staff.

We bought 4 pizzas here today, and loved them. Their pizza was delicious, with great crust, quality cheese and fresh ingredients. Adults loved the Capriciossa and Mexican, and the kids thought that the Hawaiian was the best.

Will definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2j1Z61i-gDrA4Uci5bKE31joE1CKYWx6RtZ35&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Ketron Casio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwBIJbgGs0I8DkEZa5zp4-cK7c-6EXQ_EoY7PCgD78FZmG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to share with you an incredible pizza place that I recently discovered in New west . I have ordered from them twice now, and I must say, it has been the best pizza I’ve had so far. The quality of the ingredients, the flavors, and the overall experience have truly exceeded my expectations.

One of the things that truly stood out to me was the outstanding customer service provided by the staff. The owners of the pizzeria are incredibly nice and friendly, making the whole dining experience even more enjoyable. They pay attention to every detail and ensure that their customers are well taken care of.

I highly recommend giving this pizza place a try. I believe you will love it just as much as I do. Whether you are a fan of traditional pizzas or prefer something more unique, they have a wide variety of options to choose from. I am confident that you will be impressed by the quality and taste of their pizzas.

If you decide to give it a try, please let me know your thoughts. I would love to hear about your experience. I am sure you will not be disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jmbstat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4TODiBsftPq9OFVr5nwW3ykAdRY2fPCqtIkp3MV3W0L87sjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dropped by during their soft opening and was quite surprised with the options available. Captains oven pizza is a family owned, wood fire oven pizza joint, with a long list of flavors! I tried their Mexicana picante which has a kick of heat. Falvours were delicous, and has free sauces available during dine in, the price was very fair for the size, quality and toppings. The open kitchen shows their extreme cleanliness and the staff were very friendly! Defintiley a must try before they get busy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcCOkd-7QAoVhGGHUUUwSYE7kVZdNWwrtHSeNB&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Craig Afonso","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8bAv0onJPry9osSMLvfTocBp6OFdo_ZdcbZOzskU82vSV_DZa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When it comes to pizzas, Captain’s Oven never fails to impress! We decided to stick to the classics this time, and they were nothing short of perfection—crisp crusts, perfectly balanced toppings, and flavors that hit all the right notes. It’s always a delight to see consistency in quality and taste.

What’s even better is that they’ve opened another branch, making it easier for more pizza lovers to enjoy their delicious creations. Whether you’re a fan of traditional flavors or looking to try something new, Captain’s Oven delivers a pizza experience that’s hard to beat. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ted Gould","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfi4q0CQOsJEAVRYDXJEdKJ_Mk-Kyp_l5OYNZB3Fn501cTzfk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Crispy yet chewy sourdough crust, undeniably fresh, high quality ingredients, and an amazing array of premium pizza recipes that left me astounded. Neapolitan style should always be a go-to, but something about that impressive oven and the cooking skills at this store Sets. It. Apart.

Managed to catch the soft opening this weekend, and this is a next-level pizza place! Love the modern feel to the store, great location near the Sapperton skytrain and an apparently home-made Tiramisu capped an amazing experience! Thank you Captains Oven, you'll be seeing us again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSDjoIMCC1pD46hN8Xy-VvhMoL9grdG_8euoha&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Jason B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHPM8xPtM44eW0tBpsv7VOKz7lXS8yUYGfOoO1EucOe6ha=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible quality ingredients, great people behind the counter and care put into each pie . I would consider myself a pizza enthusiast... which is nothing to be proud of haha but this is seriously one of the best sourdough pizza's I have ever had. We have tried six pizza's so far since opening, and every order has been cooked to perfection. Recommend, any pizza but for my wife and two year old, it's the Spicy Soppressata at the current favourite. The only thing I am not happy about is they are so close, and we will be spending a lot of money there haha! Thank you for being here and see you soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmzbJdgK0WwsBmCBR8Br7co4jUmXQukaFyvoI&fid=0x0:0xfc29be6bfdc1f815"],"When":"2024-12-12"}]

[{"Name":"Zoe Edin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUWt16RQ3aFyAP6MReumudNUbclGB77JypHQEpAs03_cIlRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The Frankie G burger was good, but the fries and poutine were really soft and salty. Came for the trivia and ordered what the server recommended. I will be trying different menu items next time, but it's a good place to meet up if you're in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBYD4FBdum8sdExOtepsE2Nak-UNJOxLzqsbas&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2024-10-31"},{"Name":"Dharrol Alves","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMAvQtyw-CQyBvcynigl2DD4m7x2-iyIkD47pcjsTALZj-9V5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great spot with amazing food. As well the all day happy hour drink specials are great! It’s a hidden gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFflXn_GO2fw7ak13RXEQeZMZLt0yWLtwya5cD&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Shaeli Finnie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9swc8R2K-WPKeSpodeW9gMPefWym8hWzzaxuYb_8dEHf-eO8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came and visited this bar today!
$12 pasta special and $17.5 for wings.
The pasta seemed like a good deal and the wings in B.C--- crazy expensive.
The beer was cold and the staff were extremely polite!
The place wasn't too packed and the pints are about average in price for a respectable establishment!
Only suggestions I could make are to diversify the staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randi Foulkes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoLXCTf8ZMlw2OJNLY_QrUyqBRUBWhNTjTSDcPwnhjldn_CBXGcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love it! Great atmosphere and space! Food is delicious 👍 Waitresses were super friendly and very helpful. One of the only places I've found that serves Hopping mad cider!! Will be back for sure. They said they may start up a community shuttle service soon as well, pick up and drop off service. What could be better 😆","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNufSh_XFqa7dJfkA8t2x80hS2hHceVVKUKx7-n&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2018-9-15"},{"Name":"Tran Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9eULK8-7j2U9Ze3f3qd5XAYcn_cs8--Jdb91h4DDxVjShDzqIaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here on a sunny day and their patio is great. Drinks are good too. We ordered the nacho and beef sliders. Well, the food was not very good at all. The nacho was cold and not a lot of toppings. Cheese has congealed and did not have that classic stringy pull. Oh well. But the good news was that we brought it home added more cheese and banana peppers and warm it up in the oven, and it came out perfect. 👌 The sliders were very dry. The bread was like a few days too many in the freezer. Well again, we brought the sliders home, we swapped out for fresher buns and made our homemade beef patties, and the sliders turned out perfect 👌.  I want to like this place because it is only two blocks away from our house, but I rather walk 30mins to Match for better food or just cook at home. 🤷🤷🤷","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIymzm0hgCDF6KJmyCEiZzrJ2TVP_a_JereGCN&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2023-5-7"},{"Name":"Lorna Holmes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLGTiz7X8ca9yPQGHnezPpPq3Z134oRRYTfLLhiDOE2Wbgxc-9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a pleasant experience in my lovely neighbourhood pub.  We were warmly greeted and our server, Ashley, was wonderful.  She took great care of us and our lunch was very tasty and perfectly portioned.  Will definitely be back.  Thanks Ashley!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lekha Reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmJGhl1-4gmLsjhODLv0EBv4db0I65Xj_LQ4N38nJXAbHQF354=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located in Port Royal neighbourhood, this place gives all the cozy cabin vibes with good food and drinks. The nacho melts that were on special were just so so good. Red hot wings were on spot with perfect spicy flavour we wanted. The waitress was not really checking on and had to call quite a few times for cutlery, plates and more orders. Great customer service as well.
