[{"Name":"El B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1Jp_yyor94dWcxEABRdR-csu7LJ3E6mAmEDdXvZyVkvxhIa10=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying this coffee place. It's small inside about 3 tables or so but the coffee and treats are amazing. The cinnamon roll lightly warmed with icing was delicious. Coffee was good too, the service was great. One of the washrooms was out of order but they accommodated us briefly. 5 starts definitely will go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZeiYxLHYzn9OSp6qu4-J1BdQmNM8qCr_ac1IO&fid=0x0:0xa2822641d17d77b7"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Ray Jang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3wj8Ne3ngI4eg9ouEU6zPmvERlQuudbckz4ma4Vg6pfYrsWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coffee was fantastic with smooth rich flavour in my iced Americano. I usually find it hard to extract good coffee flavours when the coffee is cold, but it was a 27’C day that called for a cold beverage…so I imagine their hot coffee is even better. I ordered a Reuben, but they ran out of sauerkraut and invited me to substitute with any of their available veggies…which turned out pretty good!  Bread was fresh as were the other ingredients. Not a spectacular sandwich, but more than decent for a coffee/tea spot with a small kitchen. Service was fast, efficient, friendly and the person taking my order offered to open the patio umbrella for me when I sat outside to enjoy the warm weather (although I was tempted to enjoy the refreshing AC indoors).  I will easily be back for their coffee. The reviews you read in Google about their great service is totally true.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeWILT7PcXZfd-TreoKAXCk_KcpyzK_znaENBb&fid=0x0:0xa2822641d17d77b7"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Mani El-Hefnawy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3TT3mozO96ldp0WKn-yNIiVROGdClqnJ7LVX989XNby6xe4iS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Local gem 💎 The coffee is unmatched, it’s always brewed fresh and tastes smooth every time. Food is delicious and baked fresh as well. Staff are always so nice and welcoming and remember you, It always feels like I’m catching up with friends rather than getting a service! Strong sense of community and I always keep coming back!
My personal go to is the Vegetarian Breakfast Bagel and a shot in the dark with cream and sugar. The quality of food and service is truly superior, Thanks Dustin and the team for always being so welcoming and offering the best service possible! ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfRf_6wUgQm-Oan2ihNu-MmrM8aw0FuJ4oY2_S&fid=0x0:0xa2822641d17d77b7"],"When":"2023-10-6"},{"Name":"Josh M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocId4sB-QmyS1ZIK-eu26hW1V34TckZCYtWAQ8yNd0uGVBGjBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Drinks were delicious, however the service was atrocious.

My friend and I went to this cafe one afternoon and ordered drinks. While waiting for our drinks, we stepped outside to chat and get some air. Please note, at this time the cafe was not busy, approximately 2-3 other customers inside, and we had full visual of the service counter from the outside. We would periodically check the counter from the outside if our drinks were ready.

Eventually we noticed that approximately 15 minutes elapsed since we placed our order and there were no sight of our drinks. I went inside to speak to one of the employees about our order and they stated, "We're sorry, we forgot.", then they promptly made our order. They did not offer anything to rectify their mistake.

TLDR: Good food, nice atmosphere, staff has a memory of a goldfish if you don't wait inside for your order.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXO5qKan2j8g7JXvUM_mUNcEEjkuTAlPUpKK4CusfodcXCVb6kr8g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A nice small Cafe at the waterfront. Four tables on the inside and some more seating outside the Cafe. The atmosphere was welcoming and the staff were lovely (they sure know their regulars!).

Ordered: black coffee, ice vanilla latte, breakfast sandwich, croissant sandwich, chocolate avalanche (chocolate criossant) and a very berry scone. Everything tasted good but wished they  had more bacon in the breakfast sandwich. They have a wide range of pastries, sandwich/wraps and drinks!

A big score for students as they give 15% off!

P.S. they allow you to bring your dog in while ordering :))","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXJadM9sTlhrZu_4VGkc9AUiVx6fIjx3i6u6HG&fid=0x0:0xa2822641d17d77b7"],"When":"2023-4-14"},{"Name":"Marina P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcL5xcNwXO0KxgZwa_eHixpB3whMI4RYt26UPe1zaLS7mZKZ1n=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favourite coffee places, whenever I’m in the area, I always take time to stop by and grab myself a drink. The mocha here is by far one of the best I’ve had.
In addition to the coffee, the service is wonderful as well. everyone here is so sweet, I always leave with a smile on my face.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Woods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7JUbYP9UfvKcKjMTVtGVK_u-4I9H-snWOBROylNTcUUw0zoIdXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is ammmmaaaazing!
Their coffee is extremely smooth, with a large  selection of fun food items and accessories.
I love that they have so many different milk options and customized your order how you like it.
What makes this place spectacular though is the overwhelming friendliness of the staff.
I'm blown away by it.
They make you feel so welcome like you're meeting a friend for coffee!  You won't want to leave 😅
Their mission statement speaks volumes on their customer service.
I am so thrilled to have finally found my go to coffee shop in New West. Oh and I love the name! ☕🙌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwMAFGYnABWA3fDk7haRTKwyEWxM1wdrXaHHxl&fid=0x0:0xa2822641d17d77b7"],"When":"2021-3-10"},{"Name":"Steve O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjmYbAzncXOf6deK5dtSoTZXay2gzbtaNYQmuCdtzraLJbMc_XHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible!

We saw this under construction for quite some time when we were shopping in the area.

We are happy to to report they are open and have some amazing products.

Firstly their Chai Tea Latte is GOD TIER. I haven't had something this great tasting since Rosso in Calgary.

They have a great selection of snacks to pair with their hot drinks.

Their staff was super friendly and great with recommendations.

I recommend this as a must stop if you're in the area or heading to the train station.

Don't miss out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRp4QsaR1_yBLIXx2wp6Ns8OwYOgrzqgGbViBi&fid=0x0:0xa2822641d17d77b7"],"When":"2021-3-7"}]

[{"Name":"Parth Thakkar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvPHMh0QVw0t-KmiqqZNyaMJ-6bNHKj4kGOSpy1qIl_Mi6qo6Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Town’s go to Indio-Chinese spot.
Must have’s: Honey Garlic Cauliflower, Veg Manchurian & Schezwan Fried Rice.

Utterly delicious, large portions & value for the money.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPn9a39iO3B3lUqJdHeKjQvaTQZ64P0aKCBK-2L&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Dr. Naresh.R. Thumati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZe9i5l3lcphUrpMV7UIgJLbGmYTbI6xZPxyGLcsocFMCumCPI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"While passing through this restaurant, I noticed this lunch special Thaali board with special price. I couldn't resist mys self to try this Thaali. I am big fan of Indian Thalis.

They said, You can choose any Curry from their menu for Thaali, which surprised me (that means they make  fresh curry for only for your Thali). I have chosen non-veg Thali (13.49$) option which comes with one veg and one chicken Curry (no lamb and shrimp included in Thali), one plain naan, Rice and Raita. I have selected Karahi Paneer (veg Curry)  and Chicken tikka Masala ( non-veg Curry). The ambience is good, very clean and good service. The food is not at it's best but I can say it's worth for the given price. It is far better than eating junk food by paying 20$ on your work day lunch. The paneer Currey is 4 out of 5, but they should work on chicken tikka masala. I didn't find any taste in it. But the quality of food is good. The naan is very plain, they should offer Garlic naan to make the Thaali more tasty. Rice is of good quality they have used. Raita is fresh. Overall I am not disappointed,  although I expected a better Chicken tikka masala which is a basic chicken curry in any Indian place and it shouldn't go wrong.

Overall I appreciate this restaurant team for their efforts to offer Thali at such low price yet quoty food. You don't even get a burger or sandwich from McD  for that price in these inflation days. Also, the girl at front was friendly and did good job.

I wanted to try Chana bathura next time.

Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0XMLgOx4y_8kqS_FWesvvQNTC3Funx6F9Rev4&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the sweets which are delicious. Trying many north indian sweets for the first time and loving the quality of it in this place.

Tried Channa Bhatura aka Poori with Chickpeas curry that comes with cream and freshly cut onions. It was for $ 6. 95 during lunch hours.

Loved its freshness and will be back soon !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoW9zMNweUNmDh1j3IGE_fstOFiSqYmG8GdWnr&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love it! Their lamb kebab, goat curry, butter chicken, garlic naans, chai tea, mango lassi and desserts are all good. My new go-to place for Indian food. The owner is very nice, price is great, and there's a big parking lot in the rear. Will come back very soon to try the rest of the menu :D","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhyKhEftWleTJIUYYOQni0QkFhMsNfBJwa28jF&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"Jashan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUT2DsBWm66GpZrhJ3gqnHsIa7xRHnVnNHTZoadqXPgkapvqB4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today, I visited this place , I tried Amritsari kulcha & veg Thali , food was awesome…… thanks for making my day ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYf6l-DGt9DsQFbMv7ez7tztfDE27OFikOd_Nv&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Leah Sargent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkbXH-OQ_7sFeemekssqTaoKEfoLwz8C9cJi6AwQRDmbir2ZKS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great gluten free, dairy free options and the food was DELICIOUS. My favourite Indian since moving to Canada (11 years ago from England) superb flavour, not too fatty and good portion sizes (good amount of leftovers). Highly recommend! (Coconut chicken curry was my fav)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcXdxQ5XM8NViO2HOwLWpTGrxkBasYP-WEHHPU&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2024-4-1"},{"Name":"Michael A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3NxtyRfPp-9ZhswWx21Mo8fQSmRiHA8ouIN6Y3mcVxWJESOSnfg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ok, so every now and then you stumble across a hole in the wall restaurant that you have to think really, why didn’t I know about this place before! Well, this is one of them! Amazing Indian food, at great price and it’s just so good we have made it our go to place for Indian cuisine moving forward. If you wish to try great Indian food , there is no other place to come!  The decor is simple and clean and comfy, but nothing fancy. Don’t be fooled by the decor, the food is insanely good! OMG ! For those lucky enough to read this, go now and order it before the queues become insane !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPKu5qrAFWM6d0rrweLwa0xObRGjgP5kOmdJOL&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2023-12-3"},{"Name":"SHAUNDRA GARDINER","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9infcm8X5heI-lHljWxW5-QG5Di7bxsDA_l6aRyrDTkLokmDC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was amazed by how good, fresh and tasty the food was. It was convenient as I was just down the street doing laundry. I’d definitely come back to try more items on the menu. The waiter was nice & our food was served in a great manner of time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcK0OdqsWfD9FyyILoyM5G8fMvmE6hQE34ORsW&fid=0x0:0xf0212ded0051493f"],"When":"2023-9-4"}]

I have never seen delivery more than 30 min.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"meedool","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqOAqZgWECUgDQqDgB6RT0rl1kxJU4z1POZnOP0Q3VEK5KM9qs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely terrible service, the food is terrible. Some parts of the menu used to be decent, but now they are terrible too. Staff seemed unfriendly and pissed for some reason, food took way too long to be made, and the store smells like a butcher shop for some reason; of raw meat.

Pizza tastes frozen and reheated too. Used to go there once in a while but I forgot how terrible it was. Definitely not going back. Just go to Queensborough Pizza, it's so much better and it's really good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vishal Goyal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi4u-i5CXrp6ymv6Vl8g03bSSYZcGDX8NEXmd3LzvtkRh_tF3OZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Title: A Slice of Heaven: New West Pizza Delights

New West Pizza in New Westminster is a culinary gem that has quickly become my go-to spot for a satisfying slice. From the moment you step inside, the inviting aroma of freshly baked dough and savory toppings greets you, setting the stage for a memorable dining experience.

The menu boasts a wide array of options, from classic pepperoni to inventive gourmet creations, ensuring there's something to please every palate. What sets New West Pizza apart, however, is the quality of their ingredients. Each bite bursts with flavor, thanks to the use of fresh, locally sourced produce and premium meats.

Not only is the pizza top-notch, but the service is also exceptional. The staff is friendly, attentive, and always eager to accommodate special requests. Whether you're dining in or opting for delivery, you can expect prompt and courteous service every time.

The cozy ambiance of the restaurant adds to the overall charm, making it the perfect spot for a casual meal with friends or a cozy date night. And with generous portion sizes at reasonable prices, you'll leave feeling satisfied without breaking the bank.

In conclusion, New West Pizza in New Westminster is a must-visit for any pizza lover. Delicious food, friendly service, and a welcoming atmosphere combine to create an unforgettable dining experience. I can't wait to return for another slice of heaven!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Krushinsky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3fmFXutFrt3LbgshWkzotw65tphKrSFQ47wyAISm4tROsygMMhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Pizza was amazing..wings were just..wings no drumettes.Deep fryer oil needs to be changed as it makes wings taste like old oil.. would not order the wings again.9$ for not very great tasting wings and no drumettes? Also..white sauce costs extra? I thought that usually this was something you could order anywhere. Without an extra cost.. I would order some pizza again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM74eeyxBSYkndHt_ogpZwGzTX7ciOQ9al0Gket&fid=0x0:0x4ba2a276347e36ab"],"When":"2022-1-23"}]

[{"Name":"M R (cndn_hippo)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSUGlOqsxZsnICDm9_y90peAIJ-FMhmEr94lfGziKuJOuHJ6qt2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Desi pizza is where it's at for Canadian pizza. IYKYK. Queensborough is no exception.  Delicious pizza with cheese and toppings right to the edge. Perfectly baked crust. Lovely staff. Decent prices for an independent pizza place.
We live in Coquitlam, so it's not somewhere we'd be going to a lot, but we'll definitely go back! Eagerly.

Skip the cheesy garlic bread.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqwZVhYJ758SderpRL_bjKXAUJkdHZYx3NL1FX&fid=0x0:0xa7f85bb1a2bb89bf"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Keith Harasymiw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJX6b2Eka9tYe9Jslf-NXuefSERW3K-SSnb2OoIjz8bje3o2w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Needed 4 pizzas ready for 1120am, called the night before to order. Pizzas were ready for us and were delicious, so good, they were not shy on the toppings which was great, perfect pizzas, we desteoyed them all. And the price was just right. Thanks again and we will be ordering again for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBmvbwBv74dWgOumLTGeGF9V9QKWiBi_JdWJ4C&fid=0x0:0xa7f85bb1a2bb89bf"],"When":"2022-4-14"},{"Name":"Bat Girl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsHrMF1U97M_AI9bk2xNb41tFGVAPF-s0krNV-O3nZrEGmgtwk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered their special, and cheese pizza for a late night snack and their pizzas did not disappoint. The ingredients seem fresh and it was a very thoughtful touch for them to have wax paper underneath the pizza so the pizza does not stick to the cardboard. Their dough is thin compared to other pizza places so there no big crust which is fine with me. The toppings are generous which I do prefer over having more crust. I would order their pizzas again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_eWl6lgzp0VpTiYrPTeRhG5D6e7cjwEwrEdn4&fid=0x0:0xa7f85bb1a2bb89bf"],"When":"2020-10-19"},{"Name":"Felix Cheung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIsEF2zYuOa8K13gofBZbzH3T6HqZa4rfVgyGQ90HEXqQB4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Just in general not bad
But ordering whole pizzas to go is better than ordering by slices cuz this is the first time i don't see reheating the pizzas for u","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shyamin Rahiman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK21PNgD59kzmiKAc5juE6SoPuB5xyaxXu7BiXCZm8PMJ93aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered 2 large pizza one veggie and other one with shrimp. Shrimp smelled so bad that my whole house stinks. I’m sure the shrimp was bad when called them…didn’t care only gave 50% of for my next order pizza. Totally disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Priyanka Ahluwalia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGh6qf5PEz8UqUvKYrwokKEc848dxK7A3gihg2iVX_JlVutwpD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Amazing!!! We asked for extra sauce and they delivered!!!

UPDATE: MARCH 13th 2024: was going to place an order like usual. We order from here very regularly and asked for the sauce (hot sauce and ranch) on top LIKE ALWAYS. The lady on the phone says she will charge me 2$. If we were to go pickup this order it would’ve be free. So just because it is being delivered they are charging for sauce. AGAIN: if i were to pick it up and open the box to put the sauce on myself = no charge. But if the lady puts it on before she hands it to the delivery guy= 2$. Im sorry what?!?!? So sad considering we’ve been coming here for 5 YEARS.

The photo below was from when they DELIVERED it with SAUCE NO CHARGE.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_FPDvUS8FlY4HFVbLYBieOtXMKX6AzpWmsbsf&fid=0x0:0xa7f85bb1a2bb89bf"],"When":"2023-12-12"},{"Name":"Ujwal Baweja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLja_obqYgWPyMF_SfnGf4p6q17DMkaRaL_xd830V41TiV0vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered two toppings pizza n they put the ratio of 90 % qty. of Capsicum n 10 % qty. of corn. Now, it's not eatable and they have denied to replace it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKldiqvGpvedqDiOB2OkW4CrIvjsobrWaTUOXxMspvKJNHw2g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"THIS RESTAURANT SERVED ME RAW CHICKEN. I ordered the Ceasar salad and when I went to bite into it I realized that the chicken was completely Raw! So I called To tell them and the woman who told me her name was Kieran (not sure of spelling) told me that they don't cook their chicken there and that it tastes better raw and that people don't get sick from eating raw chicken. She actually said that. No apologies, no offering to make it right. I asked for the owners contact information and she told me that he won't care about this and that he shouldn't be bothered with this issue. Then she told me that she will give me my money back but that they will never take an order from me again. I am so so disgusted by not only being served raw chicken and being told its fine, but the horrible customer service I received when I brought this to their attention. I order from there all the time, I can't even believe this is how they would treat a customer. Serving raw meat is never okay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2Ss3cMCES2OSPTdBsBzhYHhyKkeSWpS169wRC&fid=0x0:0xa7f85bb1a2bb89bf"],"When":"2021-8-8"}]

[{"Name":"Poonam Syan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWsK4bSKsgaXfYLz-69RxnQt7rxdbNI8dFNlHziMthj5gpnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Amazing Service by Dhyani!

I recently visited the Pizza Pizza store in New Westminster and was pleasantly surprised by the excellent customer service I received from Dhyani. She was incredibly friendly, welcoming, and made the experience so much better. Not only did she take my order efficiently, but she also made great recommendations that suited my preferences perfectly.

The pizza was fresh, delicious, and exactly as ordered. It’s rare to find such a great combination of tasty food and exceptional service, but Dhyani made it happen! I’ll definitely be coming back, thanks to her warm and professional approach. Highly recommend this location and be sure to ask for Dhyani when you're there!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQJpbDXFgQjpMv8u0Bed2Dq8c_OpbOIhPT7oY&fid=0x0:0x3dc7ae0d353627e2"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Josephine Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4ctBP8R2rm9S8Aa5NyuULMapTvyTQYakS6AvI9Cd025oSy86H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza had a deal where you could get 4 small 1 topping pizzas for $20, so my husband decided to take advantage of the deal.

The first time we tried Pizza Pizza was when they opened up a shop in New Westminster. We loved their pizza and ordered it many times.

Eventually a shop opened up closer to us, in Burnaby but we tried it twice and were quite disappointed with it.

When my husband saw this deal for the 1 topping pizzas, he decided to try ordering from the shop in New Westminster that we use to always order from before the one in Burnaby had opened.

Good call! It turns out, it's just that Burnaby location that's not up to par. The one we originally used to order from in New Westminster still makes excellent pizza. We'll only be ordering from that location from now on. Not going back to the Pizza Pizza in Burnaby ever again!

Service: Good

Location: 527 6th St., New Westminster, BC","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpQeKr9amEzfHmiw_5nvTewnc1FWBep4Tp6QX0&fid=0x0:0x3dc7ae0d353627e2"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Patel Heny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeeJELYczLx1E-tzRNK35OLtgnKy1yzFNkyhv1mwSmYEx-ZOU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an outstanding experience at Pizza Piza Store! The food was absolutely delicious—each bite of the pizza was perfectly cooked with fresh, high-quality ingredients. The variety of toppings and the unique flavor combinations were impressive. What truly stood out was the customer service; the staff was incredibly friendly and attentive, making sure every detail was perfect. I highly recommend this Store to anyone looking for top-notch pizza and a great dining experience. I'll definitely be coming back here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ganesh Kale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEJPxBdv0ynGu8yBGFDtHHpcWu3psVF1RoCQy-PpzZGUyEuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"i ordered 3 (1-extra large  and 2 large pizza on Friday and i received worst pizza i ever seen. mushroom and broccoli are almost half burn.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvSypyO1d_LKq5wDIxXgOjhafx3YMhdJ2YZ6Z0&fid=0x0:0x3dc7ae0d353627e2"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Jas Dhesi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQvfDH7uSMCEzro-CsN6IwB-0jOA8mYgacjQA_vQrRm_jz8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered pizza when I went to the store, the Girl at the  front was very friendly . The service was great and quick . very clean pizza store . Sat there with my kids to eat . I ordered chicken pizza , chicken tenders and wings. Food Tasted delicious. I recommend this pizza place .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amir Yousefi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQzNzY381-LWZEW-4YXqIwPWrNQXPQ2m75gH06nD0MtRhU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The staff’s behavior was not good at all. They were not professional. They started talking their own language in front of us.
They didn’t use gloves or hairnets.
The restaurant was very cold.
Any request we had was rejected. We asked for ketchup, and they said they didn’t have any. We had to swipe our card twice because it couldn’t be processed in a single transaction. I asked them to put all the pizza slices in one box, but they refused. Instead, they stacked two slices on top of each other.

It was not a good experience, and I absolutely not recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXY2HjShvQ_Cz09JqW0fv681DLjqachewnX3uVSlkf5Ee09RKZS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"*****BE CAREFUL WHEN PAYING!!!
My family usually order pizza from here, last time my father went to pick up 2 M pizza 2 toppings $9 dollar each,  the lady in the till had the debit machine ready to tap, when my father got in the car he noticed that this worker added $5 dollar tip without asking!! My understanding is that tips are OPTIONAL!!! I felt concerned about this as I think she took advantage of my senior dad","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sally Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWRytNEd3rFUQ5nqN3VotbBVQY7R-XLnx2acb4glkPd-K-gSTD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"**BUYER BEWARE**

There is a deal advertised on their website - $11.99 for a large 1-topping pizza. We have used this deal multiple times in-person. When I ordered a large pepperoni pizza at the store the other day, I was charged regular price. I paid, thinking the deal must no longer exist. However, sure enough, the deal was still there when I checked online. When I went to pick up the pizza, I asked and the employee said that the deal is “online only”.

When I got home, we read the fine print and it did not indicate anywhere that this special is “online only”. My husband went back to the store to confirm and the employee tried to argue that I had ordered the “recipe pizza”. Eventually they admitted that you CAN get the pepperoni pizza with the special so there was no reason to charge regular price for it, especially since I had referenced the special.  Eventually, my husband was given a $5 refund (the total difference was $5.65 lol. Oh well, by now, the amount we were owed was no longer the point).

All that to say, if the employee had charged me the regular price by mistake, I wouldn’t be mad. But to lie and say the special was “online only” to avoid honouring the deal is pretty scummy.

An email to their corporate office did not yield anything besides a scripted apology and response saying they will forward this to the appropriate team to address with the individuals involved.

All in all, pretty disappointed that none of the Pizza Pizza representatives proactively tried to make this right. We will not be back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

We had the sichuan spicy deep fried chicken which is pictured here. The pic is of only half the portion because we had already eaten the other half. Really crunchy, a little spicy and super tasty. We also had the bonless dried garlic pork and dan dan noodles which were both good too but that chicken wow. The owner Fiona was also really friendly and great to talk to. sichuan Yummy is a nice little gem.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCqWPWOv3UO1xVaZ6wKTGV9mw5YfNvGpxMt_63&fid=0x0:0xf4cb49848bba7420"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Eve Abrams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLOn2tgVKavLoEwrqVleFwjTjwyALn_uVpdUtCPvW-QlMHXWbh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food! The Sichuan chicken and honey prawns are especially outstanding. Fiona is the new owner 1 year ago and is an excellent chef buying fresh ingredients every morning. Her husband Johnny helps some evenings. They are so kind and attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgcMEu677zqQ_cKIuoeRYpyWT5n5sHulRcTmxR&fid=0x0:0xf4cb49848bba7420"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Steffen Demmitt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFHHwpToI4QtRhXMiSkA17C_b6r3gpZ3AXPde1PoUCdnlOD0sW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First off, the food was fantastic. You can tell it's not loaded with msg and harsh dyes and corn syrup. The sweet and sour pork was not bright red and overly sweet. I like this version. The dry garlic pork was the best I've had, honestly. The vermicelli noodles were a nice change from normal chow mein.
Secondly, this is a family restaurant. The owners and their kids are a very cute family and they care a lot about their business, the food and what they serve. They keep their prices low but the quality high. This is my new favorite Chinese food place, I think everyone should try.

I never give reviews, but there was absolutely nothing I didn't like about this adorable little establishment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Churchwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDoOs2_7WPuB7qqpthdBFttldETJlnMaXcAgN0pCZ-Y7fheA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly and personable in addition to excellent food.

We had three different dishes. One was a special order noodle dish , one a soup, and one a fried dish. All were excellent in taste, texture, preparation, everything. We could not decide who ‘won’ by getting the best dish.

There were a couple clarifying questions with the special order. Then the cook said, ‘will do’.

Definitely a place I can recommend and will do business with, again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diana Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUTFrTiQIrvcTrFfg1QrQ8Deh7Ze_gBfBcIfdBI89DT5v2xw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My 1st time ordering. I don't know if the owners are new or not. I must say the food is amazing and so is the price! If you are a Chinese food purist, you may not like it as the food is geared towards Westerners. Either way, the food is delicious! The lady who took my order is so welcoming and friendly! I highly recommend this place and this place is needed in the Brow of the Hill neighborhood. I will order from them again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP68_ewfRlLM2UMPMcNqjaeLH8YYcfhsSjTHXQl&fid=0x0:0xf4cb49848bba7420"],"When":"2023-1-31"},{"Name":"W Yeung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV60mis3bpZlz8qFhuGne2ZLWS2VhNV40zdvM3BS5jtQRQlPcDrCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Sichuan style Chinese food in New West, we enjoyed every single bite of the meal. Will be coming back from white rock !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs-Y-tCZE1W0ZkfjDz7guZQW6LnccyAFFWTrUL&fid=0x0:0xaecc574584f4b7c5"],"When":"2024-9-24"},{"Name":"M.Y. It is located on street level of a residential building,  thought I'd try take out first,  so I ordered the Beef Udon.  Went to pick it up,  the lady was friendly with a smile.  The broth was delicious the beef was tender.  Perfect. The cost came to $15+¢
Looking forward to testing the sushi next! 😋","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ricky Guan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPl4yNYNZp1SvXAlqdnC61ocV2kzbBMmwEqCvOrbZCIx8XslR8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Group of friends are now venturing into neighbourhood restaurants from Richmond. Found this gem through a recommendation. Seated for 8 through a booked reservation and had a private room!

Got the scallop aburi, soft shell crab roll and house roll - aburi quality is on par with the big Vancouver aburi shops. Highly recommend it. Friend also reiterated it was extremely tasty. Other two rolls were really fresh.

They dropped the price of the salmon aburi to $10 and I didn’t even see. Really wanted to try it. Another friend got the dinner bento and it seemed like crazy good value!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSiEgeSkys2EoiodkhNtCjgdH3H8hrEIBJ0COy&fid=0x0:0xaecc574584f4b7c5"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"IG hotlunchideas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiZwhqE1ymilpAiHGmsW4dSqHufAp4va14236FdaXtOKzf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have loved this restaurant since we tried it many years ago. Prices are good and the quality of the food is very good, fresh sashimi l, yummy tatakis oshis and aburis.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1TZJGUsYRuO7KjOo6w5jdJ1CyG2nShyuGIaU&fid=0x0:0xaecc574584f4b7c5"],"When":"2024-7-2"},{"Name":"T K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBjs_8XvvkzBMG-1HmgIjTdYzywRXtx1m_K9OxV4qzE99dY0-d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"You gotta eat here!! Nice food and atmosphere. Service is very good as well. I had the spicy salmon sashimi - pictured here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLJKThajeUtWqz2ORXjmDUT5FPB9jpQ9jdCnM&fid=0x0:0xaecc574584f4b7c5"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"AYM Zeto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVz5GvKrEg3A0tbZbuO2ffKhkWqqqvubt9jM_ZmqmuBuntJI2W4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great hidden little gem. Parking can be a challenge as most people have noted. I'm familiar enough with the area that I decided to bypass the parking and just walked from the SkyTrain (20 minute walk or so).

Food is really good and fresh, service is great. The server spilled my soy sauce (purely an accident; I wouldn't have detracted a star for that though) and they gave me spring rolls on the house.

Miso soup is hot, the spring rolls were hotter and the rolls were fresh. The scallop aburi was perfection.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOG2XaKMUHgBBtKiPIx8Np52tYiUOmrVgEK_t9A&fid=0x0:0xaecc574584f4b7c5"],"When":"2024-6-19"}]

[{"Name":"NO EDITS!","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTrp1VXXvSTdJg26oEr8_VrVVKxA-rhBkZwO9S5zp8nRthHr8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Friendly and good price, but quality of this meal was not good.

Where is my chicken? It's half the size of the bun... The chunk on the top bun is just skin, which was burnt and rolled up, tasted awful.  What chicken was there was also overcooked and dry AF.  Literally one bite gets onion...

I've had this sandwich at probably a dozen nandos locations, this isn't how these sandwiches should look or taste
(I ordered no tomato)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7iaT7sCtSH53pisl4PAxw78mbKpiGVfLVZefk&fid=0x0:0x2bd29f8bf31b3a3b"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"S A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJOMOiZKMkVhzEB7ZORr37dwap2afh8DAG6IHDyoctwDav8XVN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We went for lunch today around 1-2 and it was quite busy but not crowded!

As the  space is quite big enough, it didn’t seem crowded and the aesthetics are really good and I couldn’t stop myself from clicking pictures!

There was a guy who helped us today and he is very warm and welcoming, I didn’t ask for his name unfortunately but I would give 5/5 for his exceptional service!

The food is delicious, this is my second time visiting Nando’s but at diff location!

We ordered half chicken with mango and lime sauce - 4/5
Golden Cauliflower - 2.5/5
Spiced rice - 3/5
Peri peri fries - 4.5/5 I love peri peri flavour and the sauce from Nando’s!
One leg and thigh with hot sauce - 5/5
Kisses for dessert - 2.5/5
Custard tarts - 2.5/5
Rainbow rice bowl - 4/5

We had a coupon so we have used it and overall it’s a good experience !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkVTg_aBdU4RDzEBaLbD2PFU7vJOkpubE_NxlJ&fid=0x0:0x2bd29f8bf31b3a3b"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"loz designz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2Kh3OktqywzqCfM31W6GrKd8Vhm8o4t-rvOWhx5Nqw1jSDv1m=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ate for the first time at Nando's in Queensborough. I really enjoyed the lemon and herb flavour of my chicken, and the Brussels sprouts were good. We enjoyed our meals (perfectly cooked!) and the staff were all very pleasant and welcoming too. It was a bit chilly in the restaurant, but other than that we were comfortable. I'll return!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S K (OxtailGravy)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIINjUguJePPet75HTnX-unbS8rsk4LQ_Ku9eCz7eh0Wy--ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Consistently provides quality tasteful chicken with great customer service in a clean and organized restaurant. This is my go to lunch spot in New Westminster.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhQ-ZDz0797RHcEvNWO4uhqqyn3rPZpePuNwec&fid=0x0:0x2bd29f8bf31b3a3b"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"NDS Investments","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVikPs6WOuTzc-E92-sZ1BLaCA6XPNBLrLbmLXnMK-Mmkbrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our family only has done takeout at this location several times, not one issue to date.

We usually order either the Family platter or Jumbo chicken platter...few pics are attached.

Parking - plenty
Staff - attentive and wonderful
Food quality - always has been great
Portions - decent for chicken...as per sides, don't really like having to pay a fee for the rice to family portion.  The one the platters come with is not enough for a family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVDqj9a7lITay0mWYmdWLZdYT2jxXLbTXEVOT8&fid=0x0:0x2bd29f8bf31b3a3b"],"When":"2022-5-22"},{"Name":"Paighton D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3GQ1Hbfm1JHNEW83IOMXR9Az4y_1JBjQ4ckoTy247wLX8Bw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here for a lunch meal. At nandos I always order the chicken sandwich. I have never had a piece of chicken this small..... I kid u not it was mostly all bun & a couple bites of chicken. I called and she said all pieces of chicken are small for the sandwich and this is how they come now.
Well that's the last time I ever buy or eat there chicken sandwich. I want an actual proper portion of CHICKEN in the chicken sandwich.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpQkAJhWM61WTTuFdPLZbvkpnAffBmN1XT-IzO&fid=0x0:0x2bd29f8bf31b3a3b"],"When":"2023-11-29"},{"Name":"Curtis L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAXt2v13n7vgj7rJxv4X0f2PEgr_YXo4pwByRm1iYv5N-kpVs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a peri-peri bowl and I got the bowl with the chicken and when I got the bowl the piece of chicken I ordered was a big as maybe 3 chicken nuggets combined! Keep in mind the bowl was $17. The service was the only decent thing in this restaurant as the food came out quick. The atmosphere was pretty bad as there were only two other groups in the restaurant, there was also dirty dishes on some of the tables. Overall I am disappointed mainly in the portioning of the food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ariel Freebs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfNiZqYOh-Wg0pABIvhLNcpv8WWvwTVJ3bMyXrEVUERQ6geA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered a Chicken Peri peri bowl with this Nandos. I was served VERY raw chicken it was pink in every strip. When we brought it back to the counter, the manager was anything but nice to us. She gave us an extreme attitude back to me when asking for a refund and didn't seem to care at all that the kitchen just gave out pink chicken.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMW1IVLXUxEkR8NvX2k8KCSULO-kYPvTWnOVl39&fid=0x0:0x2bd29f8bf31b3a3b"],"When":"2023-10-19"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Hanna Y.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8LrpYG7xx4v1kQWGmot7xCcaz6evaR8tDdO0YcGQ-KC0CfLw2SQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"My friend got the shrimp tomato pasta and I got the picnic sampler (can’t remember the exact names on the menu but should be pretty close). My friend said her food tasted ok and was filling; I would say the same too but if you usually eat big portions, the tasting set I got might not be enough for you. The food was OK. Didn’t really find anything too unique or outstanding in terms of flavor etc. Just normal sushi in my humble opinion. It was a cute place but I wish they had some form of service. Everything was self serve when my friend and I got there — had to go up and order, get our own waters etc but as more people arrived while we were eating, I saw staff bringing menus and waters to tables and taking orders so I was confused. But overall not a bad experience, just not anything too special either.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPELAjmCgiKyc8PJEXDFe_bOpUnSlV1U3xnRvCU&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Celeste Yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIpSR-b1A4g31o5H8KWWYxuRcN1XZ5xBWouVdZTTfcsy21SQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As we were scrolling social media, we saw the food photos and decided to drive 25 minutes to give it a try. It was so delicious! All of the food was prepared with quality ingredients. So fresh 👏🥰

If you're looking for a cozy spot with great food at a reasonable price, this dining and cafe place is definitely worth a visit!

The flavors are spot-on, and the portion sizes are generous. The prices are surprisingly affordable for the quality of food you get.

Whether you're stopping by for a quick coffee or a full meal, try this new open place in New west! Highly recommended for anyone 🎊🎁","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOE_1raQ2wDidT_XO64gMrJ6TNd0w8B1GPcqd7F&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Vel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVAu-GvE4mA1NirOofZd-XTDEX5uPOQSOzmVSXf0N9FHsoHJw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered 2 of the picnic sushi samplers and I’m so glad we did because I wouldn’t want to share. It was lovely having a taste of multiple different flavours! The space is very open and airy and the employees were friendly and informative as it was our first time here. Will definitely be back to try the truffle mushroom noodles next!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmuliBLC35vkmBGT-I8im0-rnM4s4xqhxbFPFF&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Joane Thompson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXT0QXI_JGblf_Jmu0Od91iHSDLymbihaQI0yYUBHQnBO7KG_s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is absolutely delicious!

Their truffle udon is amazing- chewy and not overly creamy, which is perfect!
Their popcorn shrimp has lots of flavours which is interesting every bite!
And their sushi sampler is perfect for someone who cant decide!

Just that you have to go to the counter to order and prepay before eating, which is why one point was docked 🥲","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMr5C5QhL5-5ana_822FzZ2Gm0j7qdmztkUAHvK&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"Michelle Wan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxPyA4BLK3-WceDqM70WBBaWXOxCLW9ruWtaifPEiki-xc0VJ1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really love the atmosphere and vibe of this cozy Japanese fusion place. It's special compared to the neighbouring competition that is a more normal sushi restaurant. The sushi sampler I got is great for an indecisive person like myself.

I like how it is order at the front then wait for your order. I can simply leave once I'm done, no fuzz, no waiting around!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBwUY0iJbfP9Dqo9X8cv9tjqynvXoz0-rvb4sS&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrFP62q1VWyxHJxJ3KOkTtinMdTkw6epQMu0_FKz_IbEeXBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here after hearing really good reviews!

Always been a fan of Japanese fusion so I had high expectations and Kioku did not disappoint!! Super friendly staff and a very welcoming environment! There was a variety of options to choose from. The oshi platter gave me the choice to try everything - highly recommend!! The noodle dishes were the perfect balance of fusion flavours. My favourite was the truffle mushroom noodle! Spicy seafood salad is like a spicy ceviche, super fresh and perfect to start with!

They also have a full coffee service which was really convenient to have right after the meal!

If you're in the New West area highly recommend!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHArqSi43n2HByNsP0XEZLO9othG29bM2t_6QZ&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Daniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvd6-q0LFLnT6Fjanc2ymc9JLptLuzcaQqNrOdzOGpx9n_bEE6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Filling the shoes of AKD Kitchen, my expectations for quality was high. Thankfully, the food met that expectation.

The truffle mushroom pasta was a great balance of flavour and not being too heavy.

My favourite was the popcorn shrimp. It was my first time trying fried shrimp and it was the perfect ratio of crispy crunch to chewy shrimp. It was complimented extremely well with the salad and sauce.

I've also heard lots of great things about their sushi, so I can assure you that they hold a high standard for their food. That alone is worth going for!

The unfortunate downside I was willing to forgive (cause of the food😹) was their lack of service.

It's a bummer that they don't go out of their way to seat you, provide the menu for you, or refill your drink. I hope that will have changed cause that would benefit customer experience a lot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmSSJxT6A3_pqHqSuHkOf2IoO3pvmnNP6isHZb&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Natalie Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS2-mFWpQHfG0-UDwLE1Q7G7ElS6dnqN4ztMh6vSyHMHUEeGVM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There was so much anticipation to try out Kioku and everything about it exceeded my expectations. It was a total flavour bomb, bite after bite. The shop is nice and clean and the food comes out quickly. We ordered the Salmon Zukke, Mushroom Truffle Udon and the Sushi Sampler. All the dishes are presented beautifully! I haven’t even finished my meal and I’m already trying to plan when I can get back here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpNBjFaO9d-97AJyE7Z4eVbQ5XiqAYW59q-URp&fid=0x0:0x6521e0a010608098"],"When":"2024-12-11"}]

[{"Name":"Juliana Porto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1NsObHvzim5fX9Olc5MHUf_dYmQIrIKDlOq_BaNnHFW_TVHXh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dani Pani is absolutely amazing! The food is always delicious, and their service is top-notch. Recently, I had a small issue with the packaging of my order and shared my feedback. Their response blew me away—they were so kind, professional, and truly committed to improving. They immediately took steps to address my concerns and even went above and beyond to make things right.

This place has consistently delivered exceptional food and outstanding service, and they’ve truly earned my loyalty. I highly recommend this restaurant to everyone! You won’t be disappointed. :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Tuczek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJej_EcaTFfvf2bdZNoRSkjtMwubDn3JzZEj8GnYeKvt_ndmHP8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Dani Pani, and I was blown away by the experience! From the moment I walked in, the atmosphere was warm and inviting. The staff was incredibly friendly and made us feel right at home. The food was absolutely delicious—each dish was bursting with flavor, and you could tell everything was made with fresh ingredients and authentic spices. I especially loved the coconut chicken, which was cooked to perfection. The portion sizes were generous, and the service was quick and attentive. If you're a fan of Indian cuisine, this place is a must-visit. Can't wait to come back for another amazing meal!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thedishdetective Lala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKD_tj6k6xpF8R8uVmPtHQuGBgjvefVOKaKmqeE1mkWnmvdyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dana Pani Indian Cuisine Review

•	Location: 805 Boyd St J120, New Westminster, BC V3M 5X2, located in SmartCentres Queensborough Landing.

Service: The service was commendable, with attentive staff ensuring a pleasant dining experience. It deserves an 8 out of 10.

Overview: Dana Pani Indian Cuisine stands out as one of our favorite Indian restaurants and a hidden gem in the area. We visited for a quick bite and were thoroughly impressed by the quality and flavor of the dishes.

Food:

•	Appetizer: We started with a large portion of vegetable pakora. These were excellently prepared, with a perfect fry and a well-balanced seasoning blend. The appetizer sets a promising tone for the meal and merits an 8 out of 10.

•	Main Course: We opted for the Tiffin Thali, a diverse and satisfying selection that included both vegetarian and non-vegetarian items, rice, naan, and raita.

•	Palak Paneer: This dish, a staple of North Indian cuisine, features paneer (Indian cottage cheese) in a rich, flavorful spinach-based sauce. The spinach is blanched and pureed to a smooth consistency, then sautéed with onions, garlic, ginger, and tomatoes, along with a medley of spices. It was expertly prepared and rates an 8 out of 10.

•	Chicken Tikka Masala: Known for its vibrant orange color and rich, creamy, spiced tomato-based sauce, this dish did not disappoint. The balance of flavors and the aromatic quality of the sauce were excellent. It earns an 8 out of 10.

•	Chana Masala: This dish features chickpeas cooked in a spicy and tangy tomato-onion gravy. It is a staple in Indian cuisine, celebrated for its rich flavors and aromatic spices. While tasty, it lacked the depth of flavor found in the other dishes and receives a 7 out of 10.

•	Butter Chicken: A personal favorite, this dish featured a creamy, luscious sauce with tender, delicious chicken. It stood out as the highlight of the meal and deserves a 9 out of 10.

Ambiance: The ambiance is modest but comfortable. While the space is small, it is adequately maintained and provides a cozy setting for dining.

Price: The pricing is very affordable, making it an excellent option for those seeking quality Indian cuisine without breaking the bank.
2/5

Verdict: Dana Pani Indian Cuisine is truly a hidden gem and one of the best Indian restaurants in the area. The variety and quality of the food are outstanding, and the affordability adds to its appeal. For those who enjoy spicy food, it’s worth noting that while the dishes are flavorful, they cater to various spice preferences, offering non-spicy, medium, and very hot options. Overall, it’s a restaurant we will certainly return to and highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5yhzePV_P4zOnZyLnxZOBpAWD7VNYor1BubP0&fid=0x0:0xe029e562e7fb717a"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Chris Lochhead","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuiipc_xz9ET6nJtGoC_1SL7eafro7oB6Q-WiHyZ8PyZyITQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is a hidden New Westminster gem.  All the tasty curries you’d expect from an Indian restaurant but their cooks have an extra touch at this spot.  The naan bread (especially if you are dining in) is the absolute best in the entire lower mainland….just the right amount of crisp on the outside.  Try their Tali combo for lunch, which is a serving of two curries of your choice with rice and naan but sized for a single person…yum!  Pay a little more and make it three curries!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPl_W-FowSvJSeQc2xstWZl9ce2nbCFVentarXb&fid=0x0:0xe029e562e7fb717a"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The restaurant seemed humble but the food was tasty. My goat curry was so delicious while my husband loved his butter chicken so much. They're also very generous with the quantity of meat and rice in the portion. I especially love their garlic naan, so buttery!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJvUT8qqNQ-oJm5478Swlqw48bEmAmAjgDyUkL&fid=0x0:0xe029e562e7fb717a"],"When":"2024-3-20"},{"Name":"Hanna Sampson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUI13FeBwcP-10PKakA44vzfLYMGFIcjAI-w79aF7DmVwltrQq5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food and at a VERY reasonable price! Nice and cozy restaurant. The owner and the staff are very friendly and service is 10/10. Food quality is always fresh and delicious. My hot favorites are Fish Pakora and Grilled fish and in main course Mutton Curry. Their Indo-Chinese food is also great.

I would definitely recommend this restaurant to the locals as a GoTo place for Indian food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoW7PHAsjWzbqNC_S1QcCw5NCfBBxgi3dnQkQi&fid=0x0:0xe029e562e7fb717a"],"When":"2022-10-30"},{"Name":"Dhrumit Sheth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9r95Es3YQAlkO6Yw2Yg4R0kNpVi-5oWmckdwTw51wptlXqgTS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was craving for some fast food and found this place on google so I decided to give it a try. We recently came by to bring my sister and my niece who is visiting in town. EpicSilog is me and my husband go-to for Authentic Filipino food in BC so my family must try it during their visit. The owner was really nice and approchable, we get to chitchat to found out that she and her family was from Winnipeg, MB as well. It was so nice seeing fellow Winnipegers. She gave us a sample of her Mango Mousse. She was thinking of adding it to their already delish menu list and ask us to send her a feedback. I wanted to send her my input on it but I didnt get her contact. Hopefully this will able to reach her? The Mango was so fresh and big chunks was a real bonus, which I am sure people will appreciate because I certainly did! The cake layer was soft and not dry at all, and the buttercream/ganache/creamcheese, not sure what the cream was made of, super delish! I found myself kept on scooping until its was just the empty cup left. It was not too sweet nor bland. A perfect taste of a great dessert. I see myself ordering this type of mouse if she ever decided to make one for orders 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWFKsf8e7lAG8Ff8Vlfc1yrXXCejM69mcAmfO8&fid=0x0:0x7d819c908ae2141e"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"Tearna Salvesen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_A5qweBOzpqxR3-rNhjGapVyg_fFMEktwqcm_lRq1vNUpevSGfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Epic Grill Silogs was highly recommended from my friend in Texas so when we came to Vancouver we had to try it! user_reviews: [{"Name":"Helen Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKI-mzgGlleZ4ePt7mDYbQ4Gabh9zw-OBKk6bKlySQQQboerA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service! Food is delicious. We ordered curry beef stew, stir fried vegetable, and pan fried shrimps. My favorite is the pan fried shrimps. They are really tasty. We also ordered the shrimp dumplings but I forgot to take a picture. The atmosphere is great too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8-vtXXRnLQjyEeAAuL35jbb-rsGBTqTSnPnNw\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"minnie li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRoQOlIxvrw__7xun_s22_XplGfNg8u2NALefXOOF5MWkjHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at this Chinese restaurant. The atmosphere is fantastic, with a spacious, high-ceilinged dining area that feels very comfortable. Unlike many other Chinese restaurants, the tables here are generously spaced, giving diners plenty of room without feeling cramped. The dim sum selection is excellent, offering a wide variety of tasty dishes. One of the standout features is that there is no extra charge for tea, which means you can save a bit and order an extra dish instead.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-elniB3Hl2xWWwsMV20UfYj7JPo45Q9rbfB5_\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Peter Powell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEWICjNsYatccfG8tJU6H4w44FxzrmrGxqQilpFtPRJqpzz2xy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Comfortable dining room and good service. Our group had a set dinner with suckling pig. All the food was very good. The pig was delicious, crispy skin that was delicate and crunchy. The meat was tender and moist. Enjoyed every dish although the chicken was a little dry (common problem) even the dessert was great, black sesame balls in almond flavour milk","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQwBTYDYQZcj-v30N7LNcD4G_NH0PQNi6H4BI0\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Jenny Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgIEDkB2PzsQAjZtJxzL5NwawLrCpei_X1mvBSmllmI0Q-tBD5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both the dim sum and service here are great! The location is kind of weird and a bit challenging to both find and navigate out of with so many blocked paths/streets. The har gao, har cheung, fung jow, and pai gwut were all tasty! We didn't have enough enthusiastic eaters to try more but I'd love to come back sometime to taste more of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-35rkTyMgdRaBUJ03HfzyFPeW_rVUCeeUzPA7\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Stephie N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd0_eqzaDNFpYKxu_At0QKV_opW1IXDZ3BtSf_D5LFw7-X91jS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love going to Kirin Seafood Restaurant for dim sum. Unlike other dim sum restaurants, we always feel well-treated here. The service is detailed and prompt. Since we are not Chinese, we can’t say for certain if the dim sum is authentically made, but we love it! We always enjoy visiting this place and always will. I apologize for my poor photography skills; my pictures don’t do justice to their delicious dim sum.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlG2wAPlH7JowuXk90cPCEDk3XOcsvTxfgnNzL\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Yan Jie Pan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWtJgsuhwRId0t1MOzd5ywiIXfrBfIFDTo7UODkLUu9At3EXtegw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our friends invite us to come for lunch here, and now I’m in love with their lunch menu 😻 so many options of dim sum, and you can taste that it’s freshly made, I enjoyed them so much, and the egg tart is a must order!!! I can finish a plate of egg tart by myself 🤤 everything is worth trying, I want to come back again to try the others!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMok6cppc8y5jMaY6pPG6bkffjl_g7zGArNij8\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"Craig Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHYc_KX8jVjM1EqjfvQu304OSChoZgYUkr4ijG-TFif8471A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Juicy Siu Mei and perfectly cooked Pan Fried Prawns are our favorites this visit. The eggplant dish was overwhelmed by the fish paste and oil. The ham hock dish, on special now, was cooked well and served cold similar to poached chicken. The Beef Rice Noodle texture and flavor was perfect despite having very little beef.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGK2CzBM8uZWE1_1erm4yOs5IgF0Ns69XqSmx_\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Junhua Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXxr7N9U4iv6nEFijXKvyBgZmRQZVZlxLrBqwPq87wnlqswGv9kA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I like this restaurant. It has good service and is less crowded than the Richmond branch. The food is delicious. The portion size is just right, and they have a good selection of dishes. It is definitely one of my top dim sum places.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwfdlj7yxXWwElfc13R-1pUH7pnHLnGe6cAH3k\u0026fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2021-8-31"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Yvon Bobillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuBofwNzBTdpqP96d-D6i41TeAhBbXb0rorL7ndPnurOPFALc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We traveled all the way from Richmond to try this place, and it was absolutely worth it! The food is not only delicious but also incredibly affordable. The staff is warm and welcoming, making the entire experience even better. We had a fantastic time and will definitely be returning!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbKZQwzkcGgMEXWQF77Md4Ir6MQsHR44ES8104&fid=0x0:0xbd85d52ec3b602a3"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"J B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAwkGdHptp4NSG8jB1yPnzY78ZK3uNzq5DBh4dOU1f3ajFAto=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a tiring day of shopping, my stomach was screaming for some authentic Filipino comfort food. Luckily, this gem of a restaurant popped up on my search. Nestled within the Food Zone Inn, the place was a cozy haven with a clean and inviting atmosphere. The friendly staff made me feel right at home.

I couldn't resist ordering the classic chicken inasal, drizzled with its signature sweet soy sauce. The chicken was so tender and flavorful that it melted in my mouth. My only regret was not asking for the extra kick of calamansi and chili. It would have been the perfect finishing touch.

As a side, I indulged in a heavenly tortang talong. It
was a nostalgic taste of home, reminding me of my Nanay's cooking. While it was delicious on its own, I can't wait to try it with banana ketchup next time.

This place is a must-visit for anyone craving a taste of the Philippines. I'll definitely be back when I'm in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPykczuNPB-fE1y3oedVJYNcQIp4EcUUut0QTL&fid=0x0:0xbd85d52ec3b602a3"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"bon dorado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdm5gZCia8b-qm6PJV15yM_nzzE6iOmLUAc3M507ZZqAs6Um60=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a regular on their spot since they started out. From previous location to this new location, you just keep coming back… for more!!!! Food is awesome! When it comes to options on their menu, they have hit the spot, in my case anyway! Honestly, 100% recommended for any Foodie and crave monsters like myself out there!

And one more BEST thing so far, NANAY, like any other Filipino household, will take you home to give you that “FILIPINO HOME VIBE” you have been craving for years of working hard in the Lower Mainland!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNo4-K3PeT0UTjWAL6cKxkEfd7HX3ge7sG5CaOj&fid=0x0:0xbd85d52ec3b602a3"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Branden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIs6a_R5xAIaJ3H2Q6Ffpj_MclDRcJQiQ0Lkja_94WV7pr_tw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Some of the best Filipino I've had in the Greater Vancouver area. Extremely flavourful meats and the most garlicky fried rice you can ask for.

The beef silog and pork silog was amazing. Tried tortang talong (eggplant omelette) for the first time and I'd have to say I'm a fan. Staff was very friendly and service was good.

Highly recommend, definitely coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjUeeNEn2eHg13QtZjbpqbJS7yY_KXDAw3loYI&fid=0x0:0xbd85d52ec3b602a3"],"When":"2024-4-14"},{"Name":"Steve B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfl0h7LBzTP2I19EaQ980hbd2gVAQ-0Kn286XLsVt3NEFo4W0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has become my go-to spot for my big family gathering meals. Reasonable price, good portion size, great flavour and wonderful presentation of food. Pork Skewers are always put family's favourite. Service is always pleasant. My wish list to love this place even more? May be some vegetable options, appetizers with some texture such as Lumpia Shanghai, and allowing two same meat options to be chosen for each Feast order. This place is a must try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM41vFs1axpcsj_Jk5GoU60mpdTLaIz-VunQ59Y&fid=0x0:0xbd85d52ec3b602a3"],"When":"2024-2-18"},{"Name":"Patricia Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWnbybtut_h9HpLE5qFRIRBoJpjF5RREEnyejWQM0OH3IF8BE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered the fiesta feast plus a tray of skewers and it was more than enough to cover for about 25 people. I’m certain that it would’ve been enough for about 35 people too! People were impressed by how tasty the food was. The first to be finished was the palabok (I’ve never seen a palabok dish be finished before anything else) then the chicken inasal was definitely next to be devoured. The sauce of the bbq kept the skewers tasty and all the meats were very tender, even though we served dinner a few hours after delivery. I told our guests that when ordering from NK, they are always very consistent in flavours and presentation is beautiful. NK also had great communication with me which I really value from vendors and they delivered within the time agreed upon. I like the fact that orders can be placed by credit card online and way in advance. Saves me the hassle on a busy day. If there’s one thing that I’d suggest, it would be to add a veggie dish (ensaladang talong or something similar to a papaya salad) to accompany the grilled meats. That would complete the meal for me personally. But overall, I’m happy with my experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Jacob Pondar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0RewjrxMafb-RZK_5ylD1yBFmVh4z2flPHBqb6iTA_Rcmm2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good filipino food! portions were more than what other restaurants usually serve you. price is very friendly especially when you are on a budget. Staff were very polite and welcoming. atmosphere is wonderful… all i can say is that you will never have a problem dining here. 10/10 nice one kabayan! 🇵🇭","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiJbb4M0_bR6OMge4ZBdWIrWZQXVQiITu9Fcj0&fid=0x0:0xbd85d52ec3b602a3"],"When":"2024-2-7"},{"Name":"Kat T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUDE4zgvtMjdVoNDqd6hfL-1XFbXR-GxJgbxeIO4fWu5NKBkP-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried everything - liempo, beef, skewers, chicken, and talong (eggplant). It was all so tasty and juicy. The liempo and eggplant were my fave, and garlic rice was 10/10! Customer service was really nice, they kept offering us soup and checked in that we were doing okay. Highly recommend. Best Filipino food in the lower mainland. I can’t wait to go back to try more!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"antikimchi1","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2L3QPY-4Xjn1xG1ozNxML_0IbnWHok02hx2skd97rBbsEMM4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"A mini bowl for $11. Server had one job to add the protein and proceed to not add it.This shop is right beside a busy hospital and patient families come here to get a quick bite. This level of incompetency will probably be the last thing they want to experience when their loved ones are laying in the hospital bed. Owner of you see this please talk to your employee. This is a take out order on Sept 2 2024 at around 7:10pm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfrvE5FSQWLTIpwsTwEdS0u6py9v1gegsREyiD&fid=0x0:0x160f948e58d50f9b"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Evan Chong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9ktw6YkD4mK7Esox2Dd__HCZhLtoSZYR_iUG-BR8M2BnBw43Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Zoe who served me and my friend was an excellent server! She greeted us as the door, asked us how we were and put a big smile on our faces! She was extremely patient, friendly, and an overall personable person to talk to! I am so glad that I came in today as she made our days so much better with her positive and kind attitude. She is one of the best employees at this location that does everything in her power to provide a perfect and smooth ordering experience! Definitely coming back to this location! I hope I get to see Zoe again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fresh and filling! Good flavour options for their tuna, salmon and Scallop. The option to build your own bowl let's you customize to your liking. I like the base options which includes quinoa, salad and rice. They have large portion sizes compared to other poke places I've tried. This particular location is very clean, modern and has plenty of seating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMeVJmVH07YekRcffLPfHZUGRosB01gsqdCybw&fid=0x0:0x160f948e58d50f9b"],"When":"2023-8-6"},{"Name":"jen h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhCIsdNpI0zn0ln1R2W8y6FEnO7Rpwo3p2N6L3S94WtNoyzHf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Clean inside and pretty decent seating for the area. It is a bit cold in general (not a heated place/one to stay long) but overall good enough to eat and go. The passionfruit tea was soso in my opinion otherwise I love going to this chain for my poke fix! Always say yes to the furikake, and crunchy toppings because they just make the dish that much better. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Clara Chau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoMWRC0cDGP4nCpQ1_Zdm86daXS0A0KJbVAa9QczqqbfD7fWIZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been here twice now and I am fairly certain I'll be back again to get this elusive flan (I haven't been successful yet). The first time was with my husband and 2 friends about a month ago. We got the guacamole and chips to share and each ordered our own main dish. I had the 3 tacos with chorizo, carnitas, and fish as my meat and I chose fries as my side. Husband ordered the torta with chorizo and my friends had the tostadas and fish Baja tacos. Our food came very quickly after ordering and we were given extra sauces on the side to add as we eat. All four of us enjoyed our food and the atmosphere. We heard good things about the dessert flan but both times they were sold out. Hopefully in the next visit I'll be able to taste it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHXUjeejh_G-7ewlR4dDRRR3dcRamPh1s3MY28&fid=0x0:0x257e17c9799be243"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Duncan Nicol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl1RXaz9W1cG-1cQpzWus9MyZ9Z4DmwmfJ19N3WRDODGCbi3K7Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Tortas I’ve had. Place looks like an absolute dive from the outside (would normally have just walked by) but really nice inside and fantastic food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlmtjhhE0fNVvRdJbyotWhNlLQF3wWESY4DdgA&fid=0x0:0x257e17c9799be243"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Andy A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGvasi7PsFPWMRfT4NMlzGHrKNCf-A6CbeWvUerIXboZWgXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food, one of the best nachos we have ever had after Mexico, very authentic. I believe they make their own nacho chips instead of using the ready-made ones.

Came to know that their cooks are from Mexico city itself (that explains the authentic taste).

Also their churros are awesome!! Not overly sugary, served hot with chocolate sauce and whipped cream. Definitely recommend.

I just wish they introduce more vegetarian options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCI6Ub5m8AeP3rT5KHFVQWmY1nlQgERSj8Cmkl&fid=0x0:0x257e17c9799be243"],"When":"2024-1-13"},{"Name":"Tony Stroppa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWorU-K8BuW1G92AwUP46oBpOOvZatjMsJvChPZs-Ffd8rYPHmI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Review is written by my nine year old kid:

The churros and the jarritos were to die for. Me and my family has come multiple times, and we love it here. My mom loves the bacon burrito, and I love the jarritos and churros.  10 outta 10, would come again! "P.S. bring back the refried beans with feta!"-My Mom","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCl7YwMrWEinEQWmwV5MpLGC9sER3491VS-o5N&fid=0x0:0x257e17c9799be243"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Alejandra Valdivia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8KhKjwQ_JYy6yRml8Z0cCQaZCrE5oPKHpc1pD3B2yyrB7QOs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super delicious and very friendly service. We're definitely coming back soon and I highly recommend this place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marsel Elaine Juntilla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBxi4KTbooe-HxJ-LiPZ8gSHtcvyFddZlwZPGT8h3h3WmgX3Wd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love it! Coming back for more! :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfTxSXllFHBwHuxrqZBzZoXclLy2YTwffi1OG5&fid=0x0:0x257e17c9799be243"],"When":"2024-1-15"},{"Name":"Greg Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJc26XK8oC8MA7dwJ11WFGzppk4Qs30IcrfJ_S0JDnHt5n7xg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had some great Tacos here the other day.

I have never seen anything like this ever. I ordered 4 toppings gluten free pizza and I couldn’t believe how trash the food was. So thin it was like they put one small piece of ham and few sausages and few mushrooms on a piece of paper and sold it for $30. When I call them she said you ordered gluten free and this is what you get and I am sorry I cant do anything for you. I understand that you gotta run your business but at what price? Selling people trash and charge them lots of money and expect them To be happy and give you 5 stars?The food was so unbelievably soggy, cold, undercooked, thin, cheap and disgustingly made. Do you have to sell people trash just because they cant eat gluten? So embarrassing. I am embarrassed for you guys. I am thankful uber refunded my money but this is NOT how you should treat your customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOywJOGem6pWKMNJTVG-JbNOW1ps0doJ02Vc_mS&fid=0x0:0x88dbfcd83ccaa26f"],"When":"2024-1-26"},{"Name":"Gagandeep Singh Nijjar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBcbAv1VDOTZw6DYyuw5_g9PLWCBbPv2DYPHFyjULaXJDavw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great staff and fantastic pizza!I ordered an unlimited topping pizza, and despite the busy environment, the pizza was perfectly made. [{"Name":"Jason York","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2KL5JJiTZL1QVt_3AcqILQXXBIuqDWdYOdj3lYENvavlAma6S8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Compared to other flame grilled chicken restaurants, this is the best chicken.

We ordered the Shack Pack which includes a whole chicken and two large sides for $45.

The flavour of the Citrus & Herb chicken was tangy and flavourful!  The chicken was super TENDER and JUICY, even when we ordered near closing time!  Also, the dipping sauces were spectacular!

We also ordered the Reece's Peanut Butter Cheescake.  All cheesecakes are from The Cheesecake Factory.  I'm sure it was previously frozen but yummy nonetheless.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFpGJH1VRYnN6HWsqhxXh8Cr8nDedGtBsJI_R5&fid=0x0:0x1cd91bd1b13c01f2"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We liked the citrus & herb chicken skewers but not a big fan of the quarter breast because there's not much meat after removing the skin and bones. The mango quarter thigh was great, I like the marinate. We got flatbread and peti fries as sides and both met expectations for a fast food joint. The shop was clean but tiny, there were 4 dine-in customers but it was already packed. The staff were nice and fast. Free parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXCsJAv7G0GAD4pZiuvF41Uar4CBIu37PZuHjM&fid=0x0:0x1cd91bd1b13c01f2"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Lee Down","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx6yinfV6FX-hVwZ65Bd31UAHnzUnUA6QaeukpoNScMaTzp9yJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered via Skip to try their food for the first time tonight and I was over the moon happy with the taste, freshness and quality. I had the whole Citrus and Herb chicken with two sides, Cole Slaw & Mac and Cheese. Everything was delicious. They included two sauces which I dipped my chicken in and that added to the experience and exceeded my expectations.
